\id 2SA - Mbula
\h 2 Samuyila
\toc3 2 Sam
\toc2 2 Samu
\toc1 2 Samuyila
\mt1 ƁARIA SAMUYILA
\imt1 MƏNCAU
\im Malǝmce \k Ɓaria Samuyila \k* mǝnana nda kpata Samuyila Mǝdǝmbe ka bangcau amur acau-ɓaraɓara mala yálmúrû mala murǝm Dauda, tite a bu-nzali Yahuda a njar-kúnmur (akùré 1-4), sǝ amur nzalî puppup, kpapi andǝ Isǝrayila mǝnana a njar-nza ka (akùré 5-24). Mǝnia ka caugilǝa na mǝnana à gilǝì kǝla mǝnana kumban ngga, amur wara mǝnana Dauda war andǝ aɓimǝbura mana à nda aɓa nzali male sǝ andǝ arǝcandǝa mala abǝri-nzali ka, ace tangsǝ domurǝm male andǝ tsǝk bunomurǝm male ɓǝ̀ pangnǝ rǝcandǝa. Dauda ka à lǝmdǝi ɓwa na mǝnana ndanǝ gūliarǝu mǝlime andǝ paɓamuru aban Ɓakuli ka, sǝ ɗǝm ngga ɓwa na mǝnana gandǝnǝ nun ɓabum aɓwana male ɓǝà kùr ɓamuria arǝ kpate nǝ ɓabumia mwashat ka. Kat andǝ amani ka, à lǝmndǝ Dauda kǝla ɓwa mǝnana a ɓè pwari ka kǝ sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr ɗàng, sǝ kǝ pàkki acauɓikea mǝɓike nǝ eare male ace mǝnana nǝ̀ pàk gìr mǝnana nggūrǝì andǝ bumi earkiyice ka. Sǝama lang Natan mǝɓangnǝa mala Yahweh kumi nǝ cau mala acauɓikea male ka, Dauda ear ama mǝsǝcau pàkki acauɓikê, sǝ ak nunkiru mana Ɓakuli tasǝì ka.
\ip Do-yilǝmu mala Dauda andǝ agir mǝnana peǎ ka, ɓoarî amǝ Isǝrayila kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Sǝ mǝno tsǝa lang nzali malea yi kútí aɓa tanni arǝ anza mǝnana à yiu nǝnzǝ́mò, sǝ à earce alta ɓè murǝm ngga, à earce ɓwa mǝnana <<muna mala Dauda>> na ko <<mǝ'kà Dauda na>> ka, mǝnana nda a nggurkwar mala Dauda, sǝ nǝ̀ pàk kǝla yì ka.
\iot Agir mǝnana a ɓalǝi ka
\io1 Dauda yálmúr bu-nzali Yahuda \ior 1:1--4:12\ior*
\io1 Dauda yálmúr Isǝrayila kat \ior 5:1--24:25\ior*
\io2 Apǝlǝa mǝdǝmbe \ior 5:1--10:19\ior*
\io2 Dauda andǝ Batsheba \ior 11:1--12:25\ior*
\io2 Azunggǝliban andǝ adomǝkwane \ior 12:26--20:26\ior*
\io2 Apǝlǝa mǝ'nzǝ́moè \ior 21:1--24:25\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Dauda okce lú mala Sawul
\p 
\v 1 Anzǝm lú mala Sawul, lang Dauda nyàrǝ́nì wal amǝ'Amalek ka, pǝlǝa ueo a Zikǝlag nongŋo ɓari.
\v 2 A tàruia nongŋo ka, ɓè ɓwabura mǝnana pur a kàttì mala Sawul ka yiu, nǝ gìr'nggūrǝu mǝsanne arǝì nǝ tú a ɓamuri. Sǝ lang bwalǝna ban Dauda ka, ɓunno, kpa nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali.
\v 3 Dauda ɗì ama, <<A pur nǝ kǝshe sǝ a yiu?>> Sǝ ɓwabure pe wi eare ama, <<Ən ɓwar nǝ ɓwaro aɓa kàttì mala amǝ Isǝrayila.>>
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Dauda ɗì ama, <<Lang sǝ gìrnî pǎ? Banggam.>> Pǝlǝa eari wi ama, <<Aɓwe ɓàngŋǝ́nì kun-munǝo, sǝ ɗǝm ngga pas atà aburana ka, à wuna, sǝ Sawul andǝ muna-ɓwabura male Jonatan gbal ka, à wuna.>>
\v 5 Dauda ɗì lagga mǝno banggiyi wi cau ka ama, <<Lang sǝ a sǝlǝ ama, Sawul andǝ muna-ɓwabura male Jonatan ngga à wuna?>>
\v 6 Laggè bang ama, <<Mǝ nda amúr nkono Gilbowa, sǝ ǝn yakiarǝ Sawul aban eangnǝe arǝ nkongŋo male, sǝ awaru-pǝr andǝ amǝ'pǝ̀r na tù aban yiu amurí.
\v 7 Lang pǝlǝ mǝsǝi a nzǝmi ka, sǝnam, pǝlǝa tunǝam, sǝ ǝn eari wi, nǝma, <Mǝ ndya ka.>
\v 8 Sǝ ɗiem ama, <A nda yana?> Ən eari wi nǝma, <Mǝ nda ɓwa'Amalek.>
\v 9 Pǝlǝa banggam ama, <Yiu cam a nkanggariam sǝ wu wal-luem, acemǝnana mǝ nda aɓa tanni mǝkǝ̀rkǝ́rnì mala lú, sǝ yilǝmem malaká pur ɗàng.>
\v 10 Nda ǝn cam a nkanggari sǝ ǝn wal-luí ka, acemǝnana ǝn sǝlǝna nǝma pà nǝ̀ au ɗàng anzǝm mana ɓǝ̀ kpana ka. Sǝ ǝn twal mbulan-murǝm mǝnana a ɓamúrí ka andǝ mbaga mǝnana a nggwarbui ka. À ndya ǝn yinǝì ɓwamǝgule mem nǝia ka.>>
\p 
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Dauda bwal nggea-daura male sannì,\f + \fr 1:11 \fq bwal nggea-daura male sannì \ft ko <<bumkiɗikea bwali kǝ̀rkǝ́r.>>\f* sǝ aburana mǝnana kat à nda atè ka, à pàk anggo gbal.
\v 12 À pak-bumkiɗikea, à ɓua, sǝ à gilmur ba pwarikpǝra, ace Sawul andǝ muna-ɓwabura male Jonatan, sǝ ace aɓwana mala Yahweh andǝ ɓala Isǝrayila, acemǝnana à wal-luia a kun-munǝo ka.
\p 
\v 13 Pǝlǝa Dauda ɗì lagga mǝno yinǝi wi nǝ cau ka ama, <<A pur a ya ban?>> Pǝlǝa eari wi ama, <<Mǝ nda muna mala ɓwa'kúnɗàngna, ɓwa'Amalek.>>
\v 14 Dauda banggi wi ama, <<Pàk lang sǝ ɓangciu pàkkô arǝ loasǝ buo ace wal-lú ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh tàrì ka ɗàng?>>
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Dauda tunǝ mwashat atà alaggana male, sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Kya wal-luí.>> Nda walì sǝ wù ka.
\v 16 Sǝ Dauda bang ama, <<Bafe mala nkiliò ɓǝ̀ ue amuro, acemǝnana we nǝ kuno sǝ a bang ama, <Ən wal-lú ɓwa mala Yahweh mǝnana à ɗārǝi ka.> >>
\s1 Nggyal keban mala Dauda ace Sawul andǝ Jonatan
\p 
\v 17 Sǝ Dauda tsǝk mǝnia yì nggyal keban ngga, sǝ keban amur Sawul andǝ muna-ɓwabura male Jonatan.
\v 18 Sǝ bang ama, ɓǝ̀ à kànî amǝ'kau mala Yahuda mǝnia yì nggyal keban mǝnana à tunǝi ama Nggyal mala Nta ka; nda kam a gilǝe aɓa Malǝmce mala Jashar:\f + \fr 1:18 \fq Malǝmce mala Jashar: \ft ko \fqa Malǝmce mala Amǝ'ɓealu-pǝrapǝra.\f*
\q1 
\v 19 We Isǝrayila, amǝgulo mô amǝ'ɓoarɓwe ka, à walna-luia amur ankono mò.
\q2 Akanggǝrang aburana kpana!
\q1 
\v 20 Wu kǝa nace a Gat ɗàng,
\q1 wu kǝa hamnǝ ce amur anjarɓala mala Ashkelon ɗàng,
\q1 cè amuna-mamǝna mala amǝ'Filisti pàkkiɗire,
\q1 cè amuna-mamǝna mala amǝ'ɗwanyi-kasǝ-ɓatau pàk-banɓoarnado.
\q1 
\v 21 Wun ankónó mala Gilbowa, mbulo ko ncimna ɓǝkǝa nya amur wun ɗàng,
\q2 ko amur aɓaban ma'wun mala pusǝ mǝsǝsa ace apaɓoro ɗang.
\q1 Acemǝnana akàm sǝ à ɓǝsǝki antongŋo mala akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa.
\q2 Ntongŋo mala Sawul ka à hasǝi wi mùrú ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 22 Nta mala Jonatan nyarnǝ te arǝ nkila,
\q1 ko arǝ mùrú-nyama mala akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa mǝnana wal-luia ka ɗàng;
\q1 sǝ nggeabyau mala Sawul ka nyar ɓà ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 23 Sawul andǝ Jonatan ngga,
\q1 aɓwana earcea sǝ à pwasǝbum aɓwana.
\q2 Aɓa yilǝmu andǝ lú ka, à gau ɗang.
\q1 À kútì ankwang nǝ kaurǝa;
\q1 à kútì a'im nǝ rǝcandǝa.
\q1 
\v 24 Wun amuna-mamǝna mala Isǝrayila, wu ɓua ace Sawul,
\q2 acemǝnana yì nda ɓwa mǝnana oasǝa wun agir-nggūrǝu mǝɓoarne amǝɓoarsǝne,
\q2 sǝ gilǝkirǝ adaura ma'wun nǝ agir-njengǝlan ngga.
\q1 
\v 25 Akanggǝrang aburana kpana a ban lwa!
\q1 Lú Jonatan na aban nongŋo amur ankono.
\q1 
\v 26 Mǝ nda aɓa bumkiɗikea aceo, mǝ'eambam Jonatan;
\q1 A ndanǝ ɓoaro abanam!
\q1 Earcearǝu mô abanam ngga gir'ndali na kǝ̀rkǝ́r,
\q2 kútì earban mala ɓwama.
\q1 
\v 27 Akanggǝrang aburana kpana,
\q2 sǝ agirbura mala lwa uenaɓà!
\c 2
\s1 À ɗārǝ́ Dauda ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm mala Yahuda
\p 
\v 1 Anzǝm mǝnia ka, Dauda ɗì Yahweh ama, <<Mǝ kya aɓa mwashat atà alá mala Yahuda le?>> Sǝ Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<Kyane.>> Dauda ɗiban ama, <<Ake sǝ mǝ ká?>> Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<A Hebǝron.>>
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Dauda lo wari abanì andǝ amāmí gbal, Ahinoam ɓwama Jezǝril, andǝ Abigiyel mā-lú mala Nabal ɓwama Karmi.
\v 3 Sǝ Dauda yinǝ aburana mǝnana à nda atè ka, koyan ngga andǝ amǝ'ɓala male; sǝ à duki arǝ alá mǝnana aɓa Hebǝron ngga.
\p 
\v 4 Sǝ aburana mala Yahuda yiu a Hebǝron, sǝ à ɗārǝ́ Dauda ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amur ɓala Yahuda. Lang à banggi Dauda ama, <<Aburana mala Jabesh-Gilǝyat na à tsǝklú Sawul ka,>>
\v 5 Dauda tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân nǝ cau aban aburana mala Jabesh-Gilǝyat ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh tsǝka wun bù, ace pěmǝɓoarne mǝnia wu lǝmdǝì Sawul ɓwamǝgule ma'wun, nǝ tsǝkluí ka.
\v 6 Ado ka, ɓǝ̀ Yahweh lǝmdǝa wun earcearǝu male mǝnana kǝ gǝshi raka, andǝ domǝsǝcau male. Sǝ mim gbal ka, mǝ nǝ pàkka wun mǝɓoarne ace gìr mǝnana wu pè ka.
\v 7 Acemani ka, wu dum nǝ rǝcandǝa andǝ mǝsǝkàngkàngŋa, acemǝnana Sawul mǝtala-ɓala ma'wun ngga pàngŋǝ̀nà-lú, sǝ aɓwana mala Yahuda ɗārǝ́nam mǝ duk murǝm amúria.>>
\s1 Kúnɓuàna anre ɓala mala Dauda andǝ ɓala mala Sawul
\p 
\v 8 Sǝama Abna muna-ɓwabura mala Ner, mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'lwa mala Sawul ka, twal Ishboshet muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul sǝ yinǝi a Mahanayim.
\v 9 Tsǝì duk murǝm amur abu-nzali Gilǝyat, andǝ Ashuri, andǝ Jezǝril, andǝ Ifǝrem andǝ Benjami andǝ Isǝrayila kat.
\p 
\v 10 Ishboshet muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul ka, ndanǝ apǝlǝa lumi-ine lang à tsǝì duk murǝm amur Isǝrayila ka, sǝ yì ka pàk apǝlǝa ɓari a buno-murǝm. Sǝ ɓala mala Yahuda ka, kpata Dauda.
\v 11 Sauwa mala bàkú mǝnana Dauda nda murǝm a Hebǝron amur ɓala mala Yahuda ka, apǝlǝa tongno-nong-ɓari andǝ azongŋo tongno-nong-mwashat na.
\p 
\v 12 Abna muna-ɓwabura mala Ner, atārǝia andǝ aburana mala Ishboshet muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul ka, à lo a Mahanayim sǝ à o a Gibiyon.
\v 13 Jowap muna-ɓwabura mala Zeruya\f + \fr 2:13 \fq Zeruya \ft ka ɓwama na, mǝ'nggaula Dauda.\f* andǝ aburana mala Dauda puro sǝ à kya je andǝia a guguri mǝnana a Gibiyon ngga. Nggǝsan mwashat do a buì mala guguri man, sǝ ɓè nggǝsan ngga do a nkaring mala guguri.
\v 14 Abna banggi Jowap ama, <<Ado ka, ɓǝ̀ sǝm tsǝk aɓea alaggana ma'sǝm ɓǝà pur ace munǝo, ɓwa andǝ ɓwa arǝarǝia, a ɓadǝm sǝm.>> Sǝ Jowap bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ à lo.>>
\v 15 Nda à lo, à cam-nǝ-came sǝ à ɓallia; aburana lum-nong-ɓari a buì mala Benjami andǝ Ishboshet muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul, sǝ aburana lum-nong-ɓari a buì mala Dauda.
\v 16 Koyanale ka bwal ɓì a ɓamúrí sǝ zuɓi nkanggari-bum ɓì nǝ byau male, sǝ à kpa nzali à wǔ atārǝia. Nda tsǝa sǝ mǝno yì ban a Gibiyon ngga, à tunǝi ama, Helkat-hazurim ngga.\f + \fr 2:16 \fq Helkat-hazurim \ft ngga ɓālǝi nda <<ɓatuli/nzawara mala akun-byau.>>\f*
\p 
\v 17 Mǝsǝ munǝo bangŋa a pwari mǝno. Aburana mala Dauda gandǝ Abna andǝ aburana mala Isǝrayila.
\v 18 Amuna-burana mala Zeruya tàrú, à nda abanì: Jowap, andǝ Abishai, sǝ Asahel. Asahel ka, mǝɓiki mire na kǝla mbamba a bondo.
\v 19 Asahel pǝrta Abna, ɓinǝ kyang atà bui-mǝli ko mǝnggare, aban pǝrte.
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Abna pǝlǝ mǝsǝi a nzǝmi sǝ na ama, <<A nda le, Asahel?>> Asahel ear ama, <<E, mǝ nda.>>
\v 21 Abna banggi wi ama, <<Kyang atà buo mǝlì ko mǝnggare; gbami mwashat atà alaggana, sǝ wu ak agirbura male arǝì.>> Sǝ Asahel ka, ɗeki pǝrte ɗàng.
\v 22 Nyare Abna sà'arǝ Asahel ama, <<Nying pǝrtam. Kǝa tsǝem ɓǝn wal-luio ɗàng. Ɓǝ̀ ǝn wal-luio ka, lang sǝ mǝ nǝ sǝn mǝ'eambo Jowap a ɓamǝsǝi?>>
\v 23 Sǝ Asahel ka, ɓinǝ kyangye. Nda Abna zuɓi a bumi nǝ tǝta nzo male ka. Nzoe kò kya pur a nzǝmi; Asahel kpa a nzali abanì sǝ wǔ a ɓadǝm Abna. Ɓwa mǝnana kat yiu a ban mǝnana Asahel kpa sǝ wù kam ngga, ɓwe cam gǝs.
\p 
\v 24 Sǝ Jowap andǝ Abishai ka à pyangnǝata Abna. Lang pwari nǝ nggǝ ká kpa ka, à bwal ban mgbangban mala Ammah, tù a ban Giya, a njar ká ɓabondo Gibiyon.
\v 25 Pǝlǝa aɓwana mala Benjami ram rǝia abanɓwáná anzǝm Abna, sǝ à cam amur mgbangban.
\p 
\v 26 Pǝlǝa Abna tunǝ Jowap sǝ ɗì ama, <<Dumǝna púp sǝm nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ wal-lú rǝarǝ sǝm le? A sǝlǝ mbak ama nǝ̀ nggá duk mǝlulle a masǝlǝate? Nǝ̀ sau lang sǝ awu nǝ sà'arǝ aɓwana mô ɓǝà nying pǝrta amǝ'eambia?>>
\v 27 Jowap eari wi ama, <<Kǝla mǝnana Ɓakuli na kam nǝyilǝmu ka, ɓǝ̀ a bangma cau man raka, mbak-kàngkàng aɓwana man pa nǝ̀ vwakibuia arǝ pǝrta amǝ'eambia ɗàng ba dǝmbari.>>
\v 28 Nda Jowap twang njawe, sǝ aburane kat go-gǝs; à lidǝmba nǝ pǝrta Isǝrayila, ko à munǝ ɗǝm ɗàng.
\p 
\v 29 Osso Abna andǝ aburana male gya nǝɓa Araba aɓa dù mǝno kat. À yàlî Nggeasala Jodan, sǝ à lidǝmba nǝ gya aɓa dǝmbari mǝno ba à yi bik Mahanayim.
\p 
\v 30 Lang Jowap nyarǝnì pǝrta Abna ka, ramba amǝ'lwa male pupup abanɓwáná. Sǝni ka, aburana mala Dauda lum-bwamdǝ-tongno-nong-ine andǝ Asahel ka, à pà kàm ɗàng.
\v 31 Sǝama aburana mala Dauda wal-lú aburana mala Benjami gbǝman-tàrú nǝ lumi-tongno-nong-mwashat mǝnana à nda atà Abna ka.
\v 32 Jowap andǝ aburana male twal lú Asahel sǝ à kya tsǝî a ɓembe mala tarrí a Betalami. Pǝlǝa à gya aɓa dù kat sǝ à yi bwal Hebǝron a kwaro-la-ban.
\c 3
\m 
\v 1 Munǝo mǝnana anre ɓala mala Sawul andǝ ɓala mala Dauda ka, tè sauwa. Làkkì mala aɓwana mǝnana à nda atà Dauda ka, lidǝmba nǝ gulo kǝ̀rkǝ́r, sǝ làkkì mala aɓwana mǝnana à nda atà ɓala mala Sawul ka, camarǝ amsǝa.
\s1 Amuna-burana mǝnana à ɓǝlî Dauda a Hebǝron ngga
\r (1 Acau Kpa 3:1-4)
\p 
\v 2 À ɓǝlî Dauda amuna-burana a Hebǝron:
\li1 Muna-dǝmba male nda Amnon, nǝ bu Ahinoam, ɓwama Jezǝril;
\li1 
\v 3 ɓaria muni nda Kileyap, nǝ bu Abigiyel,\f + \fr 3:3 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 25:3-42\xt*\ft .\f* mā-lú mala Nabal, ɓwama Kamel;
\li1 tàruia muni nda Absalom, nǝ bu Ma'aka, ɓoarnsarile Talmai, murǝm Geshur;\f + \fr 3:3 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 1Sam 27:8; 2Sam 13:37-38; 14:32; 15:8\xt*\ft .\f*
\li1 
\v 4 inea muni nda Adonija, nǝ bu Haggit;
\li1 tongnoia muni, nda Shefatiya, nǝ bu Abital;
\li1 
\v 5 tongno-nong-mwashatia muni nda Itǝreyam, nǝ bu Eglah, mālá Dauda.
\m Amuna-burana mǝnia ka, à ɓǝlî Dauda a Hebǝron.
\s1 Abna o atà Dauda
\p 
\v 6 Lang munǝo mǝnana anre ɓala mala Sawul andǝ ɓala mala Dauda lidǝmba ka, Abna camarǝ kumbi ɓamúrì rǝcandǝa kpǝm a ɓala mala Sawul.
\v 7 Sawul ɗiɗyal ka ndanǝ mā-twala mǝnana à tunǝki ama Rizpa, muna-ɓwama mala Ayah ka. Ɓè fara ka, Ishboshet banggi Abna ama, <<Ace mana, sǝ a kúti aban mā-twala mala tárrám?>>
\p 
\v 8 Kara Abna ka, bumi lul kǝ̀rkǝ́r nǝ cau mǝnana Ishboshet bang ngga. Pǝlǝa nyesǝi wi cau ama, <<Mǝ nda ɓamur nvwa a buì mala Yahuda le?\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Ko \fqa A twalam kǝla mǝ nda ɓwa mǝɓane mǝ nǝ mak wun a bù Yahuda le.\f* Twal a tite ba yalung, ǝn lǝmdǝ domǝsǝcau arǝ ɓala mala tarró, Sawul andǝ aɓǝla, andǝ agyajam male. Ən tasǝ wun ɓǝ̀ wu kpa a ɓabu Dauda ɗàng. Kat andǝ amani ka, a tsǝkam-cau-arǝàm mala pàk cauɓikea nǝ ɓwama mǝnia ka!
\v 9 Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli ɓashiam, sǝ yale ɓǝ̀ wal-luem, mim Abna, ɓǝ̀ ǝn pakkì Dauda gìr kǝla mǝnana Yahweh kánbi wi ama nǝ̀ pàkki wi ka, raka.
\v 10 Mǝ nǝ tusǝ domurǝm ɓǝ̀ nying ɓala mala Sawul, sǝ mǝ nǝ tamsǝkusǝ bunomurǝm mala Dauda, amur Isǝrayila andǝ Yahuda, twal a Dan aban ká Biyasheba.>>
\v 11 Sǝ Ishboshet ka, nyare ne Abna kǝ cau ɗǝm ɗang, acemǝnana ɓangciu pàkki wi arǝì.
\p 
\v 12 Pǝlǝa Abna tasǝa amǝ'na-túrbân ɓǝà kyanbi wi aban Dauda nǝ cau ama, <<Nzali ka, mala yana ɗe? Kùrcau nǝ mim, sǝ mǝ nǝ bwalo kàm, ace yinǝ Isǝrayila kat a bano.>>
\p 
\v 13 Pǝlǝa Dauda bang ama, <<Yàwá, mǝ nǝ kùrcau sǝnǝ we, sǝama, ǝn nggǝ earce gìr mwashat nǝ we: A pà wunǝ sǝn ɓamǝsǝàm ɗàng sheɓǝ̀ we, atà dǝmbe ka, a yinanǝ Mikal, muna-ɓwama mala Sawul, lang awu nǝ yiu a sǝnam ngga.>>
\p 
\v 14 Pǝlǝa Dauda tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aban Ishboshet, muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul, ɓǝà banggi wi ama, <<Pam māmám, yì Mikal, mǝnana ǝn pur'amuri mǝ alí nǝ nggú-ɓata amǝ'Filisti gbǝman-mwashat ka.>>\f + \fr 3:14 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 18:20-25\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 15 Anggo, Ishboshet túrban sǝ à ak Mikal arǝ burí, Paltiyel, muna-ɓwabura mala Layish.
\v 16 Kat andǝ amani anggo ka, burí o atè, camarǝ ɓua aceì, amur njar kat aban ká ɗār a Bahurim. Pǝlǝa Abna banggi wi ama, <<Nyare o!>> Sǝ nyare o.
\p 
\v 17 Pǝlǝa Abna nacau nǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Isǝrayila ama, <<Banì sauwuna adyan, mana wu kǝ earce ama, wun nǝ̀ tsǝk Dauda ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm ma'wun ngga.
\v 18 Ado ka, wu pè wi, ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm! Yahweh ka panacau aban Dauda ama, <Nǝ bu guro mem Dauda, sǝ mǝ nǝ amsǝ aɓwana mem, Isǝrayila, a bù amǝ'Filisti sǝ a bù aɓia-mǝbura kat.> >>
\p 
\v 19 Pǝlǝa Abna nacau nǝ amǝ'tàu mala Benjami. Sǝ wari a Hebǝron, ace banggi Dauda gìr mǝnana kat Isǝrayila andǝ ɓala mala Benjami puppup earǝnace ama à nǝ̀ pàk ka.
\p 
\v 20 Lang Abna andǝ aburana male lumi-ɓari atè yiu aban Dauda a Hebǝron ngga, Dauda pak girlina-nàtà ace Abna andǝ aburana mǝnana à yiu atè ka.
\v 21 Pǝlǝa Abna banggi Dauda ama, <<Earam, ɓǝ̀ ǝn o mǝ kya ram Isǝrayila kat, ace ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kùrcau nǝ we, sǝ ace mǝnana wu yálmúr gìr mǝnana kat ɓabumo earkice ka.>> Nda Dauda tasǝ Abna o aɓa rǝpwala ka.
\s1 Jowap wal-lú Abna
\p 
\v 22 Zuku ka, aburana mala Dauda andǝ Jowap nyarǝnì ban mǝnana à wari kam ace tǝlliban ngga, sǝ à yinǝ gǝna-lwa kpǝm a buia. Sǝ Abna ka, pà a ban Dauda a Hebǝron ɗàng, acemǝnana Dauda tasǝni, umǝna aɓa rǝpwala.
\v 23 Lang Jowap, andǝ amǝ'lwa mǝnana kat atè à yi bwalǝna ka, aɓwana banggi Jowap ama, <<Abna, muna-ɓwabura mala Ner, yiu aban murǝm, sǝ murǝm ɗekini ɓǝ̀ o, sǝ umǝna aɓa rǝpwala.>>
\p 
\v 24 Pǝlǝa Jowap wari aban murǝm, sǝ ɗì ama, <<Mana mǝnia a pê ka? Abna yiu a bano! Palang sǝ a ɗeki o? Sǝ ado ka nyarǝna umǝna!
\v 25 We ka, a súrǝ́nà rǝ Abna, muna-ɓwabura mala Ner; yiu male ka, nda ace swárkiǒ, sǝ ɓǝ̀ súrǝ̀ puro mô andǝ nyare mô, sǝ ɓǝ̀ súrǝ̀ gir mǝnana kat a pakkiyi ka.>>
\p 
\v 26 Jowap pǝlǝa nying ban Dauda, sǝ tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân atà Abna, ama ɓǝà banggi wi ɓǝ̀ nyare. À kya kumi a ban tūli-mùr mǝnana a Sirah ka, sǝ à nyesǝì à yinǝi. (Sǝ Dauda ka, sǝlǝce gìrnî ɗàng.)
\v 27 Lang Abna nyarǝna yina a Hebǝron ngga, Jowap warinǝi aɓa ɓè muna kurǝm a kún nggea-là, kǝla nǝ̀ nacau nǝi, kǝ yia ɓari. Sǝ abanì ka, Jowap kara soa Abna nǝ byau a bumi, wal-luí, ace mbwegìr akúnì nkila mala mǝ'eambi Asahel.
\p 
\v 28 Nǝnzǝ́mò, lang Dauda okce mǝnia yì gìr ka, bang ama, <<Mim sǝnǝ nzali domurǝm mem, aɓadǝm Yahweh tàtǝ́k ka, bù sǝm pà aɓa cau mala sukki nkila mala Abna muna-ɓwabura mala Ner ɗàng.
\v 29 Ɓǝ̀ bafe mala nkila male sulǝ a ɓamur Jowap sǝ amur ɓala mala tárrí kat! Ɓǝ̀ ɓala mala Jowap ɓǝkǝa ɗwanyi ɓwa mǝnana ndanǝ penye mana mùrgìr kǝ sur kam, ko ndanǝ kwánó nggû,\f + \fr 3:29 \fq kwánó nggû \ft ko ɓè kwánó mǝɓike mala nggū rǝu mana kǝ ak rǝ ɓwa ka.\f* ko muna-ɓwabura mǝnana nggilung-ɓwa na, ko mǝnana à wal-luí nǝ nggeabyau, ko kǝ paktǝla girlina ka ɗàng.>>
\p 
\v 30 (Jowap andǝ mǝ'eambi Abishai ka, à wal-lú Abna acemǝnana, yì na mǝnana wal-lú mǝ'eambia Asahel, a kun-munǝo a Gibiyon ngga.)
\s1 Dauda ɓua-lú Abna
\p 
\v 31 Pǝlǝa Dauda banggi Jowap andǝ aɓwana mana kat andǝi ka, ama, <<Wu sàngi agir-nggūrǝu ma'wun, wu oasǝ anggubyau-doatú\f + \fr 3:31 \fq anggubyau-doatú \ft ko <<asanginagìr>>\f* arǝ wun, sǝ wu ɓua aɓadǝm Abna.>> Murǝm Dauda nǝ ɓamuri ka, gya anzǝm aɓwana mana à twal kpamgbang-lú ka.
\p 
\v 32 Pǝlǝa à tsǝk-lú Abna a Hebǝron; murǝm loasǝ gì ɓua a ɓembe mala Abna. Sǝ aɓwana kat ɓua Abna.
\p 
\v 33 Pǝlǝa murǝm tù mǝnia yì nggyal keban ngga, amur Abna, ama:
\q1 Ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ Abna wǔ kǝla wù mala gǝmɓwa le?
\q2 
\v 34 À tà ka abuo ɗàng,
\q2 sǝ akusǝo pà aɓa nsolo ɗang.
\q1 Kǝla mǝnana ɓwabura nǝ̀ kpa aɓadǝm amǝ'ɓealɓikea ka, anggo sǝ a kpa.
\m Aɓwe kat ɓua aceì ɗǝm.
\p 
\v 35 Pǝlǝa aɓwe yiu aban Dauda, sǝ à ɓuakiarǝi ɓǝ̀ lì girlina sǝ pwari na piu a kuli. Sǝ Dauda ka, kángìr ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli ɓashiam, yale ɓǝ̀ wal-luem ɓǝ̀ ǝn tsǝk girlina ko ɓè kǝgir a kunam sǝ pwari kpa ka!>>
\v 36 Sǝ aɓwana kat falǝnǝ mǝnia ka, sǝ gìrnî pwasǝbumia. Yale koya gìr murǝm pè ka, pwasǝbum aɓwe kat.
\v 37 Nda aɓwana kat andǝ Isǝrayila kat yi bwalte, a pwari mǝno ka, ama, murǝm ngga, buì pà aɓa wal-lú Abna, muna-ɓwabura mala Ner ɗàng.
\p 
\v 38 Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi amǝ'túró male ama, <<Wu sǝlǝ mbak ama, ɓwamǝgule nggea ɓwabura mǝcandǝe kpana yalung a Isǝrayila?
\v 39 Yalung ngga, rǝàm-wukina, kat andǝ amani ama, mǝ nda murǝm mana à ɗārǝí ka. Aburana mǝnia, yià amuna mala Zeruya ka, à dupam nǝ kwanô kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh mbwe mǝtúró-ɓikea akúnì gìr mǝnana kārǝa arǝ ɓealɓikea male ka!>>
\c 4
\s1 À wal-lú Ishboshet
\p 
\v 1 Lang Ishboshet, muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul ongŋǝna ama, Abna wuna a Hebǝron ngga, ɓabumi ɓunggio, sǝ Isǝrayila kat ka, múrí-kàrì.
\v 2 A bàkú mǝno ka, muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul, yì Ishboshet ka, ndanǝ aburana ɓari mǝnana à nda ka amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amur anggǝsan mala amǝ'lwa ace kánǝ tǝlliban ngga. Mwashat ateà ka, lullǝi ama, Baanah, sǝ ɓè ka, lullǝi ama, Rekap; yia mǝnia ka, amuna-burana mala Rimon, ɓwa Beerot a tàu mala Benjami na. (Beerot ka à ɓalli aɓa bu-nzali Benjami,
\v 3 acemǝnana aɓwana mala Beerot ka, à ɓangŋa à nying Gittem, sǝ à yi do kǝla abǝri mǝnana à yiu ace dola ka, sǝ à nda kam ba yalung.)
\p 
\v 4 Jonatan, muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul ka, ndanǝ muna-ɓwabura, mǝnana gbakǝri arǝ akusǝi ka. Yì ka, ndanǝ apǝlǝa tongno, sǝ cau pur a Jezǝril ama à walna Sawul andǝ Jonatan a munǝo. Mǝ'iulǝe twali ɓangŋa nǝ̀ umnǝi akaurǝa, sǝama lang nda aban ɓangŋa nǝ̀ o akaurǝa ka, kara muna kpa, nda duk gbakǝre ka. Lullǝi nda Mefiboshet.
\p 
\v 5 Rekap andǝ Baanah, amuna-burana mala Rimon, ɓwa Beerot ka, à lo aban ká a ɓala mala Ishboshet. À kya bik banì nǝ pwarizǝkya, lang yì ka, ndaban nongŋo ace usǝlǝo mala pwarizǝkya ka.
\v 6 Ɓwama mǝ'yál kunɓala ka nda aban nyaulǝki mǝssa-alkama; ntulo-ayiki sǝ koa ntulo; nda Rekap andǝ mǝ'eambi yi kúti zàng ngga.\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Gk: Ib \fqa Pǝlǝa à kùtí aɓa ɓala, kǝla à nǝ̀ ɗàrǝ́ mǝssa-alkama, sǝ à zuɓi a bumi. Pǝlǝa Rekap andǝ mǝ'eambi Baanah, à ɓangŋa à o.\f*
\p 
\v 7 Lang à kutina aɓa ɓala ka, à kum Ishboshet, ndaban nongŋo amur gyangŋan-nongŋo aɓa ndà-nongŋo male. À zuɓi, à wal-luí, sǝ à kasǝ ɓamúrí. Pǝlǝa à twal ɓamúrí sǝ à gingnǝi nǝ njar Araba dùkkù-dúkkú,
\v 8 sǝ à yinǝ ɓamur Ishboshet aban Dauda a Hebǝron. Sǝ à banggi murǝm ama, <<Ɓamur Ishboshet nia ka, yì muna-ɓwabura mala Sawul, ɓiomǝbura, mǝnana alta yilǝmo ka; Yahweh mbwenî ɓwamǝgule mem, yì murǝm akúnì, amur Sawul andǝ nggurkwar male.>>
\p 
\v 9 Sǝama Dauda nyesǝî Rekap andǝ mǝ'eambi Baanah, amuna-burana mala Rimon cau ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam, mǝnana akmúr yilǝmem aɓa koya tanni mana kumam ngga,
\v 10 lang ɓeɓwa yiu a Zikǝlag sǝ banggam ama, <Sawul wuna ka,> ɓwê twali ama, ndarǝ yinǝàm nǝ bǝsacau mǝɓoarne. Sǝama ǝn bwal ɓwenî, ǝn wal-luí. Mǝno ka, nda tangnakusǝu mana ǝn pe wi ace bǝsacau male ka!
\v 11 Sǝ acemǝnana wun aburana amǝɓealɓike, wu walna-lú mǝ'kunpwasǝa a ɓala male, sǝ amur gyangŋan-nongŋo male ka, mǝ nǝ pàkka wun gìr mǝnana ɓike-kútìbanì ka. Pà mǝ nǝ ɗice nkile a bù wun, sǝ mǝ nǝ kiɗiki wun a ɓanza re?>>
\p 
\v 12 Nda Dauda, pè alaggana male nzongcau, sǝ à wal-luia ka. À kasǝki abuia andǝ akusǝia, sǝ à gyarkia tù a ban guguri mǝnana a Hebǝron ngga. Sǝama ɓamur Ishboshet ka, à twali à kya tsǝî a ɓembe-ɓa-tali mala Abna, a Hebǝron.
\c 5
\s1 Dauda duk murǝm Isǝrayila
\r (1 Acau Kpa 11:1-3)
\p 
\v 1 Pǝlǝa atau mala Isǝrayila kat yiu aban Dauda a Hebǝron, sǝ à ne wi ama, <<Sǝni, sǝm nda ka nkiliò andǝ nyamo.
\v 2 Ɗiɗyal mǝnana Sawul nda murǝm amur sǝm ngga, a ndà ɓwamǝgule amur amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila. Sǝ Yahweh banggo ama, <Awu nǝ duk mǝ'yál aɓwana mem Isǝrayila, sǝ awu nǝ duk murǝm amur Isǝrayila.> >>
\p 
\v 3 Akanó a Hebǝron Murǝm Dauda kùrcau nǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Isǝrayila kat a ɓadǝm Yahweh lang à yina aban murǝm ngga. À ɗārǝ́ Dauda nǝ mùrú olif ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amur Isǝrayila.
\v 4 Dauda ka, ndanǝ apǝlǝa lumi-tàrú a ɓanza sǝ tita yálmúrû. Pàk apǝlǝa lumi-ine a buno-murǝm.
\v 5 A Hebǝron ngga pàk apǝlǝa tongno-nong-ɓari nǝ azongŋo tongno-nong-mwashat nda murǝm amur Yahuda, sǝ a Urǝshalima ka, pàk apǝlǝa lumi-tàrú nǝ mǝsǝì tàrú nda murǝm amur Isǝrayila kat andǝ Yahuda.
\s1 Dauda lì Urǝshalima a lwa
\r (1 Acau Kpa 11:4-9; 14:1-2)
\p 
\v 6 Pǝlǝa murǝm lo andǝ aburana male sǝ à wari a Urǝshalima ace kánǝ lwa arǝ amǝ'Jebus, yì aɓwana mǝnana à nda à tita do a mǝno yì là ɗiɗyal sǝ à ndakam ngga. Amǝ'Jebus sà'arǝ Dauda ama, <<A pà nǝ kútí kani ɗang! Nggearǝ ante andǝ gbakǝre ma'sǝm kārǝ́na à nǝ̀ mgbalio.>> Yia amǝ'Jebus ka à kǝ twali ama Dauda pà nǝ̀ gandǝ kúti kano nǝ̀ ak là arǝia ɗàng, nda tsǝa sǝ à bang anggo ka.
\v 7 Sǝ kat andǝ amani ka, Dauda ak ban-mǝcandǝe mala Siyona mǝnana ado à kǝ tunǝi ama Nggea-là mala Dauda ka.
\v 8 A pwari mǝno ka Dauda bang ama, <<Ɓwa mǝnana kat nǝ̀ kánǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'Jebus ka, dumǝna púp nǝ̀ kàr nǝ njar-tǝta'nzali mala mùr sǝ nǝ̀ bik ban amǝno yì <agbakǝre andǝ ante,> mǝnana à nda ka aɓibura mala Dauda ka.>> Acemani ka, à bang ama, agbakǝre andǝ ante pa nǝ kùtí a \f + \fr 5:8 \fq ɓalae \ft ko \fqa ɓala mala Yahweh.\f*ɓalae ɗàng.
\p 
\v 9 Anggo sǝ Dauda nyesǝ ban-mǝcandǝe pǝlǝ là do male, sǝ tunǝi ama Nggea-là mala Dauda. Sǝ Dauda ɓakiaɓa kàrì banì, tite a ban Millo aban ká a ɓalǝu.
\v 10 Anggo sǝ Dauda lidǝmba nǝ gulo aɓa rǝcandǝa mala yálban, acemǝnana Yahweh Ɓakuli mǝnana Karban kat nǝ Gulo ka nda atè.
\p 
\v 11 Hiram, Murǝm mala nzali Taya tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aban Dauda, nǝ agbǝlang nggun-seda, andǝ amǝ'túró shàr-nggun andǝ gballi-nggun, andǝ amǝ'túró ɓun-tali ace ɓak sheran, sǝ à ɓakkî Dauda ɓala.
\v 12 Nda Dauda yi sǝlǝ ama Yahweh dumsǝni mbak-kàngkàng yì nda murǝm amur Isǝrayila, sǝ ɗǝm ngga Yahweh hangǝlina domurǝm male atàcau mala aɓwana male Isǝrayila.
\p 
\v 13 Anzǝm mǝnana Dauda tùrǝ́nǝì Hebǝron sǝ yina a Urǝshalima ka, twalki amā-twala sǝ alki amamǝna amur amǝnana ndanǝia ka, sǝ à ɓǝlî Dauda amuna-burana andǝ amuna-mamǝna amur amǝnana ndanǝia ka.
\v 14 Amǝnia ka à nda ka alullǝ amuna-burana mala Dauda mǝnana à ɓǝlia a Urǝshalima ka: Shamuwa, andǝ Shobap, andǝ Natan, andǝ Solomon,
\v 15 andǝ Ibǝhar, andǝ Elishuwa, andǝ Nefeg, andǝ Jafiya,
\v 16 andǝ Elishama, andǝ Eliyada, sǝ Elifelet.
\s1 Dauda munǝo andǝ amǝ'Filisti
\r (1 Acau Kpa 14:8-17)
\p 
\v 17 Lang amǝ'Filisti ok ama à ɗārǝ́na Dauda nda murǝm amur Isǝrayila ka, amǝ'Filisti kat o a alta Dauda ace gbamì. Sǝama Dauda okce, nda sulǝo wari aɓa kanggǝrang-ban ngga.
\v 18 Adyan ngga amǝ'Filisti yiu, sǝ à mesǝ aɓa Ɓangŋaban Refayim.
\v 19 Pǝlǝa Dauda alta nê mala Yahweh ama, <<Mǝ kyan nǝ munǝo arǝ amǝ'Filisti le? Awu nǝ tasǝia aɓa buam le?>> Sǝ Yahweh earî Dauda ama, <<E, kyane. Mbak-kàngkàng mǝ nǝ tasǝ amǝ'Filisti aɓa buo.>>
\p 
\v 20 Nda Dauda wari a Baal-perazim sǝ gandǝ amǝ'Filisti abanì; sǝ bang ama, <<Yahweh ar aɓalǝ aɓiam-mǝbura a ɓadǝmbam kǝla ara mala mùrɓangŋa.>> Acemani ka, tunǝ lullǝ banì ama Baal-perazim.\f + \fr 5:20 \fq Baal-perazim \ft ngga ɓālǝi nda <<Ɓwamǝgule mǝnana kǝ ar ban, ko kǝ san ban ngga.>>\f*
\v 21 Amǝ'Filisti nying aɓǝ̀nzál malea a banì, sǝ Dauda andǝ aburana male pwania à umnǝia.
\p 
\v 22 Amǝ'Filisti yiu ɗǝm, sǝ à yi mesǝ aɓa Ɓangŋaban Refayim.
\v 23 Sǝ lang Dauda ɗìbancau a ban Yahweh ka, Yahweh banggi wi ama, <<A pa wunǝ ká arǝia [kporong] ɗàng. A kún mani ka, kàr nǝnzǝmia sǝ wu yiu arǝia nǝ ɓadǝm anggun nkǝling-kǝling.
\v 24 Sǝ lang awu nǝ ok gì gya mala twalkusǝu-anzǝmarǝia ani a ɓong anggun nkǝling-kǝling ngga, gbaratè akaurǝa, acemǝnana anggo ka, Yahweh angŋǝ́nò-dǝmba purna a ɓadǝmbo ace ká wàl amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti.>>
\v 25 Nda Dauda pàk gìrnî kǝla mǝnana Yahweh tsǝki wi nzongcau ka, wàl amǝ'Filisti tite a Gibiyon aban ká ɗār a Geza.
\c 6
\s1 Dauda yinǝ Akwati Kùrcau a Urǝshalima
\r (1 Acau Kpa 13:1-14; 15:1--16:3,43)
\p 
\v 1 Dauda nyare ramba aburana mala Isǝrayila mǝnana à tarkia ka kat abanɓwáná, aɓwana á-lumi-tàrú.
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Dauda lo andǝ aburana mǝnana kat à nda atè ka, sǝ à wari a Baala\f + \fr 6:2 \fq Baala \ft Mǝnia ka ɓè lullǝu na ace Kiriat-Jarim.\f* aɓa bu-nzali Yahuda, ace twal Akwati Kùrcau a ban mǝno, à nǝ̀ yinǝi, yì Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli, mǝnana à tunǝi nǝ Lullǝì, nggearǝ lullǝ Yahweh, Mǝtala Abangŋo, mǝnana do amur bunomurǝm a nre ka acerup amur Akwatinî ka.
\v 3 À tamsǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli amur bǝsa keke-ndá sǝ à pur nǝi a ɓala mala Aminadap, mǝnana nda amur mgbangban ngga. Uzza andǝ Ahiyo, amuna-burana mala Aminadap ka à nda à kǝ gingnǝ bǝsa keke-ndê ka.
\v 4 À pur nǝi nǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli amurí, a ɓala mala Aminadap, mǝnana nda amur mgbangban ngga. Ahiyo na aban gya a ɓadǝm Akwatini.
\v 5 Sǝ Dauda andǝ ɓala Isǝrayila kat ka, à ndaban pakkiɗire, à kǝ yalke aɓadǝm Yahweh, nǝ nggyal andǝ walki adànà andǝ azangŋan, andǝ akarata-bu, andǝ awassak, andǝ akpaksha.
\p 
\v 6 Sǝama lang à yina a katǝra mala Nakon ngga, ndǎ annda, pǝlǝa Uzza lǝmdǝ buì bwal Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli [ace mǝnana ɓǝkǝa kpa raka.]
\v 7 Kara bumlulla mala Yahweh earke arǝ Uzza, sǝ Ɓakuli koè túrí a nzali a banì atàcau mala mǝnia yì yàl-nzong ngga. Nda Uzza wù akǝ banì a nkanggari Akwati mala Ɓakuli ka.
\v 8 Sǝ bum Dauda lúllô ace ara mala bumlulla mala Yahweh amur Uzza; nda tunǝ lullǝ banì ama Perez Uzza,\f + \fr 6:8 \fq Perez Uzza \ft ka ɓalǝi nda <<Ara arǝ Uzza.>>\f* sǝ anggo sǝ à kǝ tunǝi piu ba yalung ngga.
\p 
\v 9 Ɓangciu pàkkî Dauda arǝ Yahweh a pwari mǝno ka, sǝ bang ama, <<Lang sǝ Akwati mala Yahweh nǝ̀ yiu abanam?>>
\v 10 Dauda eare nǝ̀ yinǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh aɓa Nggea-là mala Dauda ɗàng; a kún mani ka kàrnǝi a ɓala mala Obed-Edom ɓwa'Gitti.
\v 11 Nda Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh ue a ɓala mala Obed-Edom azongŋo tàrú, sǝ Yahweh tsǝkî Obed-Edom bù andǝ amǝ'ɓala male kat.
\p 
\v 12 Cau yiu aban Dauda ama, <<Yahweh tsǝngŋǝ́nì ɓala mala Obed-Edom bù andǝ gir mǝnana kat ndanǝi ka, atàcau mala Akwati mala Ɓakuli.>> Nda Dauda wario kya twal Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli a ɓala mala Obed-Edom, sǝ yinǝi a Nggea-là mala Dauda nǝ banɓoarnado ka.
\v 13 Lang aburana mana à kǝ twal Akwati mala Yahweh twalna kusǝia tongno-nong-mwashat ka, Dauda pà gir'nkila nǝ jamnda andǝ muna-ndǎ mǝ'nyane.
\v 14 Dauda oasǝ efot\f + \fr 6:14 \fq efot \ft ka daura-múrɓì mala adaura-pǝris na. Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pur 28:4-28; 1Sam 2:18\xt*\ft .\f* mala nggubyau linǝn arǝì sǝ ndaban ta'nggwam nǝ rǝcandǝa male kat aɓadǝm Yahweh.
\v 15 Anggo sǝ Dauda andǝ ɓala Isǝrayila kat yinǝ Akwati mala Yahweh, nǝ ɓuà-gāwàn andǝ twang anjawe.
\p 
\v 16 Sǝ lang à ndaban kúti nǝ Akwati mala Yahweh aɓa Nggea-là mala Dauda ka, Mikal, ɓoarnsarile Sawul sǝnban a mǝsǝkurǝm. Sǝ lang sǝn Murǝm Dauda aban yalke sǝ kǝ ta'nggwam a ɓadǝm Yahweh ka, kara ɓǝsǝki Dauda a ɓabumi.
\p 
\v 17 À kùtí nǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh sǝ à kya tamsǝi a ban male, aɓa tara mǝnana à loasǝi aceì ka; sǝ Dauda pāki apagir mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ apagir mala dotarǝu aɓadǝm Yahweh.
\v 18 Anzǝm mǝnana Dauda malna pāki apagir mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ apagir mala dotarǝu ka, tsǝkî aɓwana bù aɓa lullǝ Yahweh, Mǝtala Abangŋo.
\v 19 Sǝ gakì aɓwe kat, aɓa ɓwabundǝa mala Isǝrayila puppup, bǝredi, andǝ nyama, andǝ kyak mala dabino, andǝ kyak mala ɓǝla-anap mǝ'ime; pè koyan ngga kāmbe, aburana andǝ amamǝna kat. Anzǝm mǝno ka aɓwana mesǝ kat, sǝ koyan ngga nyar a ɓala male.
\p 
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Dauda nyare nǝ̀ ká a ɓala ace tsǝkî amǝ'ɓala male bù. Sǝama [māmí] Mikal muna-ɓwama mala Sawul puro nǝ̀ nggá kúllì, sǝ bang ama, <<Ɓafo yalung ngga murǝm Isǝrayila pànî ɓamúrì gulo kpana-kpana, mǝnana swár agir'nggūrǝì sǝ pur nǝ ɓarǝì aɓa ɗwanyi kǝsǝkya, a mǝsǝ aguro male, aburana andǝ amamǝna, kǝla mǝnana mwashat atà aburana mǝɓane kǝ pak ka!>>
\p 
\v 21 Pǝlǝa Dauda earî Mikal ama, <<Mǝ nda [aban ta'nggwam] aɓadǝm Yahweh, mǝnana nying tárró andǝ ɓala male kat sǝ twalam, nyesǝam mǝ duk mǝdǝmba amur Isǝrayila aɓwana mala Yahweh ka. Acemani ka, mǝ nǝ pakkiɗire aɓadǝm Yahweh.
\v 22 Mǝ nǝ tsǝk ɓamúràm aɓa kǝsǝkya mǝnana kútì mǝno ka, sǝ mǝ nǝ dum nǝ kyauwikiban a mǝsǝàm. Sǝama a mǝsǝ aguro amamǝna mǝno a bangcea ka, mǝ nǝ dum nǝ gulo!>>
\v 23 Nda Mikal, muna-ɓwama mala Sawul ue nkombi na aɓa do-yilǝmu male kat.
\c 7
\s1 Yahweh pàcau aban Dauda
\r (1 Acau Kpa 17:1-15)
\p 
\v 1 Murǝm Dauda ka, Yahweh pe wi usǝlǝo, yállí arǝ aɓi-mǝbura mǝnana kat à gumbǝli ka, sǝ yi do a ɓala male.
\v 2 Pǝlǝa murǝm ne Natan mǝɓangnǝa ama, <<Sǝni, mǝ ndya ǝn do a ɓala mǝnana à ɓè nǝ nggun-seda\f + \fr 7:2 \fq nggun-seda \ft ko \fq nggun mǝɓoarjami \f* ka, sǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Yahweh ka nda kano a gumli.>>
\p 
\v 3 Natan earî murǝm ama, <<Pàk gìr mǝnana kat a ndanǝi a ɓabumo ka, acemǝnana Yahweh na atò.>>
\p 
\v 4 Sǝama àkǝ̀ dù mǝno ka Yahweh ne Natan ama:
\pi1 
\v 5 <<Kyane kya ne guro mem Dauda ama, <Mǝnia ka nda cau mala Yahweh: A nda mǝnana awu nǝ ɓakkam ɓala mǝ duk kam ngga le?
\v 6 Twal a pwarian mǝnana ǝn pusǝ amǝ Isǝrayila a Masar bà yalung ngga, ǝn duk ma aɓa ɓekǝ ɓala ɗàng. Ən nggǝ turki nǝ turkio arǝ abân, aɓa gumli kǝla ban-do mem.
\v 7 Arǝ abân mǝnana kat ǝn gingnǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat kàm ngga, ǝn ɓua nǝ kǝ ɓwa atà aɓwana-mǝgule mǝnana ǝn twalia ace yál aɓwana mem amǝ Isǝrayila ka ama, <<Ace mana sǝ wu ɓakkam ɓala nǝ nggun-seda raka>>le?>
\pi1 
\v 8 <<Acemani ka, banggi guro mem Dauda ama: <Mǝnia ka nda cau mǝnana Yahweh Mǝtala Abangŋo kǝ bang ngga: Ən twalo a ban yál-agir a bondo, a ban gyata anzur andǝ ambul, sǝ ǝn nyesǝo a pǝlǝ mǝgulo amur aɓwana mem Isǝrayila.
\v 9 Ban mǝnana kat a wari kam ngga, mǝ nda atò, sǝ ǝn twalta aɓio-amǝbura kat a ɓadǝmbo. Ado ka mǝ nǝ tsǝk lullǝo nǝ̀ zǝ́kí kpǝm, kǝla mala aɓwana amǝgulke mala ɓanza.
\v 10 Mǝ nǝ kumbi aɓwana mem Isǝrayila ban-do, sǝ mǝ nǝ dumsǝia kàm, ace mǝnana ɓǝà do a nzali mǝnana malea na ka, sǝ kǝ ɓwa pà nǝ̀ zorǝia ɗǝm ɗàng. Aɓwana amǝɓealɓike pà nǝ̀ paria ɗǝm, kǝla mǝnana à pangnǝia ɗiɗyal,
\v 11 tite arǝ apǝlǝa mǝnana ǝn twal akasǝla amur aɓwana mem Isǝrayila ka ɗàng. Sǝ mǝ nǝ po usǝlǝo arǝ aɓio-amǝbura. Mim Yahweh ǝn nggǝ nô ama, nǝnggearǝam, mǝ nǝ tsǝo nggurkwar mò ɓǝ̀ duk ɓala-murǝm.
\v 12 Lang a yi wuna, à tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nó atà akeô ka, mǝ nǝ loasǝ mwashat atà amǝkeo, mǝnana nǝ̀ pùr a tǝrto ka, ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm a buno mô, sǝ mǝ nǝ tsǝk domurǝm male ɓǝ̀ cam nǝ rǝcandǝa.
\v 13 Yì nda ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ ɓakkam ɓala, ace lullǝam ngga. Sǝ buno-murǝm mala domurǝm male ka, mǝ nǝ kwákítè nǝ̀ cam kàngkàng, málá male pà kàm ɗàng.
\v 14 Mǝ nǝ duk tárrû abaní, sǝ yì ka nǝ̀ duk munem. Ɓǝ̀ pàk cauɓikea ka, mǝ nǝ gilǝki, mǝ nǝ kwarkiri nǝ nkamso, kǝla mǝnana koya tárrú nǝ̀ pàngnǝ muni ka.
\v 15 Sǝ pěmǝɓoarne aɓa earcearǝu mem mana kǝ dǝurǝ raka, pà nǝ̀ nyingte, kǝla mǝnana ǝn twali arǝ Sawul ka ɗàng, yì Sawul mǝnana ǝn pusǝì ace mǝnana wu duk murǝm ngga.
\v 16 Ɓala mò andǝ domurǝm mò ka, à nǝ̀ lidǝmba a ɓadǝmbam, tè pà nǝ̀ mal ɗang, sǝ buno-murǝm mò ka, nǝ̀ cam kàngkàng masǝlǝate pà kàm ɗàng.> >>
\p 
\v 17 Natan banggi Dauda acau mǝnia ka kat kǝla mǝnana à lǝmdǝì wi aɓa sǝna mǝnia kat ka.
\s1 Hiwi yàwá mala Dauda
\p 
\v 18 Pǝlǝa Murǝm Dauda wario sǝ kya do aɓadǝm Yahweh, sǝ bang ama:
\pi1 <<Mǝ nda yana, sǝ mana nda ɓala mem, mǝnana We Mǝtalabangŋo Ɓakuli, a pakki agir mǝnia kat acem ngga?
\v 19 Sǝ kat andǝ amani ka, mǝno a mǝsǝo, We Mǝtalabangŋo Ɓakuli ka, gìr mǝ kyauwe na, acemǝnana a nyare a nacau amur ɓala mem, mim guro mò, amur gìr mǝnana awu nǝ̀ pè, arǝ anza mǝnana à nǝ̀ yiu kuko ka. Anggo sǝ a kǝ pangnǝ aɓwapǝndǝa kat le, We Mǝtalabangŋo Ɓakuli?
\v 20 Mana ɗǝm mim Dauda, mǝ nǝ gandǝ banggo? A súrǝ́nà yan nda mim, guro mò, We Mǝtalabangŋo Yahweh.
\v 21 Nda atàcau mala pacau mò, sǝ aɓa kpata kàne mò sǝ a pàk mǝnia yì gìr mǝgule ka, sǝ a lǝmdǝí abanam mim guro mò, ace mǝnana mǝ sǝlǝce ka.
\v 22 Acemani ka, gulo ka mona, We Mǝtalabangŋo Yahweh! Kǝ ɓwa pà kàm kǝla we ɗàng, sǝ kǝ Ɓakuli pa kàm ɗàng she we, kǝla mǝnana sǝm oè nǝ kir sǝm ngga!
\v 23 Ya nzali mala aɓwapǝndǝa na kam mwashat a ɓanza kǝla aɓwana mô Isǝrayila, mǝnana We Ɓakuli malea a pur ace ká akmúria kǝla aɓwana ace ɓamúrò, sǝ ace kumbì ɓamúrò lullǝu ka? A pàkki agir mǝgulke andǝ agir kàrmúrû acea, nǝ pǝr anzali mala aɓwapǝndǝa andǝ aɓakuli malea a ɓadǝmbia, yia aɓwana mô mǝnana a akmúria a Masar ka.\f + \fr 7:23 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 4:32-38\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 24 A tsǝk Isǝrayila ɓǝ̀ duk aɓwana mô tàtǝ́k, sǝ We Yahweh ka a dumǝna Ɓakuli malea.\f + \fr 7:24 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 6:7; Nggur 26:18\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 25 Sǝ adyan ngga, We Yahweh Ɓakuli, cau mǝnana a ne amuram mim guro mò sǝ amur ɓala mem ngga, lùmsǝì ɓǝ̀ kum came tàtǝ́k. Pè kǝla mǝnana a ne ka,
\v 26 ace mǝnana lullǝo ɓǝ̀ dum nǝ gulo tàtǝ́k ka. Sǝ aɓwana nǝ̀ bang ama, <Yahweh, Mǝtala Abangŋo, nda Ɓakuli amur Isǝrayila!> Sǝ ɓala mala guro mò, mim Dauda ka ɓǝ̀ lidǝmba aɓadǝmbo tàtǝ́k,
\v 27 acemǝnana We Yahweh mǝnana a Karban Kat nǝ Gulo, yì Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila ka, a lǝmdǝni abanam, mim guro mò ama, awu nǝ ɓakkâm ɓala.\f + \fr 7:27 \fq awu nǝ ɓakkâm ɓala \ft ko \fqa awu nǝ tsǝk amunem andǝ amǝ'kem à nǝ̀ duk amurǝma.\f* Nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ mim guro mò ka, ǝn kum mǝsǝkàngkàngŋa mala pakhiwi a bano ani ka.
\v 28 Ado ka, We Yahweh Ɓakuli, a nda Ɓakuli, sǝ acau mò ka mǝsǝcau na. A panacau mala mǝnia yì gìr mǝɓoarne ka abanam, mim guro mò.
\v 29 Acemani ka, ɓǝ̀ bumo pwasǝo wu tsǝki ɓala mala guro mò bù, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ lidǝmba tàtǝ́k aɓadǝmbo. We Yahweh Ɓakuli ka, a angŋa-dǝmba a nanacau, sǝ nǝ tsǝkbu mò ka, ɓala mala guro mò nǝ̀ kum tsǝkbu tàtǝ́k.>>
\c 8
\s1 Alimurǝm mala Dauda a lwa
\p 
\v 1 \f + \fr 8:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Kpa 18:1-17; Ang 60\xt*\ft .\f*Anzǝm mǝnia ka, Dauda gandǝ amǝ'Filisti a lwa, sǝ yinǝia aɓata rǝcandǝa male; sǝ ak nggea-là Meteg Ammah a ɓabù amǝ'Filisti.
\p 
\v 2 Ɗǝm ngga, Dauda gandǝ nzali Mowap a lwa. Pǝlǝa tsǝk amǝ'Mowap à nonggi a nzali a nkanggari-arǝia. Karǝki sarǝa mala nongŋo malea nǝ nggúr. Abanì ɓari aɓa gauwe tàrú mala aɓwana mǝno ka, wal-luia, sǝ nying banì mwashat nǝyilǝmu. Amǝ'Mowap duk aguro mala Dauda, sǝ à yinǝì wi nǝ agir-cemi\f + \fr 8:2 \fq sǝ à yinǝì wi nǝ agir-cemi \ft ko \fqa sǝ kǝ cemia.\f*.
\p 
\v 3 Lang Hadadeza muna-ɓwabura mala Rehop, murǝm Zoba puro ace ká nyesǝ bu-nzali mǝnana a ban Nggeasala Yiufǝretis, aɓata rǝcandǝa male ka, Dauda gandǝi a lwa amur njar.\f + \fr 8:3 \ft Ko: \fqa Lang Hadadeza muna-ɓwabura mala Rehop, murǝm Zoba puro ace ká nyesǝ bu-nzali mǝnana a ban Nggeasala Yiufǝretis, aɓata rǝcandǝa male ka, Dauda gandǝi a lwa amur njar.\f*
\v 4 Dauda gbami amǝpǝr á-mwashat nǝ gbǝman-tongno-nong-ɓari (1,700) andǝ asoje-kusǝu á-lumi-ɓari (20,000) arǝ murǝm Zoba. Sǝ Dauda kasǝki amazo kusǝ apǝr mǝno kat, sǝama nying aɓea ɗǝkǝm mǝnana à nǝ̀ nggǝ ɓangnǝ awaru-pǝr gbǝman-mwashat ka (100).
\p 
\v 5 Sǝ lang amǝ'Aram mala Damaska yiu ace bwalì Hadadeza murǝm Zoba munǝo ka, Dauda wal-lú amǝ'lwa malea á-lumi-ɓari-nong-ɓari (22,000).
\v 6 Dauda tamsǝ anggǝsan mala amǝ'lwa aɓalǝ amǝ'Aram a Damaska. Amǝ'Aram duk aguro mala Dauda, sǝ à yinǝì wi nǝ agir-cemi. Yahweh pè Dauda limurǝm arǝ abân mǝnana kat wari kam ngga.
\p 
\v 7 Dauda ak atongŋo bolo-njengǝlan mǝnana à nda a bù amǝgulo mala Hadadeza ka, sǝ yinǝia a Urǝshalima.
\v 8 Ɗǝm ngga, Murǝm Dauda pwan bolo-bángŋá kpǝm a Teba andǝ Berotai, anggea-là mala Hadadeza.
\p 
\v 9 Lang Toyi murǝm Hamat ok ama Dauda gandǝna amǝ'lwa mala Hadadeza puppup ka,
\v 10 pǝlǝa tasǝ Joram muna-ɓwabura male aban Murǝm Dauda, ɓǝ̀ kya makki-wi-kûn sǝ ɓǝ̀ tsǝki wi bù ace limurǝm mǝnana kum a lwa amur Hadadeza ka. Toyi pàk anggo acemǝnana ɗiɗyal ka Hadadeza camarǝ lwa-lwa andǝ Toyi tùtù. Joram yinǝì murǝm Dauda agirtúró mǝnana à pea nǝ bolo-azǝrfa, andǝ bolo-njengǝlan, andǝ bolo-bángŋá ka a buì.
\p 
\v 11 Murǝm Dauda tàr amǝnia yì agir ka ace Yahweh, atārǝia andǝ bolo-azǝrfa andǝ bolo-njengǝlan mana ea arǝ anzali mǝnana ɓunnia ka:
\v 12 yià anggea-là mala Aram,\f + \fr 8:12 \fq Aram \ft ko \fqa Edom\f* andǝ Mowap, andǝ amala amǝ'Amon, andǝ amǝ'Filisti, andǝ amǝ'Amalek. Tària kat andǝ agǝna-lwa mǝnana pwania arǝ Hadadeza muna-ɓwabura mala Rehop, murǝm Zoba ka.
\p 
\v 13 Lullǝ Dauda zǝ́kí, lang nyarǝni wal-lú aburana á-lum-bwamdǝ-tongno-nong-tàrú (18,000) mala amǝ'Aram\f + \fr 8:13 \fq amǝ'Aram \ft ko \fqa amǝ'Edom\f* a Ɓangŋaban Tuɓamur ka.
\v 14 Pǝlǝa tamsǝ anggǝsan mala amǝ'lwa male a Edom, sǝ amǝ'Edom kat pǝlǝ aguro male. Yahweh pè Dauda limurǝm arǝ abân mǝnana kat wari kam ngga.
\s1 Amǝgulo mala Dauda
\p 
\v 15 Nda Dauda yálmúr Isǝrayila kat ka; sǝ pàkgìr aɓa mǝsǝcau andǝ ɓealɓoarna ace aɓwana male kat.
\li1 
\v 16 \f + \fr 8:16 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa kùré 20:23-26 mala malǝmce mǝnia ka.\f*Jowap mǝnana nggè nda Zeruya ka, nda mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amur amǝ'lwa mala Dauda;
\li1 Jehoshafat muna-ɓwabura mala Ahilud nda mǝ'tsǝkacau aɓa malǝmce;
\li1 
\v 17 Zadok muna-ɓwabura mala Ahitup andǝ Ahimale muna-ɓwabura mala Abiyata ka, à nda ka apǝris;
\li1 Serayia ka, mǝgilǝgir mala murǝm na;
\li1 
\v 18 Benaya muna-ɓwabura mala Jehoyada ka nda ɓwamǝgule mala amǝ'Keret andǝ amǝ'Pelet;\f + \fr 8:18 \fq amǝ'Keret andǝ amǝ'Pelet \ft ka à nda ka amǝ'yáltà murǝm.\f*
\li1 sǝ amuna-burana mala Dauda ka, à nda ka apǝris.\f + \fr 8:18 \fq apǝris \ft ko amǝ'bwal-kuntúrô mala murǝm ko amǝ'tà murǝm.\f*
\c 9
\s1 Dauda lǝmdǝì Mefiboshet pěmǝɓoarne
\p 
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Dauda ɗìban ama, <<Kǝɓwa ueo atà amǝ'ɓala mala Sawul, mǝnana mǝ nǝ lǝmdǝì wi pěmǝɓoarne atàcau mala Jonatan ngga re?>>
\p 
\v 2 Adyan ngga, ɓè mǝturo-ɓala nakam a ɓala mala Sawul, lùllǝì ama \f + \fr 9:2 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 16:1-4; 19:17; 19:29\xt*\ft .\f*Ziba. À tunǝi, sǝ yiu aɓadǝm Dauda. Pǝlǝa murǝm Dauda ɗì ama, <<A nda Ziba le?>>
\p Ziba ear ama, <<E, mǝ nda, mim guro mò.>>
\p 
\v 3 Murǝm ɗì ama, <<Kǝɓwa pà kàm a ɓala mala Sawul mana ue mǝ nǝ lǝmdǝì wi pěmǝɓoarne mala Ɓakuli ka re?>>
\p Ziba earî murǝm ama, <<Ɓè muna-ɓwabura mala Jonatan nakam; gbakǝre na arǝ akusǝi kǝm.>>
\p 
\v 4 Murǝm ɗìban ama, <<Ndake?>>
\p Ziba pe wi eare ama, <<Nda a ɓala mala Makir muna-ɓwabura mala Ammiyel a Lo-Debar.>>
\p 
\v 5 Pǝlǝa murǝm Dauda túrban a ɓala mala Makir muna-ɓwabura mala Ammiyel, a Lo-Debar, sǝ à kya yinǝ Mefiboshet.
\p 
\v 6 Lang \f + \fr 9:6 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt 2Sam 16:4; 19:24; 19:25; 19:30; 21:7\xt*\ft .\f*Mefiboshet muna-ɓwabura mala Jonatan, mǝ'kà Sawul yina aban Dauda ka, yi ɓun a nzali ace pe wi gulo.
\p Dauda tunǝban ama, <<Mefiboshet!>>
\p Pǝlǝa Mefiboshet ear ama, <<Mǝ ndya ka, mim guro mò.>>
\p 
\v 7 Dauda ne wi ama, <<Ɓangciu ɓǝkǝa pakko ɗàng, acemǝnana mǝ nǝ lǝmdǝo pěmǝɓoarne atàcau mala tárró Jonatan. Mǝ nǝ nyesǝô anzali mala keò Sawul, sǝ awu nǝ̀ nggǝ ligirlina a kpamgbang-lǐ mem.>>
\p 
\v 8 Nda Mefiboshet nyare ɓun a nzali sǝ bang ama, <<Mǝ nda yana mǝnana awu nǝ̀ ɗenyinǝ mim ngga? Yì mim guro mò mǝnana ǝn kútì luna nva nǝ gulo raka.>>
\p 
\v 9 Pǝlǝa Dauda tunǝ Ziba, mǝtúró mala Sawul, sǝ ne wi ama, <<Ən pani Mefiboshet mǝ'kà mǝtala-ɓala mò agir mǝnana kat amala Sawul andǝ ɓala male na ka.
\v 10 We wunǝ amuna-burana mô, sǝ amǝ'túró-ɓala mò ka, wun nǝ̀ nggǝ rikì wi ɓaban male, sǝ wun nǝ̀ nggǝ yinǝi wi agirɓaban male, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu kúmbi muna-ɓwabura mala mǝtala-ɓala mò girlina mǝnana nǝ̀ lì ka. Sǝama Mefiboshet mǝ'kà mǝtala-ɓala mò ka, nǝ̀ nggǝ ligirlina a kpamgbang-lǐ mem koya pwari.>> (A bàkú mǝno ka, Ziba ndanǝ amuna-burana lum-bwamdǝ-tongno andǝ amǝ'túró-ɓala lumi-ɓari.)
\p 
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Ziba banggi murǝm ama, <<Mim guro mò ka, mǝ nǝ̀ pàk gìr kat kǝla mǝnana we, mǝtala-ɓala mem, yì murǝm, a nam ama mǝ pak ka.>> Nda Mefiboshet ligirlina a kpamgbang-lǐ mala murǝm Dauda, kǝla mwashat aɓalǝ amuna-burana mala murǝm ngga.
\p 
\v 12 Mefiboshet ndanǝ muna-ɓwabura lo-ɓwa, lùllǝì ama \f + \fr 9:12 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Kpa 8:34\xt*\ft .\f*Mika. Sǝ aɓwana mǝnana kat à ndanǝdo a ɓala mala Ziba ka, à duk amǝ'túró mala Mefiboshet.
\v 13 Nda Mefiboshet do a Urǝshalima, acemǝnana kǝ ligirlina a kpamgbang-lǐ mala murǝm koya pwari ka. Yì ka, gbakǝre na arǝ akusǝi kǝm.
\c 10
\s1 Dauda gandǝ amǝ'Amon andǝ amǝ'Aram a munǝo
\r (1 Acau Kpa 19:1-19)
\p 
\v 1 Anzǝm mǝnia ka, Nahash murǝm mala amǝ'Amon paklú, sǝ Hanun muna-ɓwabura male eau a buno-murǝm.
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Dauda bang ama, <<Mǝ nǝ lǝmdǝì Hanun muna-ɓwabura mala \f + \fr 10:2 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 11:1\xt*\ft .\f*Nahash pěmǝɓoarne kǝla mǝnana tárrí lǝmdǝam pěmǝɓoarne ka.>> Nda Dauda tasǝ aɓea amǝ'túró male ace giriki Hanun atàcau mala lú mala tárrí ka. Lang amǝ'túró mala Dauda yiu a nzali mala amǝ'Amon ngga,
\v 3 amǝgulo mala amǝ'Amon banggi Hanun ɓwamǝgule malea ama, <<A kǝ sǝni kǝla Dauda naban gusǝlǝ tárró, mǝnana tasǝ amǝgirikiban a bano ka le? Awo, Dauda tasǝia a bano ace shenzǝ nggea-là ma'sǝm andǝ pelǝki ɓalǝi, ace mǝnana ɓǝà yinǝ kpa-kiɗìkì male ka!>>
\v 4 Nda Hanun gbami amǝtúró mala Dauda, sǝ mwaki koyan atea ka gauwa-tsùrú mala mbotokuni. Pǝlǝa kasǝki anggea-daura malea aɓalǝu yi sulǝ a ɓunnia, sǝ tasǝia ɓǝà o.
\p 
\v 5 Lang à banggi Dauda mǝnia yì cau ka, tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân ɓǝà kya kumia, sǝ ɓǝà banggia wia ama, <<Wu ue a Jeriko sheɓǝ̀ ambotokun wun twangŋǝna ka, sǝ wu nyar a là.>> Acemǝnana gìr mǝno à pàkkia wia ka tsǝia aɓa kǝsǝkya kǝ̀rkǝ́r.
\p 
\v 6 Lang amǝ'Amon sǝni ama à pàngŋǝ̀nà gìr mǝnana tsǝa Dauda nǝ̀ ɓinǝmǝsǝia ka, à túrban sǝ à pà boalo aban amǝ'lwa mala aɓea anzali ɓǝà yi camatea: asoje-kusǝu á-lumi-ɓari (20,000) mala amǝ'Aram mala bu-nzali Bet-Rehop andǝ amǝ'Aram mala bu-nzali Zoba, andǝ murǝm mala Ma'aka nǝ aburana á-mwashat (1,000) atè, sǝ aburana á-lum-nong-ɓari (12,000) mala bu-nzali Top.
\p 
\v 7 Lang Dauda okce ka, tasǝ Jowap andǝ amǝ'lwa puppup, yià akanggǝrang aburana, ɓǝà kya munǝo arǝia.
\v 8 Amǝ'Amon puro, sǝ à tsaɗi akunarǝia a bankutio mala kún nggea-là [Rabba] ace munǝo, sǝ amǝ'Aram mala Zoba andǝ Rehop, andǝ aburana mala Top andǝ Ma'aka ka, à twal bancame malea tarang a ɓawan.
\p 
\v 9 Lang Jowap sǝni ama nzong-kún'munǝo nakam aɓadǝmbi sǝ ɓè nakam a nzǝmi, ace yiu arǝì ka, tàrki aɓea aburana aɓalǝ aburana mǝnana à ɓoarî acili aburana kat a Isǝrayila ka, pǝlǝa tamsǝia aɓa gilǝrǝu ace tùl andǝ amǝ'Aram.
\v 10 Sǝ acili aburana ka, Jowap nyia a ɓabù mǝ'eambǝi Abishai, sǝ tamsǝia aɓa gilǝrǝu ace tùl andǝ amǝ'Amon.
\v 11 Jowap ne Abishai ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ amǝ'Aram kutiam nǝ rǝcandǝa ka, awu nǝ yiu ace bwalàm; sǝ ɓǝ̀ amǝ'Amon kútiǒ nǝ rǝcandǝa ka, mǝ nǝ ká ace bwalò.
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ mǝsǝ sǝm candǝe, sǝ ɓǝ̀ sǝm munǝ nǝ mǝsǝkang-kangŋa ace aɓwana ma'sǝm, sǝ ace anggea-là mala Ɓakuli ma'sǝm! Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh pàk gìr mǝnana ɓoari wi a mǝsǝi ka.>>
\p 
\v 13 Nda Jowap andǝ amǝ'lwa mǝnana à nda atè ka, à sung tù ace munǝo arǝ amǝ'Aram, kara amǝ'Aram ndǝli nǝ mire aɓadǝmbi.
\v 14 Sǝ lang amǝ'Amon sǝni ama amǝ'Aram ɓangŋǝna ka, yià gbal ka à ndǝli nǝ mire aɓadǝm Abishai, sǝ à kya kutikio aɓa nggea-là malea. Pǝlǝa Jowap nyarî munǝo arǝ amǝ'Amon, sǝ yiu a Urǝshalima.
\p 
\v 15 Sǝama lang amǝ'Aram sǝnǝni ama amǝ'Isǝrayila gandǝnia ka, à nyare à ram rǝia abanɓwáná.
\v 16 Pǝlǝa Hadadeza murǝm Zoba túrban nǝ cau aban amǝ'Aram mǝnana à nda a takuli mala Nggeasala Yiufǝretis ka; sǝ à yiu a Helam; sǝ Shobak mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'lwa mala Hadadeza duk múrià.
\p 
\v 17 Lang Dauda okce ka, ram Isǝrayila kat abanɓwáná, à yàlî Nggeasala Jodan, sǝ à wari a Helam. Pǝlǝa amǝ'Aram gilǝrǝia a nzong-kún'munǝo ace ká je andǝ Dauda, sǝ à soa munǝo arǝì.
\v 18 Sǝama amǝ'Aram ndǝli nǝ mire aɓadǝm Isǝrayila; sǝ Dauda wal-lú amǝkok awaru-pǝr gbǝman-tongno-nong-ɓari (700) andǝ amǝpǝr á-lumi-ine (40,000), sǝ Shobak mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'lwa malea ka, à kwarí, sǝ wù abanì.
\v 19 Lang amurǝma mǝnana kat à nda aɓata Hadadeza sǝni Isǝrayila gandǝnia ka, à alta dorǝpwala nǝ Isǝrayila, sǝ à duk aguro malea. Nda ɓangciu pàkki amǝ'Aram arǝ ká bwali amǝ'Amon ɗǝm ngga.
\c 11
\s1 Cauɓikea mǝgule mǝnana Dauda pàk ka
\p 
\v 1 Nǝ kún gbangŋan, a bù-pǝlǝa mǝnana amurǝma kǝ umnǝi a lwa ka, Dauda tasǝ Jowap andǝ amǝtè andǝ [amǝ'lwa mala] Isǝrayila puppup ɓǝà o a munǝo arǝ amǝ'Amon. À kya kiɗiki amǝ'Amon, sǝ à kàrì Rabba, nggea-là malea a ɓalǝu. Sǝ yì Dauda ka ue a Urǝshalima.
\p 
\v 2 A ɓè pwarikpǝra ka, Dauda loapi ban nongŋo sǝ ndaban gya a múr-kurǝm mala palta, kara sǝn ɓè ɓwama aban sussǝo. Mǝnia yì ɓwama ka ɓoarnsari kǝ̀rkǝ́r.
\v 3 Pǝlǝa Dauda túrban ɓǝà kya ɗice yana nda mǝno yì ɓwama ka. Ɓwa mǝnana à túrí ka nyare yi banggi wi ama, <<Ɓwame ka lùllǝì nda Basheba muna-ɓwama mala Eliyam, sǝ yì nda mālá Yuriya ɓwa'Hitti.>>
\p 
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Dauda túr amǝ'na-túrbân ɓǝà kya yinǝi; sǝ lang ɓwame yina a palta ka, Dauda yi nong nǝi. (Mǝno yì ɓwama ka ndo kǝ mal lakɓamuru male anzǝm sukkio mala nkila bumkwana male ka.) Pǝlǝa ɓwame nyare o a ɓala male.
\v 5 Nǝnzǝ́mò lang Basheba yi sǝlǝ ama muna kpana a bumi ka, túrban ɓǝà kya banggi Dauda ama zongŋo kutini.
\p 
\v 6 Pǝlǝa Dauda túrban nǝ cau aban Jowap ama, <<Tàsǝâm Yuriya ɓwa'Hitti ɓǝ̀ yiu.>> Nda Jowap tasǝta Yuriya aban Dauda ka.
\v 7 Lang Yuriya yina aban Dauda ka, Dauda ɗi ama, <<Lang Jowap andǝ amǝ'lwa? Sǝ lang ká mala munǝo?>>
\v 8 Pǝlǝa Dauda banggi Yuriya ama, <<Kya a ɓala mò, sǝ wu lakki akusǝo.>> Nda Yuriya nying palta, sǝ murǝm tasǝban nǝ ɓoro ama ɓǝà pe wi.
\v 9 Sǝama Yuriya ka, o a ɓala male ɗàng; nongŋo a kún ɓala mala murǝm atārǝia andǝ amǝ'túró mala mǝtala-ɓala male kat.
\v 10 Lang à banggi Dauda ama Yuriya o a ɓala male raka, Dauda ɗì Yuriya ama, <<A nyari gya mǝsauwe adyan. Palang sǝ a wari a ɓala mò ɗàng?>>
\p 
\v 11 Yuriya earî Dauda ama, <<Akwati Kùrcau, andǝ Isǝrayila andǝ Yahuda ka, à ndaban do aɓalǝ agumli; sǝ ɓwamǝgule mem Jowap andǝ aburana mala mǝtala-ɓala mem ngga, à nda a kàttì a patal. Palang sǝ ado ka mǝ nǝ ká a ɓala mem, mǝ li sǝ mǝ nu, sǝ mǝ nong nǝ māmám? Ən kanbo nǝ yilǝmo, pà mǝ nǝ pàk gìr kǝla man ɗang!>>
\p 
\v 12 Pǝlǝa Dauda ne Yuriya ama, <<Kúndǝ nongŋo mwashat ɗǝm, sǝ lí ka mǝ nǝ nyio wu nyare.>> Nda Yuriya ueo a Urǝshalima a pwari mǝno andǝ pwari mǝnana anzǝm mǝno ka.
\v 13 Pǝlǝa Dauda tunǝ Yuriya ɓǝ̀ yiu ɓǝ̀ lìli sǝ ɓǝ̀ nu atè, sǝ tsǝk Yuriya mba-walì. Sǝama nǝ pwarikpǝra ka, Yuriya puro wario kya nongŋo a kala male aɓalǝ aguro mala mǝtala-ɓala male; wari a ɓala male ɗàng.
\p 
\v 14 Banfana nǝ dǝmbari ka, Dauda gilǝ cauterǝa aban ká aban Jowap sǝ pè Yuriya ɓǝ̀ kya pe wi.
\v 15 Aɓa mǝno yì cauterǝa ka, Dauda narǝ ne Jowap ama, <<Tasǝ Yuriya a dǝmba a kun-munǝo a ban mǝnana munǝo candǝ kam ngga. Sǝ wu nyar nǝ ta wun, wu nying Yuriya ace mǝnana ɓǝà walì ɓǝ̀ wú.>>
\p 
\v 16 Nda lang Jowap yinanǝ amǝ'lwa, à kárìna nggea-là Rabba ka, tasǝ Yuriya ɓǝ̀ o a buì mǝnana sǝlǝna ama a kàm sǝ akanggǝrang aburana mala aɓia-mǝbura pàk ka.
\v 17 Lang amǝ'lwa mala aɓia-mǝbura mǝnana aɓa nggea-là purna sǝ à soa munǝo arǝ Jowap ka, à wal aɓea amǝ'lwa mala Dauda. Yuriya ɓwa'Hitti ka nda atà aɓwana mǝnana à walia ka.
\p 
\v 18 Pǝlǝa Jowap tasǝban nǝ cau ɓǝà kya ne Dauda amur gìr mǝnana kat kǝ kumban a kún lwa ka.
\v 19 Sǝ banggi mǝ'na-túrbân cau ama, <<Anzǝm mana a malǝna banggi murǝm acau mala agir mǝnana kat à kumban ngga,
\v 20 yakǝla bum murǝm nǝ̀ lúllô sǝ nǝ̀ ɗiban ama, <Palang sǝ wu gbàshìban nggea-lê nǝ munǝo? Wu sǝlǝ mbo ama à nǝ̀ túr mundi nǝ múr sheran?
\v 21 Yana wal-lú Abimale muna-ɓwabura mala Jerubbeshet?\f + \fr 11:21 \fq Jerubbeshet \ft ka à súrǝì gbal ama \fqa Jerub-ba'al \ft (ko Gidiyon)\f* Ɓwama na mǝnana túr muna-taligo nǝ múr sheran amurí, sǝ wali wù ka re?\f + \fr 11:21 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Akas 9:50-54\xt*\ft .\f* Palang sǝ wu wari tù aban sheran?> Pǝlǝa awu nǝ ne wi ama, <Guro mò, yì Yuriya ɓwa'Hitti gbal ka wuna.> >>
\p 
\v 22 Nda mǝ'na-túrbân mǝno puro o, sǝ yi banggi Dauda acau mǝnana kat Jowap tasǝi ɓǝ̀ yi nea ka.
\v 23 Mǝ'na-túrbân mǝno ne Dauda ama, <<Bù aɓisǝm-mǝbura twalki arǝ sǝm, sǝ à pur atà sǝm a patal ace munǝo arǝ sǝm, sǝama sǝm cambia wia kàngkàng aban ká ɗār a bankutio mala kún nggea-lê.
\v 24 Pǝlǝa amǝ'nta malea túr amundi nǝ múr sheran arǝ sǝm aguro mò, sǝ aɓea aɓwana atà aburana mala murǝm wù. Guro mo, yì Yuriya ɓwa'Hitti gbal ka wuna.>>
\p 
\v 25 Pǝlǝa Dauda banggi mǝ'na-túrbân mǝno ama, <<Banggi Jowap mǝnia yì cau ka ama, <Kǝa ɗeki mǝnia yì gìr kumban ngga ɓǝ̀ zurǝì ɗenyicau mò ɗàng, acemǝnana nggeabyau kǝ tàr ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ wal ka ɗàng. Wu lidǝmba nǝ nggiki nggea-lê nǝ munǝo, sǝ wu kiɗiki.> Ɓakɓabumi nǝ amǝnia yì acau ka.>>
\p 
\v 26 Lang Basheba, mālá Yuriya ongŋǝna ama burí wuna ka, keban ace burí.
\v 27 Anzǝm mǝnana Basheba malǝna ɓua burí ka, Dauda twali yinǝi a ɓala male yi duk māmí, sǝ ɓǝlî wi muna-ɓwabura. Sǝama mǝnia yì gìr Dauda pè ka, kiɗikibum Yahweh.
\c 12
\s1 Ɓakuli Yahweh gim Murǝm Dauda
\p 
\v 1 Yahweh túr Natan mǝɓangnǝa aban Dauda. Lang Natan yina aban Dauda ka, bang ama, <<Aburana nakam ɓari aɓa ɓè nggea-là, mwashat ka mǝkume na sǝ ɓì ka mǝ'tǝ̀r na.
\v 2 Mǝkume ka ndanǝ andá andǝ anzur pas,
\v 3 sǝ mǝ'tǝ̀r ka pànǝ kǝgìr ɗàng she kǝ mǝ-nzur mǝnana kúrrô lǝsǝì gul andǝ amuni ka. Mǝnia yì muna-nzur ka kǝ lili aɓa kwar mǝ'mwashati andǝ mǝtale, kǝ nù mùr aɓa kwar nû mùr male, sǝ pak ka mǝtale nǝ̀ nongsǝì a byalí. Mǝnia yì muna-nzur a baní ka nda kǝla ɓoarnsarile.
\p 
\v 4 <<A ɓè pwari ka, bǝri yipì mǝkume a ɓala male. Mǝkume ka earce ama nǝ̀ wàl mwashat atà agirkusǝu male nǝ̀ pak girlina ace bǝri mǝnana sulǝ a baní ka ɗàng; a kún mani ka, wario kya bwal kǝ muna-nzur mwashat mala mǝ'tǝ̀r man wàlì, lambǝî bǝri male.>>
\p 
\v 5 Bum Dauda lul kǝ̀rkǝ́r arǝ mǝkume man. Kángìr aban Natan ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga, ɓwa mǝnana pak mǝnia yì gìr ka ɓoaro ɓǝà wal-luí!
\v 6 Dumǝna púp nǝ̀ mbwekî mǝ'tǝ̀r man anzur ine a kúnì mwashat, ace mǝnia yì gìr pè ka, acemǝnana pànǝ sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr ɗàng.>>
\p 
\v 7 Natan ne Dauda ama, <<A nda kǝ ɓwe! Yahweh Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila na ama: <Ən ɗārǝo a duk murǝm amur Isǝrayila, sǝ ǝn amsǝo a ɓabù rǝcandǝa mala Sawul.
\v 8 Ən po ɓala mala mǝtala-ɓala mò andǝ amāmí aɓata yálban mò. Ən po ɓala mala Isǝrayila andǝ mala Yahuda. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ mǝnia kat ka karǝo raka, ɓǝ́n pano mǝnana kútì ka.
\v 9 Ace mana sǝ a būrǝce cau mala Yahweh, ace pàk gìr mǝnana mǝɓike na ka a mǝsǝì? A wal-lú Yuriya ɓwa'Hitti nǝ nggeabyau mala amǝ'Amon, sǝ a twal māmí ɓǝ̀ duk mô.
\v 10 Twal ado aban ká a dǝmba ka, ɓala mò pà nǝ̀ usǝlǝi lú mala aɓwana kam mǝnana à nǝ̀ walia nǝ nggeabyau ka ɗàng, acemǝnana a ɓǝsǝkiam, sǝ a twal mālá Yuriya ɓǝ̀ duk māmó.>
\p 
\v 11 <<Yahweh bang ama: <Ace man yì gìr a pe ka, Mǝ nǝ tsǝk zunggǝliban ɓǝ̀ lo arǝò a ɓala mò. Akǝ mǝsǝo Mǝ nǝ twal amāmó Mǝ nǝ pe ɓè ɓwa mǝnana nda a bano tù ka; nǝ̀ nongnǝia a ɓaɓwa bwāng.
\v 12 A pê aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa, sǝ Mim ngga, Mǝ nǝ tsǝk mǝnia yì gìr ka ɓǝ̀ yi pa nǝ pwari a kùli, a ɓamǝsǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat.> >>
\p 
\v 13 Pǝlǝa Dauda banggi Natan ama, <<Ən pangŋǝ́nì Yahweh cauɓikea.>>
\p Sǝ Natan eari wi ama, <<Yahweh twalǝno banì. A pà nǝ̀ wù ɗàng.
\v 14 Sǝama acemǝnana a pakce Yahweh ɓà nǝ mǝno yì gìr a pe ka, muna mǝnana à ɓǝ̀lô ka nǝ̀ wú.>>
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Natan nyare o a ɓala male.
\p Sǝ Yahweh tsǝk muna mǝnana mālá Yuriya ɓǝlî Dauda ka bwal nǝ rǝkwana.
\v 16 Dauda zǝmbî Yahweh ace mune. Gilmùr sǝ kya kuti a ɓala, mal dù kat ndaban nongŋo a nzali.
\v 17 Aɓwana-mǝgule mala ɓala male yiu abani ace loasǝe ɓǝ̀ loapi nzali ɓǝ̀ li girlina andǝia, sǝama ginǝe.
\v 18 A tongno-nong-ɓaria nongŋo ka, mune paklú. Ɓangciu pàkki amǝ'túró-ɓala mala Dauda arǝ banggi wi ama mune pàngŋǝ̀nà-lú, acemǝnana à pakɗenyicau ama, <<Lang mune ndanǝ yilǝmu piu ka, sǝm ne wi cau sǝ kwakikiri arǝ sǝm ɗàng. Lang ado sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ ne wi ama mune wuna? Earka, nǝ̀ pàkki ɓamurì gìr mǝɓane.>>
\p 
\v 19 Sǝama lang Dauda sǝn amǝ'túró-ɓala male naban sherǝki-acau arǝarǝia ka, yi sǝlǝ ama mune wuna. Nda Dauda ɗia ama, <<Mune wuna le?>>
\p À ear ama, <<E, wuna.>>
\p 
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Dauda loapi nzali, sǝ sussǝo, hasǝ mùrú, sǝ nggaɗi agir-nggūrǝu male. Sǝ o a ɓala mala Yahweh kya peri. Osso nyare yiu a ɓala male sǝ bang ama ɓǝà pe wi girlina; à yinǝi wi nǝ girlina sǝ lìli.
\p 
\v 21 Pǝlǝa amǝ'túró-ɓala mala Dauda ɗì ama, <<Mana man a pàk ka? A gilmùr sǝ a pak-bumkiɗikea ace munio lang ndanǝ yilǝmu ka, sǝama lang mune wuna ka, a lo sǝ a li girlina.>>
\p 
\v 22 Dauda ear ama, <<Lang mune na nǝyilǝmu piu ka, ǝn gilmùr sǝ ǝn pak-bumkiɗikea acemǝnana ǝn pakɗenyicau ama, <Yana sǝlǝa ko ear ka Yahweh nǝ̀ ɓwamuram, sǝ nǝ̀ nying mune nǝyilǝmu?>
\v 23 Sǝama ado ka, mune wuna; palang sǝ mǝ nǝ gilmùr? Mǝ nǝ gandǝnǝ nyesǝ mune ɗǝm le? Mǝ nǝ ká abaní. Yì ka pà nǝ̀ nyar abanam ɗàng.>>
\s1 Ɓǝlban mala Solomon
\p 
\v 24 Dauda giriki māmí Basheba, sǝ kúti abani, nong nǝi. Basheba ɓǝl muna-ɓwabura, sǝ tunǝi ama Solomon. Yahweh earce mune,
\v 25 sǝ tasǝ cau nǝban Natan mǝɓangnǝa ama ɓǝà tunǝ mune ama \f + \fr 12:25 \fq Jedidia \ft ka ɓālǝi nda ɓwa mana Yahweh earce ka.\f*Jedidia.
\s1 Masǝlǝata lwa nǝ amǝ'Amon
\r (1 Acau Kpa 20:1-3)
\p 
\v 26 Aɓa mǝno anggo ka Jowap narǝ munǝ arǝ Rabba, nggea-là mala amǝ'Amon, sǝ angŋǝna kanggǝrang-ban mala murǝm malea.
\v 27 Jowap pǝlǝa tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aban Dauda nǝ cau ama, <<Ən munǝna arǝ Rabba, sǝ ǝn angŋǝna máɗí-mùr malea arǝia.
\v 28 Ado ka, ramba acilia amǝ'lwa abanɓwáná sǝ wu gumbǝli nggea-lê wu e; ɓǝ̀ ana raka, mǝ nǝ e, sǝ à nǝ̀ tunǝi nǝ lullǝam.>>
\p 
\v 29 Nda Dauda ramba amǝ'lwa kat abanɓwáná, sǝ wari a Rabba, munǝ arǝ nggea-lê sǝ e ka.
\v 30 Sǝ ak mbulan-murǝm mǝnana a ɓamur murǝm\f + \fr 12:30 \ft Ko \fqa a ɓamur Milkom, \ft ɓakuli mala amǝ'Amon; Milkom gbal ka à tunǝi ama Molek.\f* malea ka, sǝ à oasǝì Dauda a ɓamuri. Mbulan-murǝmì ka à pè nǝ bolo-njengǝlan sǝ à nbákí nǝ amǝsǝ tali-gǝna; dǝmbǝrya male na talent mwashat.\f + \fr 12:30 \fq talent mwashat \ft ko tyang lumi-tàrú-nong-ine.\f* Dauda pwan gǝna-lwa kpǝm a nggea-lê.
\v 31 Ɗǝm ngga, Dauda pusǝ aɓwana mǝnana aɓa nggea-lê ka, sǝ tsǝia púp arǝ atúró mǝcandǝe ɓǝà pea nǝ byau zanzǝki nggun, andǝ asoro bolo-candǝa, andǝ abero bolo-candǝa. Sǝ tsǝia ɗǝm aɓa túró ɓak tobali. Pàkkî anggea-là mala amǝ'Amon amǝnia yì gìr ka kat. Pǝlǝa Dauda andǝ amǝ'lwa kat nyar a Urǝshalima.
\c 13
\s1 Amnon gbárí Tamar
\p 
\v 1 Adyan ngga, \f + \fr 13:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 3:2-3; 1Kpa 3:2,9\xt*\ft .\f*Absalom muna-ɓwabura mala Dauda ka ndanǝ mǝ'nggaula mǝɓoarnsarì, lùllǝì ama Tamar; sǝ Amnon muna-ɓwabura mala Dauda ka earce Tamar.
\p 
\v 2 Amnon ngga suno mǝ'nggaule Tamar ɓākì kǝ̀rkǝ́r gandǝa tsǝk ɓamurì bwal nǝ rǝkwana. Sǝama Amnon kǝ sǝni ndanǝ kwano sǝ nǝ̀ pakki wi kǝgìr acemǝnana yì Tamar ka súrǝ̀ ɓwabura ɗàng.
\p 
\v 3 Sǝ Amnon ngga ndanǝ gyajam, lullǝì ama Jonadap muna-ɓwabura mala Shimeya,\f + \fr 13:3 \ft Ko \fqa Shama\ft kǝla mǝnana aɓa: \xt 1Sam 16:9; 17:13; 1Kpa 2:13\xt*\ft .\f* mǝ'eam Dauda. Jonadap ka mǝkutan na kǝ̀rkǝ́r.
\v 4 Jonadap ɗì Amnon ama, <<Palang sǝ akǝ̀ kiɗiki ɓamǝsǝo anggo kǝ̀rkǝ́r koya dǝmbari ka, we muna-ɓwabura mala murǝm? A pà nǝ banggam re?>>
\p Amnon ne wi ama, <<Ən nggǝ earce Tamar, mǝ'nggaula mǝ'eambǝam Absalom.>>
\p 
\v 5 Jonadap banggi wi ama, <<Nongnǝ-nongŋo amúr gyangŋan-nongŋo mô, sǝ wu ɓosǝki rǝo kǝla a pà jam ɗàng. Ɓǝ̀ tárró yiu ace sǝno ka, ne wi ama, <Ida, nying mǝ'nggaulem Tamar ɓǝ̀ yi pam bǝredi mǝ shê, sǝ ɓǝ̀ lam girlina a mǝsǝam, ace mǝnana mǝ sǝni sǝ mǝ lî a buì ka.> >>
\p 
\v 6 Nda Amnon nongnǝ-nongŋo, sǝ ɓosǝki rǝì kǝla pà jam ɗàng. Lang murǝm yiu a sǝne ka, Amnon banggi murǝm ama, <<Ida, nying mǝ'nggaulem Tamar ɓǝ̀ yi pàkkam agbatali kyak ɓari a mǝsǝam, ace mǝnana mǝ li a ɓabuì ka.>>
\p 
\v 7 Pǝlǝa Dauda túrban nǝ cau aban Tamar a ɓala ama, <<Ida, kya ɓala mala mǝ'eambo Amnon ado, kya lambì wi girlina.>>
\v 8 Nda Tamar wari a ɓala mala mǝ'eambi Amnon, sǝ kumi ndaban nongŋo. Pǝlǝa Tamar twal dyar bǝredi, pàk agbatali kyak nǝi a mǝsǝ Amnon, sǝ lurǝia.
\v 9 Pǝlǝa yinǝ agbatali kyak man aɓa tasau yi tamsǝi wi a ɓadǝmbi; sǝama Amnon ɓinǝ shè.
\p Amnon bang ama, <<Wu pusǝ koyana ka ɓǝ̀ purî ban mǝnia ka.>> Sǝ koyan ngga puro nyì.
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Amnon banggi Tamar ama, <<Yinǝ girline aɓa ndà-nongŋo mem, ace mǝnana mǝ li a ɓabuo ka.>> Sǝ Tamar twal agbatali kyak mǝnana pea ka, sǝ yinǝì mǝ'eambi Amnon aɓa ndà-nongŋo male.
\v 11 Lang yina nǝia abaní tù ɓǝ̀ lì ka, kara Amnon gbami, sǝ ne wi ama, <<Mǝ'nggaulem, yiu mǝ nongnǝ we!>>
\p 
\v 12 Tamar ne wi ama, <<Awo, mǝ'eambǝam, kǝa kiɗikiam ɗàng! Gìr kǝla mǝnia ka, ɓǝà kǝa pè a Isǝrayila ɗàng.\f + \fr 13:12 \ft Ɓalli aɓa: \xt Pǝris 18:9,11; 20:17\xt*\ft .\f* Kǝa pàk mǝnia yì gìr-kǝsǝkya mala ɓwaɓana ɗàng.
\v 13 Sǝ mim ngga, aya bân sǝ mǝ tsǝk muram atàcau mala kǝsǝkya? Sǝ we ka, awu nǝ̀ duk mwashat aɓalǝ agǝmɓwa amǝɓealɓike a Isǝrayila. Ida, nacau nǝ murǝm; acemǝnana yì ka pà nǝ̀ giro nǝ mim ɗang.>>
\v 14 Sǝ Amnon ngga ɓinǝ kwakikiri arǝì, sǝ acemǝnana kútì nǝ rǝcandǝa ka, gbárí, kiɗiki.
\p 
\v 15 Anzǝm mǝno ka, Amnon twal nǝ nggea ɓinǝmǝsǝu mǝgule arǝ Tamar. Yale ɓinǝmǝsǝu mǝnana ɓinǝi nǝi ka, gulo kútì suno mana oè aceì a tadǝmbe ka. Amnon ne Tamar ama, <<Lo, puro o!>>
\p 
\v 16 Sǝ Tamar banggi wi ama, <<Awo, mǝɓane mǝnia a kǝ pè nǝ pǝram ngga, ɓiki kǝ̀rkǝ́r kútì gìr mǝnana a pángnǝ́nàm ngga.>> Sǝ yì Amnon ngga, kwakikiri arǝì ɗàng.
\v 17 Pǝlǝa tunǝ lagga male mǝtúró-ɓadǝmbi sǝ ne wi ama, <<Usheni, pusǝ ɓwama mǝnia ka, ramtè a nza adyadyan ɓǝ̀ upi ɓadǝmbam, sǝ wu kumli kunkurǝm anzǝmi.>>
\v 18 Nda mǝtúró-ɓadǝm Amnon pusǝ Tamar, ramtè a nza sǝ kumli kunkurǝm anzǝmi ka. Tamar ka ndanǝ daura mǝlime mǝnana bwal ban akusǝi nǝ abui mǝsake ka arǝì, acemǝnana mǝnia ka nda ulang daura mana amuna-mamǝna mala murǝm mana à malaká súrǝ̀ ɓwabura raka, à kǝ oasǝ arǝia ka.
\v 19 Tamar ɗàrǝ́ tú, soe a ɓamúrí, sǝ bwal daura mǝlime mǝnana bwal ban akusǝi nǝ abui mǝsake, mǝnana arǝì ka, sannì. Tsǝk abui a ɓamúrí, sǝ loasǝ gì kǝ ɓua aban o.
\p 
\v 20 Absalom mǝ'eam Tamar, ɗì Tamar ama, <<Mǝ'eambo Amnoê ka tsǝo-púp nongnǝ we le? Ado ka, pwalo kǝa ɓua ɗàng, mǝ'nggaulem; yì ka mǝ'eambo na, kǝa tsǝk cau mǝnia ka a ɓabumo ɗàng.>>Nda Tamar ueo anggo nǝmurǝì aɓa bumkiɗikea a ɓala mala mǝ'eambi Absalom ngga.
\p 
\v 21 Lang murǝm Dauda ok acau mǝnia kat ka, bumi lul kǝ̀rkǝ́r.
\v 22 Absalom ne Amnon kǝ cau, ko mǝɓoarne ko mǝɓane ɗàng. Absalom ɓinǝmǝsǝ Amnon, acemǝnana kiɗikina mǝ'nggaule Tamar.
\s1 Absalom wal-lú Amnon
\p 
\v 23 Anzǝm mana apǝlǝa ɓari kutina ka, Absalom ramba amǝ'túró male ace mwaki wi nyang anzur male a Ba'al Hazo, là mǝnana nda tù a nzong-nzali Ifǝrem ngga. Sǝ tunǝ amuna-burana mala murǝm ɓǝà yiu atè ace lili-banɓoarnado abanì.
\v 24 Pǝlǝa Absalom wari aban murǝm Dauda, sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Sǝni, mim guro mò ka ǝn tunǝna amǝ'mwa-nyang nzur ace mwakam nyang anzur mem. Ida, ɓǝ̀ murǝm andǝ amǝ'túró male yiu ace lili-banɓoarnado atà sǝm.>>
\p 
\v 25 Sǝama murǝm banggi Absalom ama, <<Awo, munem, pà sǝm nǝ̀ ká kat ɗàng, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm nggá dupo twalo raka.>> Kat andǝ amani ama Absalom ɓuaki arǝì ka, ɓinǝe pà nǝ̀ ká ɗàng, sǝama tsǝki wi bù.
\p 
\v 26 Pǝlǝa Absalom bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ a pà wunǝ ká raka, ida, ɗeki mǝ'eambǝam Amnon ɓǝ̀ kya atà sǝm.>>
\p Murǝm ɗì ama, <<Ace mana sǝ a kǝ earce ama ɓǝ̀ kya atò?>>
\v 27 Sǝama Absalom nyare ɓuaki arǝì, nda murǝm Dauda nying Amnon andǝ amuna-burana mala murǝm kat à o atà Absalom ngga.
\p 
\v 28 Absalom tsǝki amǝtúró male cau ama, <<Wu tsǝkmǝsǝ wun arǝ Amnon, lang nda aɓa banɓoarna mala walo-mba, sǝ ǝn bangga wun nǝma, <Wu wali> ka, pǝlǝa wun nǝ̀ wal-lui. Cè ɓangciu pàkka wun ɗàng; mǝ nda mǝnana ǝn bangga wun nǝma ɓǝ̀ wu pè ka re? Wu cam kàngkàng, sǝ ɓǝ̀ mǝsǝ wun candǝe.>>
\v 29 Alaggana mala Absalom pàkkî Amnon kǝla mǝnana Absalom banggia wia ka. Nda amuna-burana mala murǝm lo, sǝ koyana ateà ka, eau a nzǝm pǝr-mǝdambǝriso\f + \fr 13:29 \fq pǝr-mǝdambǝriso \ft Mǝnia yì ulang pǝ̀r ka, à kǝ kumi aɓa eau'eawe mala pǝ̀r andǝ mǝdambǝriso.\f* male, sǝ à ɓangŋa akaurǝa à o.
\p 
\v 30 Lang à nda piu a njargula ka, cau yi bik ban Dauda ama, <<Absalom walna amuna-burana mala murǝm, sǝ kǝɓwa au ateà ɗàng.>>
\v 31 Pǝlǝa murǝm lo, san daura male,\f + \fr 13:31 \fq san daura male \ft ace bumkiɗikea\f* sǝ nongŋo a nzali; amǝtúró male mǝnana kat à nda ban came abanì ka, à sanggia adaura malea gbal.
\p 
\v 32 Jonadap, muna-ɓwabura mala Shimeya, mǝ'eam Dauda, na ama, <<Ɓwamǝgule mem ɓǝkǝa twali ama amuna-burana male, amuna-murǝm na kat à wal-luia ka ɗàng; Amnon nǝmurǝi na wù ka. Mǝnia ka nda gìr mǝnana Absalom kànì a ɓabumi nǝ̀ pè, twal a pwari mǝnana Amnon gbárí mǝ'nggaule Tamar ka.
\v 33 Acemani ka, ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm ɓǝkǝa falǝnǝ cau mana ama, amuna-burana mala murǝm na kat à wù ka ɗàng; Amnon na nǝmurǝi wù ka.>>
\p 
\v 34 Sǝ anggo ka, Absalom ɓangŋǝna. Lagga mǝnana cam yale amur nggea-là ka loasǝ mǝsǝi sǝ pelǝban, kara sǝn aɓwana pas aban yiu nǝ njargula mana a nzǝmi ka, a nkanggari mgbangban.
\p 
\v 35 Jonadap banggi murǝm ama, <<Sǝni, amuna-burana mala murǝm nia à kǝ yiu ka! Nda kǝla mǝnana guro mò ne ka.>>
\v 36 Tù anzǝm mǝnana Jonadap malǝna nacau ka, amuna-burana mala murǝm yi tusǝo, sǝ à loasǝ già, à ɓua. Murǝm andǝ amǝtúró male kat gbal ka, à ɓua, nggea ɓua mǝkwanbani.
\p 
\v 37-38 Sǝ Absalom ngga ɓangŋa o aban \f + \fr 13:37-38 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 3:3; 1Kpa 3:2\xt*\ft .\f*Talmai muna-ɓwabura mala Ammihud, murǝm mala \f + \fr 13:37-38 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 14:23; 14:32; 15:8\xt*\ft .\f*Geshur, sǝ ue kano pǝlǝa tàrú. Twal anonggio pas Dauda ɓua ace muna-ɓwabura male, Amnon;
\v 39 sǝama lang murǝm Dauda kumǝna girikiban amur lú mala Amnon ngga, ɓabumi o arǝ Absalom, sǝ pak-nzal sǝne.
\c 14
\s1 Absalom nyar a Urǝshalima
\p 
\v 1 Adyan ngga, Jowap muna-ɓwabura mala Zeruya yi sǝlǝ ama, ɓabum murǝm nyarǝna aban Absalom.
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Jowap túrban atà ɓè ɓwama mǝ'sǝlǝe, mǝnana ndanǝdo a Tekowa ka, sǝ ne wi ama, <<Ɓosǝki rǝo kǝla a nda aɓa ɓua-lú, sǝ wu oasǝ anggubyau ɓua-lú. Kǝa hasǝ mùrú ɗàng; pǎ kǝla ɓwama mǝnana twalǝna anonggio pas nda aɓa bumkiɗikea ace ɓwa male mǝnana wù ka.
\v 3 Sǝ wu kya aban murǝm, wu ne wi cau mǝnana mǝ nǝ banggo wu na ka.>> Sǝ Jowap pe wi cau a kúni.
\p 
\v 4 Lang ɓwama Tekowa man warina aban murǝm ngga, sárǝ́ nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali nǝ pagulo, sǝ na ama, <<Amsǝam, murǝm.>>
\v 5 Sǝ murǝm ɗì ama, <<Mana gyammo?>> Pǝlǝa ear ama, <<Mǝ nda mā-lú, burém wuna.
\v 6 Sǝ guro mò ka ndanǝ amuna-burana ɓari, sǝ à munǝo arǝaria a dalang. Kǝɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ gauwia ɗàng; man mwashat ka wal ɓi, wal-luí.
\v 7 Sǝ adyan ngga, aɓǝla mem kat longŋǝna amuram, a na ama, <Pà ɓwa mana wal mǝ'eambi ka, ace mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ wal-lui a kún yilǝmi mǝ'eambi mǝnana wal-lui ka. Ɓǝ̀ ǝn pak mǝnia ka à nǝ̀ kiɗiki mǝliɓala gbal. Anggo sǝ à nǝ̀ limgi nkalang bǝsa mem mǝnana ue ka, sǝ à pà nǝ̀ nyinggi burém lullǝu ko mǝ'kau a ɓanza ɗàng.> >>
\p 
\v 8 Pǝlǝa murǝm ne ɓwama man ama, <<O a ɓala mò, sǝ mǝ nǝ tsǝa à nǝ̀ tsǝkiro.>>
\v 9 Osso ɓwama Tekowa man ne murǝm ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ aɓwana kum cauɓikea aɓa cau mǝnia a twal ace bwalam ngga, ɓǝ̀ bafe mala cauɓike do a muram, ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm, sǝ ɓǝ̀ do amur ɓala mala tárrám; ɓǝ̀ murǝm andǝ bunomurǝm male ɓǝ̀ dum nǝ ɗwanyicau-arǝǔ.>>
\v 10 Murǝm ne wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa na kǝ cau amuro ka, yinǝi abanam, sǝ pà nǝ jeo ɗǝm ɗàng.>>
\v 11 Pǝlǝa ɓwame na ama, <<Ida, ɓǝ̀ murǝm zǝmbi Yahweh Ɓakuli male ama mǝ'mbweban-akúnì nkila mana à sukki ka, ɓǝkǝa wal-lú ɗǝm ɗàng, sǝ ɓǝ̀ munem ngga, ɓǝà kǝa kiɗiki ɗàng.>> Sǝ murǝm bang ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam ngga, nyang mur munio mwashat pà nǝ̀ kpa a nzali ɗàng.>>
\v 12 Pǝlǝa ɓwama man na ama, <<Ida, nying guro mò ɓǝ̀ nacau nǝ ɓwamǝgule mem, yi murǝm.>> Sǝ murǝm banggi wi ama, <<Nacau.>>
\v 13 Osso ɓwame na ama, <<Palang sǝ a twal cau mǝɓane a bumo kǝla mǝnia ka, arǝ aɓwana mala Ɓakuli? Acemǝnana twalkusǝu mǝnia murǝm twal amur cau man ngga, kasǝni ɓamúrì ɓashi, mǝnana ɓinǝ nyesǝ muni ɓǝ̀ nyar a là ka, muni mana pǝri o a ɓè nzali ka.
\v 14 Sǝm kat ka dumǝna púp sǝm nǝ̀ nggá wú; sǝ sǝm nda kǝla mùr mǝnana à solǝi a nzali, sǝ à pà nǝ̀ gandǝ rambi ɗǝm raka. Ɓakuli ka pà nǝ̀ twal yilǝmu ɗàng; kǝ pak njar mala nyesǝ ɓwa mǝnana a pǝri a là ka, ace mǝnana ɓǝkǝa ue a nza raka.
\v 15 Sǝ adyan ngga, ǝn yiu ace banggi ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm mǝnia yì cau ka, acemǝnana aɓwe tsǝem ɓangciu pakkam. Sǝ mim guro mò ka ǝn pakɗenyicau ama, mǝ nǝ bangcau nǝ murǝm; yakǝla nǝ̀ pè guro male gìr mǝnana zǝm ngga.
\v 16 Ən sǝlǝna ama murǝm nǝ̀ kwakikiri, sǝ nǝ̀ amsǝam a ɓabù ɓwa mana kǝ alte nǝ̀ wal-lú munem sǝ nǝ̀ kiɗikiam, sǝ anggo ka nǝ̀ twalta sǝm aɓa nzali liɓala mǝnana Ɓakuli pê aɓwana male ka.
\v 17 Sǝ adyan ngga, mim guro mò, ǝn nggǝ na nǝma, <Ida, ɓǝ̀ cau mala ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm yinǝàm nǝ usǝlǝo,> acemǝnana ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm ngga, nda kǝla mǝturonjar mala Ɓakuli mana kǝ súrǝ̀ mǝɓoarne andǝ mǝɓike ka. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh Ɓakuli mô do atò!>>
\p 
\v 18 Pǝlǝa murǝm earî ɓwama man ama, <<Cè a sǝmbǝrǝam kǝgir mǝnana mǝ nǝ ɗio ka ɗàng.>>Sǝ ɓwame na ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm ɓǝ̀ nacau.>>
\v 19 Murǝm ɗì ama, <<Bù Jowap pa aɓa mǝnia yì gìr a pàkki kat ka ɗang?>> Ɓwama man eare sǝ na ama, <<Kǝla mana a ndakam nǝyilǝmu ka, ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm, ɓwa pà nǝ̀ kyang atà bu-mǝli ko mǝnggare lang ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm ɗiban ngga ɗàng. E, guro mò Jowap nda mǝnana banggam ama mǝ pak gìr mǝnia ka; yì na tsǝkam acau mǝnia kat a kunam ngga.
\v 20 Guro mò Jowap na mǝnana pàk mǝnia yì gìr ka, ace mana ɓǝ̀ tsǝo wu nggaɗi ɗenyicau mò amur gìr mǝnana kǝ̀ u ka. Sǝama ɓwamǝgule mem ngga ndanǝ kwaro kǝla kwaro mala mǝturonjar mala Ɓakuli ace súrǝ̀ agir mǝnana kat a ɓanza ka.>>
\s1 À nyesǝ Absalom a là
\p 
\v 21 Pǝlǝa murǝm ne Jowap ama, <<Adyan ngga, ǝn earǝ́nò wu pak gìr mǝnana a earkiyice ka. Kyane kya nyesǝ laggè, yi Absalom.>>
\v 22 Pǝlǝa Jowap kpa nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali, pe murǝm gulo sǝ tsǝki wi bù. Sǝ Jowap na ama, <<Yalung sǝ guro mò sǝlǝ ama ǝn kumǝna earmúrú a bano, ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm, mǝnana a panam gìr mǝnana ǝn zǝm ngga.>>
\v 23 Nda Jowap lo sǝ wari a Geshur, sǝ kya nyesǝ Absalom a Urǝshalima ka.
\v 24 Sǝ murǝm bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ kya do a ɓala male zak; ɓǝ̀ kǝa yiu a ɓadǝmbǝam ɗàng.>> Nda Absalom do a ɓala male zak, sǝ yiu aɓadǝm murǝm raka.
\p 
\v 25 Adyan ngga, kǝɓwa pà kàm a Isǝrayila mana aɓwana ɓwangsǝi ace ɓoarjam male kǝla Absalom ngga ɗàng. Twal a ɓakusǝi kya pur a kwar ɓamuri ka, kǝ mǝɓane pà kàm arǝì ɗàng.
\v 26 Kǝ kasǝki nyang múrí a masǝlǝata koya pǝlǝa; ɓǝ̀ dǝmbǝrì wi ka, kǝ kasǝki; ɓǝ̀ kārǝ́ dǝmbǝrya mala nyang múrí ka, kǝ bik shekel gbǝman-ɓari, aɓa kpata shekel mala murǝm.
\v 27 À ɓǝlî Absalom amuna-burana tàrú, sǝ muna-ɓwama mwashat mana lullǝì ama Tamar ka. Tamar ka ɓwama mǝɓoarnsari na.
\p 
\v 28 Absalom ngga do lùmsǝ apǝlǝa ɓari a Urǝshalima, kúti aɓadǝm murǝm ɗàng.
\v 29 Pǝlǝa Absalom túrban atà Jowap, ace mǝnana nǝ̀ túrí aban murǝm ngga, sǝ Jowap ka yiu abaní ɗàng. Nyare túrban atè ɓaria, sǝ Jowap ka ɓinǝ yiu.
\v 30 Pǝlǝa Absalom ne amǝtúró male ama, <<Wu sǝni, ɓaban mala Jowap ka nda nzong andǝ mem, sǝ ndanǝ mǝssa-bálì kam. Wu kyane, wu soaki wi bǝsa.>> Nda amǝtúró mala Absalom wario sǝ à soaki ɓabanì bǝsa ka.
\p 
\v 31 Jowap lo sǝ wari aban Absalom a ɓala male, sǝ ɗì ama, <<Ace mana sǝ amǝ'túró mô kya soaki ɓaban mem bǝsa?>>
\v 32 Absalom pè wi eare ama, <<Nda acemǝnana ǝn túrban atò ama, wu yiu ɓǝ̀n túrǒ aban murǝm ngga, sǝ a ɓinǝ yiu. Ən earce nǝma wu kya aban murǝm sǝ wu ɗikamì ama, <Ace mana sǝ ǝn nying Geshur sǝ ǝn yiu kani? Nǝ̀ ɓoaribani ɓǝ̀ mǝ nda kano piu ka.> Ado ka, ǝn nggǝ earce nǝma wu pak njar acem ɓǝ̀n kúti aɓadǝm murǝm; sǝ ɓǝ̀ kumam nǝ kǝ cauɓikea arǝàm ngga, ɓǝ̀ wal-luem.>>
\p 
\v 33 Pǝlǝa Jowap wari aban murǝm sǝ ne wi mǝnia yì cau ka. Pǝlǝa murǝm túrban atà Absalom ɓǝ̀ yi kúti abaní. Sǝ Absalom yiu aɓadǝm murǝm, sǝ kūndǝ nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali aɓadǝm murǝm; sǝ murǝm gingsǝi kùrì zǝp.
\c 15
\s1 Absalom kùrkún amur Dauda
\p 
\v 1 Anzǝm mǝnia ka, Absalom kumbi ɓamurì waru-pǝr andǝ apǝr, andǝ aburana lumi-tongno ɓǝà kǝ ɓang a ɓadǝmbi.
\v 2 Pàkka, Absalom nǝ̀ lo nǝ dǝmbari ɗiɗyal sǝ nǝ̀ cam a gírí njargula mala kun-nggealà. Sǝ lang kǝ ɓwa nǝ̀ yiu a wuliban aɓadǝm murǝm ace kasǝ-ɓashi ka, Absalom nǝ̀ tunǝi, sǝ nǝ̀ ɗi ama <<A pur aya la?>> Sǝ ɓǝ̀ na ama <<Guro mò pur a bu-nzali mala Isǝrayila man ko mǝno ka,>>
\v 3 Absalom nǝ̀ banggi wi ama, <<Sǝni acau mò ka à ɓoaro sǝ ɓafo na, sǝama kǝɓwa pà kàm mǝnana murǝm twali ɓǝ̀ oeo ka ɗàng.>>
\v 4 Pǝlǝa Absalom nǝ na ama, <<Sǝni, ɓǝ̀ à na ama mǝ nda mǝɓashi aɓa nzali man ngga, ɓǝ́ koyan mana ndanǝ ɓekǝ kúnɓuana ko wuliban ngga, nǝ̀ yinǝi abanam, sǝ mǝ nǝ pàk ɓashi-mǝsǝcau.>>
\v 5 Sǝ koya pwari ɓwa sung abaní ace pe wi gulo ka, nǝ̀ sárǝ́ abui, nǝ̀ bwali sǝ nǝ̀ kùrrì zǝp.
\v 6 Anggo sǝ Absalom kǝ pakki amǝ Isǝrayila mana à yiu aban murǝm ace ɓashi ka. Ani sǝ Absalom iu ɓabum aburana mala Isǝrayila.
\p 
\v 7 Anzǝm apǝlǝa ine ka, Absalom ne murǝm ama, <<Ida, earam ɓǝn kya a Hebǝron ace mbwe kángir mem mana ǝn kánbi Yahweh ka.
\v 8 Lang mǝ nda aban do a Geshur a nzali Aram ngga, ǝn pacau nǝ kána, ama, <Mǝsǝcau ɓǝ̀ Yahweh nǝ̀ nyesǝam a Urǝshalima ka, mǝ nǝ nggá peri abaní.> >>\f + \fr 15:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 28:20-21; 1Sam 1:11\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 9 Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi wi ama, <<Kya aɓa rǝpwala.>> Nda lo sǝ o a Hebǝron ngga.
\p 
\v 10 Sǝama Absalom tasǝ amǝ'na-túrbân aban atau mala Isǝrayila kat, aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa, nǝ cau ama, <<Lang wu ongŋǝna ɓua mala njawe ka, tsuk-tsuk wu bang ama, <Absalom nda murǝm a Hebǝron!> >>
\v 11 Absalom umnǝ aburana gbǝman-ɓari mǝnana tunǝia à pur a Urǝshalima andǝi ka, sǝ à wari aɓa kunpwasǝa malea, sǝ à sǝlǝ kǝ cau ɗàng.
\v 12 Sǝ lang Absalom na aban pāki apagir mala gir'nkila ka, túrban atà Ahitofel ɓwa'Gilo, mǝkwarkir Dauda, a Gilo là male. Kùrkûn malea candǝe, sǝ aɓwana mana à nda atà Absalom ngga à lidǝmba nǝ lakki.
\s1 Dauda ɓangŋa nying Urǝshalima
\p 
\v 13 Sau ɗang ɓè mǝ'na-túrbân yiu aban Dauda sǝ ne wi ama, <<Ɓabum aburana mala Isǝrayila umǝna atà Absalom.>>
\v 14 Pǝlǝa Dauda ne aguro male mana kat atè a Urǝshalima ka ama, <<Wu lo, ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɓangŋa akaurǝa, ɓǝ̀ ana raka pà sǝm nǝ̀ apî Absalom ɗàng. Wu o akaurǝa, cè kasǝmúr sǝm tù, sǝ yinǝ mǝɓike amur sǝm, sǝ nǝ̀ wal-lú koyan mǝnana nda aɓa nggea-là ka nǝ nggeabyau.>>
\v 15 Aguro mala murǝm ne murǝm ama, <<Sǝni, sǝm aguro mò ka, sǝm nda aɓa gilǝrǝu ace pàk gìr mǝnana kat we mǝtala-ɓala ma'sǝm murǝm, a twalo awu nǝ pàk ka.>>
\v 16 Nda murǝm pur andǝ amǝ'ɓala male kat atè. Sǝama murǝm nying amā-twala lum ɓǝà ueo ace tsǝkir ɓala.
\v 17 Sǝ murǝm puro, andǝ aɓwe kat atè. Sǝ à yi cam a masǝlǝata là.
\p 
\v 18 Pǝlǝa amǝgulo male kat cam a nkanggari, sǝ amǝ'Keret andǝ amǝ'Pelet\f + \fr 15:18 \fq amǝ'Keret andǝ amǝ'Pelet \ft ka à nda ka amǝ'yáltà murǝm.\f* kat gya sǝ à kùtí a ɓadǝmbi. Sǝ amǝ'Gitti kat, yì aburana gbǝman-tongno-nong-mwashat mana à kpate a Gat ka, à gya à yi kutio aɓadǝm murǝm.
\v 19 Pǝlǝa murǝm ne Ittai ɓwa'Gitti ama, <<Palang sǝ a o atà sǝm gbal? Nyare, o kya do atà murǝm, acemǝnana we ka, a nda bǝri-ɓwa, sǝ ɗǝm ngga a nying nzali mô sǝ a yiu ace àwá. Nyar a ɓala mò.
\v 20 Kǝ yilung sǝ a yiu, sǝ yalung ngga mǝ nǝ tsǝo a sokki-kún atà sǝm le? Yale ǝn súrǝ̀ ban mǝnana ǝn kákiyi kam ngga? Nyare o, twal amǝ'eambo atò. Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh lǝmdǝo earcearǝu mǝnana kǝ nggaɗi raka andǝ domǝsǝcau.>>
\p 
\v 21 Sǝ Ittai earî murǝm ama, <<Mbak-kàngkàng Yahweh nakam, sǝ ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm na kam nǝyilǝmu ka, ban mǝnana kat ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm nǝ̀ pàk kàm, ko aɓa lú ko yilǝmu ka, a kǝ banì sǝ mim guro mò nǝ̀ pa.>>
\v 22 Pǝlǝa Dauda ne Ittai ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ nda ana ka, fa.>> Pǝlǝa Ittai ɓwa'Gitti gya kutio, andǝ aburana male kat, andǝ amuna mǝkeke mǝnana kat atè ka.
\v 23 Sǝ là kat kpa ɓua bang-bang lang Dauda andǝ aɓwana mǝnana atè kat nǝ̀ nggǝ kúti ka. Sǝ murǝm yàlî ɓangŋaban Kidǝron, sǝ aburana male kpa, sǝ yià kat à twal njargula o a ɓabondo.
\p 
\v 24 Pǝlǝa Abiyata yiu, sǝ Zadok yiu gbal andǝ amǝ'Lawi kat, nǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli a buia. Sǝ à yi tamsǝ Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli a nzali she lang aɓwana kat kutina, à purǝnì ɓá nggea-là ka.
\v 25 Pǝlǝa murǝm ne Zadok ama, <<Wu nyesǝ Akwati Kùrcau aɓa nggea-là. Ɓǝ̀ ǝn kum earmúrú a mǝsǝ Yahweh ka, nǝ̀ nyesǝam sǝ nǝ̀ tsǝa ɓǝn sǝni, andǝ bando male.
\v 26 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ na ama, <Banɓoaram arǝò raka,> mǝ ndya ka, ɓǝ̀ pakkam gìr mǝnana sǝni nda ɓoari wi ka.>>
\v 27 Murǝm banggi Zadok pǝris ɗǝm ama, <<A nda mǝ'sǝna re? Nyare o aɓa nggea-là aɓa rǝpwala, we wunǝ amuna-burana mô ɓari, Ahimaz andǝ Abiyata.
\v 28 Sǝni, mǝ nǝ kúndǝô a ban yálì nkaring mùr nǝ njar mana umnǝ ɓabondo ka, she ɓǝn angŋa cau a bano ka.>>
\v 29 Osso Zadok andǝ Abiyata twal Akwati Kùrcau mala Ɓakuli, à nyesǝi a Urǝshalima, sǝ à ue kano.
\p 
\v 30 Sǝ Dauda ka eau a bum Nkono Olif, kǝ ɓua aban ká nǝ ɓakusǝi, sǝ gìr múrí. Sǝ aɓwana mǝnana kat atè ka, à gìr múrià sǝ à kǝ eauwe, nǝ ɓua a kunia aban ká.
\p 
\v 31 Ɓeɓwa ne Dauda ama, <<Ahitofel na aɓalǝa amǝ'kùrkûn atà Absalom.>> Pǝlǝa Dauda pakhiwi ama, <<Yahweh, ida, nyesǝ kwarkiru mala Ahitofel ɓǝ̀ duk cau mǝɓangge.>>
\p 
\v 32 Lang Dauda bik ɓong Nkono Olif, a ban mǝnana aɓwana kǝ peri kàm aban Ɓakuli ka, Hushai ɓwa'Arki yiu ace je andǝi, nǝ daura-murɓe male mǝnana à sannì ka, sǝ tú na a ɓamuri.
\v 33 Dauda ne wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ a o atàm ngga, awu nǝ dupam twalo.
\v 34 Sǝama ɓǝ̀ a nyar a nggea-là, sǝ a ne Absalom ama, <Mǝ nǝ duk guro mò, murǝm; kǝla mǝnana mǝ nda guro mala tárró ɗiɗyal ka, anggo sǝ mǝ nǝ duk guro mò adyan> ngga, anggo sǝ awu nǝ gandǝâmce kwarkiru mala Ahitofel.
\v 35 Zadok andǝ Abiyata yià apǝris ka, à pà atò kano re? Acemani ka, gìr mǝnana kat a oê a ɓala mala murǝm ngga, banggi Zadok andǝ Abiyata yià apǝris.
\v 36 Sǝni, amuna-burana malea ɓari, Ahima'az muna-ɓwabura mala Zadok, andǝ Jonatan muna-ɓwabura mala Abiyata ka, à nda kano ateà. Wun nǝ̀ túriá abanam nǝ cau mǝnana kat wu ok ka.>>
\v 37 Nda Hushai, gyajam mala Dauda, yiu aɓa nggea-là ka; yiu male karǝ nǝ kutio mala Absalom aɓa Urǝshalima.
\c 16
\s1 Dauda andǝ Ziba
\p 
\v 1 Lang Dauda kutini ɓong nkono\f + \fr 16:1 \ft Nkono Olif\f* ka, Ziba guro\f + \fr 16:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 9:12\xt*\ft .\f* mala Mefiboshet kya kumi nǝ amǝdambǝriso ɓari mǝnana à twal agbatali bǝredi gbǝman-ɓari, andǝ adangŋanshi ɓǝla-anap mǝ'ime gbǝman-mwashat, sǝ ɓǝla-vwari gbǝman-mwashat, andǝ sambǝram mana à lùmsǝì nǝ mùr-anap ka.
\v 2 Pǝlǝa murǝm ɗì Ziba ama, <<Ace mana sǝ a yinǝ amǝnia yì agir ka?>> Pǝlǝa Ziba eari wi ama, <<Amǝdambǝriso mǝnia ka à nda ace amǝ'ɓala murǝm ɓǝà kǝ eau a nzǝmia, sǝ bǝredi andǝ ɓǝla-vwari ka, à nda ace alaggana ɓǝà shea, sǝ mùr-anap ka, nda ace aɓwana mǝnana à aulǝa aɓa pǝɗanban ngga.>>
\v 3 Murǝm nyare ɗì ama, <<Muna-ɓwabura mala mǝtala-ɓala mò ka nda ke?>> Ziba banggi murǝm ama, <<Nda a Urǝshalima; yì ka bang ama, Yalung ngga ɓala mala Isǝrayila nǝ̀ nyesǝî wi domurǝm mala tárrí.> >>
\v 4 Murǝm pǝlǝa banggi Ziba ama, <<Sǝni, agir mǝnana kat à mala Mefiboshet na ka à dumǝna amô.\f + \fr 16:4 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 9:3-11\xt*\ft .\f*>> Sǝ Ziba bang ama, <<Ən ɓun aɓadǝmbo; eare ɓǝn kum earmúrú a bano, we ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm.>>
\s1 Shimeyi sú Dauda
\p 
\v 5 Lang Murǝm Dauda yiu a Bahurim ngga, ɓè ɓwabura mǝnana pur a nggurkwar mala ɓala mala Sawul, lullǝi ama Shimeyi, muna-ɓwabura mala Gera ka, pur aban yiu, sǝ lang yina ka, camarǝ sáng Dauda.
\v 6 Ɓukki Dauda nǝ̀ atali, sǝ ɓukki aguro mala murǝm Dauda gbal, sǝ anggo ka, aɓwana kat andǝ akanggǝrang aburana ka à nda a koya buì mala Dauda.
\v 7 Sǝ Shimeyi kǝ sangban ama, <<Upi ban mǝnia ka, upi ban mǝnia ka, we mǝ'sukki-nkila, we ɓwa mǝɓane!\f + \fr 16:7 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 22:28\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 8 Yahweh mbweno a kúnì nkila mala amǝ'ɓala mala Sawul mǝnana kat a sukki, sǝ a ak bunomurǝm male ka. Yahweh pana domurǝmì a ɓabu munio Absalom. Sǝni, ɓealɓikea mô yina amuro acemǝnana a nda mǝ'sukki-nkila.>>
\p 
\v 9 Pǝlǝa Abishai muna-ɓwabura mala Zeruya banggi murǝm ama, <<Ace mana sǝ lu-nvwa mǝnia nǝ̀ sáng ɓwamǝgule mem, yì murǝm? Ɗekiam mǝ kyane mǝ kasǝ ɓamuri.>>
\v 10 Sǝama murǝm bang ama, <<Mana kpapi sǝm sǝnǝa wun le, wun amuna-burana mala Zeruya? Ɓǝ̀ nda aban sangban acemǝnana Yahweh banggi wi ama, <Sáng Dauda> ka, yana ɗe nǝ̀ bang ama, <Palang sǝ a pak ana?> >>
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Dauda ne Abishai andǝ aguro male kat ama, <<Wu sǝni, munem mǝnana ǝn ɓǝli nǝ tam ngga, nda aban alta yilǝmem; palang sǝ nǝ̀ duk gir'ndali nǝ ɓwa'Benjami mǝnia ka? Ɗeki ɓǝ̀ sangban, acemǝnana Yahweh na mǝnana banggi wi ama ɓǝ̀ sangban ngga.
\v 12 Yakǝla Yahweh nǝ̀ sǝn mǝɓane mǝnana à pàkkam ngga, sǝ nǝ̀ mbwem a kúnì nǝ mǝɓoarne atàcau mala sangban male yalung.>>
\v 13 Nda Dauda andǝ aburana male lidǝmba aban o amur njargula, sǝ Shimeyi kǝ gya a nkanggari nkono, a nkāɓe nǝ Dauda, sǝ kǝ sanggi, kǝ túrki wi atali, sǝ kǝ loasǝi wi tú.
\v 14 Lang murǝm andǝ aɓwana mǝnana à nda atè, à yi bwal ban Nggeasala Jodan ngga, à aulǝna. Pǝlǝa à usǝlǝ abanì.
\s1 Absalom kùtí a Urǝshalima
\p 
\v 15 Ado ka, Absalom andǝ aɓwana kat, yì aburana mala Isǝrayila, à yiu a Urǝshalima, sǝ Ahitofel ka nda atè.
\v 16 Sǝ lang Hushai ɓwa'Arki, gyajam mala Dauda yiu aban Absalom ngga, yi ne Absalom ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ yilǝmio sauwa we murǝm! Ɓǝ̀ yilǝmio sauwa we murǝm!>>
\v 17 Pǝlǝa Absalom banggi Hushai ama, <<Mǝnia ka nda earcearǝu mǝnana awu nǝ lǝmdǝì gyajam mô le? Ace mana sǝ a o atà gyajam mô ɗang?>>
\v 18 Hushai eari wi ama, <<Awo, ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh, andǝ aɓwana mǝnia, andǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat twal ka, mǝ nǝ duk male, sǝ mǝ nǝ ue atè.
\v 19 Sǝ ɗǝm ngga, yana mǝ nǝ duk guro male? Muni na re? Kǝla mǝnana ǝn duk guro mala tárró ka, anggo gbal sǝ mǝ nǝ duk guro mò.>>
\p 
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Absalom ne Ahitofel ama, <<Pà sǝm kwarkiru mô. Mana ɓǝ̀ sǝm pa?>>
\v 21 Ahitofel banggi Absalom ama, <<Kyane kya nongnǝ amā-twala mala tárró mǝnana ɗekia ɓǝ̀ à kǝ tsǝkir ɓala ka, sǝ Isǝrayila kat nǝ̀ okce ama a pani tárró kǝsǝkya a ɓaɓwa, sǝ aɓwana mǝnana à nda atò ka, à nǝ̀ kum mǝsǝkang-kangŋa.>>\f + \fr 16:21 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 2Sam 12:11-12\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 22 Nda à tsǝkî Absalom tara a múr-kurǝm, pǝlǝa Absalom nongnǝ amā-twala mala tárrí a mǝsǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat ka.
\v 23 Absalom kpata kwarkiru mala Ahitofel kǝla mǝnana Dauda pàk ka. Koya cau mǝnana pur a kún Ahitofel ka, à kǝ sǝn sǝlǝe aɓalǝi kǝla cau mǝnana pur a kún Ɓakuli nǝnggearǝì ka.
\c 17
\s1 Hushai amsǝ Dauda
\p 
\v 1 Ahitofel ne Absalom ɗǝm ama, <<Ɗeki ɓǝ̀n twal aburana á-lum-nong-ɓari, sǝ mǝ nǝ lo mǝ nǝ pyangnǝ atà Dauda a du man yalung ngga.
\v 2 Lang aulǝna sǝ ɓabumi ɓungina ka, mǝ nǝ eau amurí, sǝ mǝ nǝ pe wi ɓangciu, sǝ aɓwana mǝnana à nda atè kat ka, à nǝ̀ ɓang nǝ mire. Kǝ murǝm nǝmurǝi nda mǝ nǝ wal-luí ka,
\v 3 sǝ mǝ nǝ nyesǝô aɓwana mǝno kat a bano. Kǝ yilǝmi ɓwa mwashat nda mǝnana a alkiyite ka, sǝ aɓwana kat ka, à nǝ̀ do aɓa rǝpwala.>>
\v 4 Sǝ mǝno yì kwarkiru ka pwasǝbum Absalom andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala Isǝrayila kat.
\p 
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Absalom bang ama, <<Wu tunǝ Hushai ɓwa'Arki gbal ɓǝ̀ sǝm o cau mǝnana nǝ na ka.>>
\v 6 Sǝ lang Hushai yina aban Absalom ngga, Absalom ne wi ama, <<Mǝnia ka nda cau mǝnana Ahitofel bang ngga; ɓǝ̀ sǝm pak kǝla mǝnana na ka le? Ɓǝ̀ pa anggo raka, we ka bangŋa.>>
\p 
\v 7 Pǝlǝa Hushai ne Absalom ama, <<Mǝnia adyan ngga, cau mǝnana Ahitofel bang ngga, mǝɓoarne na ɗang.>>
\v 8 Hushai bang ama, <<A sǝlǝna ama tárró andǝ aburana male ka, akanggǝrang aɓwana na, sǝ à ndanǝ bumlulla mǝkǝ̀rkǝ́rnì kǝla nyam-candǝa mǝnana à gauwi andǝ amuni a ɓawanban ngga.\f + \fr 17:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pas 17:12; Hos 13:8\xt*\ft .\f* Ko anggo raka, tárró ka gbani lwa na; pà nǝ̀ nong atà aɓwana aɓa dù ɗàng.
\v 9 Sǝni, ko ado ka, sǝmbǝrǝna a ɓekǝ tūli, ko a ɓekǝ ban. Ɓǝ̀ puro sǝ yiu arǝ wun nǝ munǝo, sǝ wal atà aburana mô kpokyak ka, cau nǝ̀ mesǝ ama, <À walna aɓwana mǝnana à nda atà Absalom ngga.>
\v 10 Ko nggearǝ ɓwabura-ɓwa mǝnana ɓabumi na kǝla ɓabum im\f + \fr 17:10 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Amo 3:8\xt*\ft .\f* ngga, ɓangciu nǝ̀ pakki wi, sǝ ɓabumi nǝ̀ tùmùr, acemǝnana Isǝrayila kat ka sǝlǝna ama tárró ka kanggǝrang ɓwabura na, sǝ aɓwana mǝnana à nda atè ka, amǝ'mǝsǝkàng-kàngŋa na.
\v 11 Sǝama kwarkiru mem ngga, nda mǝnana ama Isǝrayila kat ɓǝ̀ ramba a bano abanɓwáná, twal a Dan, aban ká a Biyasheba; lakki malea ɓǝ̀ pa kǝla sala a kún nggeamùr,\f + \fr 17:11 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 22:17\xt*\ft .\f* sǝ wu kya a lwa nǝ nggearǝo.
\v 12 Pǝlǝa sǝm nǝ̀ ká amurí a ɓè ban mǝnana à nǝ̀ gandǝ kume kàm ngga, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ sulǝ amurí kǝla sulǝo mala ncimna a nzali, sǝ yì andǝ aburana mǝnana à nda atè ka, kǝɓwa pà nǝ̀ au ɗàng.
\v 13 Ɓǝ̀ nyar nǝnzǝmi sǝ kúti a ɓekǝ nggea-là ka, Isǝrayila kat ka nǝ̀ yinǝ anggur ɓǝ̀ kàrì nggea-lê, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ nunni aɓa ɓangŋaban, sheɓǝ̀ tali mwashat pa kàm mǝnana nǝ̀ ue kam raka.>>
\v 14 Pǝlǝa Absalom andǝ amǝ Isǝrayila kat bang ama, <<Kwarkiru mala Hushai ɓwa'Arki ɓoarî mala Ahitofel.>> (Yahweh ka, angŋǝna dǝmba tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà\f + \fr 17:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pas 21:30; 1Kor 1:19\xt*\ft .\f* ama nǝ̀ kiɗiki\f + \fr 17:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 15:31-34\xt*\f* kwarkiru mǝɓoarne mala Ahitofel, ace mǝnana Yahweh nǝ̀ yinǝ gir'murmwana amur Absalom ngga.)
\p 
\v 15 Pǝlǝa Hushai banggi Zadok andǝ Abiyata yià apǝris ama, <<Kwarkiru mǝnana Ahitofel pe Absalom andǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝ Isǝrayila ka, ndya ani ka, sǝ mim ngga kwarkiru mana ǝn pa ka, ani sǝ pa.
\v 16 Ado ka, túrban tsuk-tsuk ɓǝà banggi Dauda ama, <Kǝa nong a kún nggeasala, ban yàl nkaring mala ká a ɓabondo yalung ɗàng; ɓariki yàl a nkaring,> ɓǝ̀ ana raka, murǝm andǝ aɓwana mǝnana atè kat ka, à nǝ̀ kiɗikia.>>
\p 
\v 17 Adyan ngga, Jonatan andǝ Ahimaz ka, à nda aban kúndǝô a En-Rogel. Ɓè guro muna-ɓwama na kǝ wario kǝ banggia wia, sǝ yià gbal ka à nǝ̀ ká à nǝ̀ banggi Murǝm Dauda, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kǝa sǝnia aban kúti aɓa nggea-là raka.
\v 18 Sǝama ɓekǝ lagga sǝnia sǝ kya ne Absalom. Anggo sǝ yià kǝm ngga à o tsuk-tsuk, sǝ à bik ɓala mala ɓekǝ ɓwabura a Bahurim mǝnana ndanǝ tūli-mùr a ɓala male ka. Sǝ à sulǝ aɓa tūli-mùrnî.
\v 19 Pǝlǝa mālá ɓwabure twal kál-anzǝgir, sárǝí a kún tūli-mùrnî sǝ anzǝ mǝsǝsa amurí. Kǝɓwa sǝlǝce gìr mǝnana pàk ka ɗàng.
\v 20 Lang aguro mala Absalom yiu aban ɓwame a ɓala ka, à ɗi ama, <<Ahimaz andǝ Jonatan ngga à ndake?>> Pǝlǝa ɓwame banggia wia ama, <<À yàlnà a nkaring guguri.>> Lang à kya altea sǝ à gandǝ kumia raka, à nyar a Urǝshalima.
\p 
\v 21 Anzǝm mǝnana à umǝna ka, aburane eapi ɓá tūli-mùrnî, sǝ à wario à kya ne Murǝm Dauda. À banggi Dauda ama, <<Lo, o tsuk-tsuk kya yàl a nkaring mùr, acemǝnana Ahitofel pana kwarkiru amuro ani.>>
\v 22 Pǝlǝa Dauda lo andǝ aɓwana mǝnana à nda atè ka, sǝ à kya yàlî Mùr Jodan. Kaniama ban nǝ̀ fa ka, kǝ ɓwa pà kàm mǝnana malaká yàlî Jodan raka ɗàng.
\p 
\v 23 Lang Ahitofel sǝni ama à kpata kwarkiru male raka, sárǝ́ gir-do a nzǝm mǝdambǝriso male, lo o a nggea-là male. Wario kya tsǝk ɓala male a nggùnì sǝ gyar ɓamúrì,\f + \fr 17:23 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 27:5\xt*\ft .\f* wǔ, sǝ à tsǝì a ɓembe-ɓa-tali mala tárrí.
\p 
\v 24 Pǝlǝa Dauda yiu a Mahanayim. Sǝ Absalom andǝ aburana mala Isǝrayila kat ka, à yàlî Mùr Jodan.
\v 25 Absalom angŋa-dǝmba tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà Amasa\f + \fr 17:25 \fq Amasa \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 19:13; 20:9-12; 1Amur 2:5,32\xt*\ft .\f* amur amǝlwa, a kúnì Jowap. Amasa ka muna-ɓwabura mala ɓè ɓwa na, mǝnana à kǝ tunǝi ama Itǝra, ɓwa'Ishmayel, mǝnana al Abigiyel muna-ɓwama mala Nahash,\f + \fr 17:25 \fq Nahash \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Kpa 2:13,16\xt*\ft .\f* mǝ'eam Zeruya, nggea Jowap ka.
\v 26 Sǝ Isǝrayila andǝ Absalom ngga à tsǝk kàttì a nzali Gilǝyat.
\p 
\v 27 Lang Dauda yiu a Mahanayim ngga, Shobi muna-ɓwabura mala Nahash,\f + \fr 17:27 \fq Nahash \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 10:1-2\xt*\ft .\f* ɓwa'Amon mǝnana pur a Rabba, andǝ Makir muna-ɓwabura mala Amiyel mǝnana pur a Lo-debar ka,\f + \fr 17:27 \fq Lo-debar \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 9:4\xt*\f* andǝ Barzilayi ɓwa'Gilǝya mǝnana pur a Rogelim\f + \fr 17:27 \fq Rogelim \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 19:31-32; 1Amur 2:7; Ezr 2:61\xt*\ft .\f* ngga,
\v 28 à yinǝ akal-nongŋo, andǝ ankenye, andǝ ankwaring-dǝɓang, sǝ mǝssa mǝnana à lurǝi ka, andǝ mǝssa-alkama, andǝ mǝssa-bálì, andǝ muku, andǝ gwalong, andǝ mǝsǝ-nkunding,
\v 29 andǝ mur-nyi, sǝ kiura mǝbwale, andǝ anzur, andǝ kiura-mǝpange, à pe Dauda andǝ aɓwana mǝnana à nda atè ka ɓǝà li, acemǝnana à bang ama, <<Aɓwana mǝnia ka nzala walǝnia, à aulǝna, sǝ mǝsamur walǝnia aɓa pǝɗanban.>>
\c 18
\s1 À gandǝ Absalom a lwa
\p 
\v 1 Pǝlǝa Dauda ramba aburana mǝnana à nda atè ka, sǝ tsǝk amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala aá andǝ amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala agbǝman amúrià.
\v 2 Pǝlǝa Dauda tasǝ amǝ'lwa ɓǝà kyane; tsǝk banì mwashat aɓa gauwe tàrú malea aɓata sàrǝ̀ban mala Jowap, sǝ ɓè banì mwashat aɓa gauwe tàrú ka, nda aɓata sàrǝ̀ban mala Abishai muna-ɓwabura mala Zeruya, mǝ'eam Jowap, sǝ tàruia banì mwashat aɓa gauwe tàrú ka, nda aɓata sàrǝ̀ban mala Ittayi ɓwa'Gitti. Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi aburane ama, <<Mim nǝ ɓamúràm gbal ka, mǝ nǝ ká sǝnǝa wun.>>
\v 3 Sǝama aburane ne wi ama, <<A pà wu nǝ pur ace ká [munǝo] atà sǝm ɗàng. Acemǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm ɓang ngga, à pa nǝ̀ falǝnǝ sǝm ɗàng. Sǝ ko ɓǝ̀ gauwa-tsùrú ma'sǝm wù ka, à pa nǝ̀ falǝnǝ sǝm ɗàng. Sǝ we ka, a nda akúnì lakki mala aɓwana ma'sǝm á-lum. Acemani ka, nǝ̀ ɓoaribani wu tasǝa sǝm gbasha nǝ ɓá nggea-là.>>
\v 4 Pǝlǝa murǝm banggia wia ama, <<Koyagir mǝnana kat, wu sǝni nda ɓoaro kutibani ka, mǝ nǝ pe.>> Nda murǝm cam a nkanggari bankutio [mala Mahanayim], sǝ aburana male kat ging-gya twalkusǝu-anzǝmarǝia sǝ à kǝ kutio aban puro arǝ anggǝsanì malea, mala agbǝman andǝ aá.
\p 
\v 5 Pǝlǝa murǝm tsǝki Jowap andǝ Abishai andǝ Ittai nzongcau ama, <<Lagga man, yì Absalom ngga, wu pangnǝi ɓukɓuk, acem.>> Sǝ amǝ'lwa kat ok cau mǝno murǝm ne amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban, amur Absalom ngga.
\p 
\v 6 Nda amǝ'lwa mala Dauda purî ɓá nggea-là aban ká lwa arǝ Isǝrayila. Mǝnia yì munǝo ka, à pe a ndà-nggun mala bu-nzali Ifǝrem.
\v 7 Akano ka, amǝ'lwa mala Dauda gandǝ amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila. Sǝ aɓwana mǝnana à wal-luia ka, à nda kpǝm. À wal-lú aɓwana á-lumi-ɓari (20,000).
\v 8 Kara lwa ara ak ɓá nzali kat, sǝ ɓwabundǝa wù kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Yale làkkì mala aɓwana mǝnana à wù atàcau mala agir'mur'mwana mǝnana kum aɓwe aɓa ndà-nggun ngga, kútì làkkì mala aɓwana mǝnana à wal-luia nǝ nggeabyau ka.
\s1 Lú mala Absalom
\p 
\v 9 Lang munǝo na arǝ lidǝmba ka, Absalom kya jakiarǝ aburana mala Dauda. Sǝ yì ka, ɓariki nǝ̀ ɓangŋa a nzǝm pǝr-mǝdambǝriso male ace àwá, sǝama lang pǝr-mǝdambǝriso ɓangŋa kúti aɓata ɓè nggun mǝgule mana abu-nggunì na zukǝtǝp ka, kara ɓamúrí gbāli a nre ka abu-nggunì. Sǝ pǝr-mǝdambǝrisonî lidǝmba nǝ o, ɗeki aban gyare a nre bumkuli andǝ nzali.
\p 
\v 10 Mwashat aɓalǝ aburana mala Dauda sǝn mǝnia yì gìr ka, sǝ banggi Jowap ama, <<Ən sǝn Absalom aban gyare arǝ ɓè bu-nggun mǝgule.>>
\v 11 Jowap pǝlǝa ɗì ɓwabure ama, <<Mana! A sǝni? Palang sǝ a ɓinǝ wal-luí, a túrí a nzali akǝ̀ banì ɗàng? Yale ɓǝ́n pano amǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa shekel lum andǝ nggur-ɓunu mala amǝ'lwa.>>
\p 
\v 12 Sǝ ɓwabure eari wi ama, <<Ko ɓǝ̀ a pam amǝsǝ bolo-azǝrfa shekel á-mwashat aɓa buam ngga, pà mǝ nǝ tsǝk buam arǝ muna-ɓwabura mala murǝm ɗàng, acemǝnana sǝm kat ka, sǝm oè nǝ kir sǝm, lang murǝm tsǝko nzongcau wunǝ Abishai andǝ Ittai, ama, <Wu tsǝkir mǝlagga, yì Absalom, acem.>
\v 13 Sǝ ɓǝn mangŋǝna murǝm, ǝn walna-lú muna-ɓwabura male ka, murǝm nǝ̀ yia sǝlǝ nǝnzǝ́mò ama, mǝ nda mǝnana ǝn wal-lú muni ka, sǝ we nǝ nggearǝo ka, awu nǝ nyem.>>
\p 
\v 14 Pǝlǝa Jowap bang ama, <<Mim ngga, pa mǝ nǝ kiɗiki pwari kǝla mǝnia sǝnǝ we ɗàng.>> Pǝlǝa Jowap twal ankongŋo tàrú a bui, wari aban Absalom, mǝnana nda nǝyilǝmu piu, aban gyare a bu-nggun mǝgule ka. Pǝlǝa zuɓiki nǝ ankongŋo mǝno ka a kun-ɓalǝi.
\v 15 Pǝlǝa lum aɓalǝ amǝ'bwal-agirmunǝo mala Jowap, gumbǝli Absalom a ɓalǝu, à tǝmnggi, sǝ à wal-luí.
\p 
\v 16 Pǝlǝa Jowap twang njawe, nda amǝ'lwa male nyarî pǝrta amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila, acemǝnana Jowap tamsǝia ka.
\v 17 À twal Absalom, à túrí aɓa tūli mǝlime aɓa ndà-nggun, sǝ à ramba atali amurí gum-gum. Sǝ anggo ka, amǝ Isǝrayila kat ɓangŋǝna, koyanale ka umǝna a ɓala male.
\p 
\v 18 (Mǝnana Absalom malaká wù raka, tsǝkî ɓamúrì nggea tali, a Ɓangŋaban mala Murǝm, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ duk gir'lǝmndǝa ace lidǝmba mala lullǝi ka. Acemǝnana pakɗenyicau ama, <<Mim ngga, ǝn panǝ muna-ɓwabura mana nǝ lidǝmba nǝ lullǝam a ɓanza, mana à nǝ̀ nggǝ ɗenyinǝ mim nǝi ka ɗàng.>> Pǝlǝa tunǝ nggea tali mǝno nǝ lullǝì. Anggo sǝ à kǝ tunǝi ama, <Nggea tali mala Absalom,> ba yalung.)\f + \fr 18:18 \ft Absalom tsǝk nggea tali mǝnia ka a bàkú mǝnana malaká ɓǝl amuna-burana male raka (\xt 2Sam 14:27\xt*\ft ); ko à wukina sǝ tsǝk talinì.\f*
\s1 Cau mala lú mala Absalom // andǝ bumkiɗikea mala murǝm Dauda
\p 
\v 19 Pǝlǝa Ahima'az muna-ɓwabura mala Zadok bang ama, <<Came, ɓǝn ɓangŋa, ɓǝn kyan nǝ bǝsacau man aban murǝm; mǝ nǝ nggá ne wi ama Yahweh kasǝna-ɓashi, angŋamurí a bù aɓi-mǝbura.>>
\p 
\v 20 Pǝlǝa Jowap ne wi ama, <<A nda mǝnana awu nǝ ká nǝ mǝnia yì bǝsacau yalung ngga ɗàng. Awu nǝ gandǝnǝ ká nǝi wi nǝ cê a ɓè pwari, sǝama dumǝna púp a pà wu nǝ ká nǝ cê yalung ɗàng, acemǝnana muna-ɓwabura mala murǝm [yì Absalom] ngga, pàngŋǝ̀nà-lú.>>
\p 
\v 21 Pǝlǝa Jowap ne ɓè ɓwa'Kush ama, <<We, kya banggi murǝm gìr mǝnana a sǝni ka.>> Pǝlǝa ɓwa'Kush ɓun aɓadǝm Jowap, sǝ ɓangŋa aban o.
\p 
\v 22 Pǝlǝa Ahima'az, muna-ɓwabura mala Zadok ne Jowap ɗǝm ama, <<Ko palang le ka, ida, came mǝ ɓangŋa atà ɓwa'Kush mǝno.>> Sǝ Jowap pe wi eare ama, <<Muna-ɓwabura mem, ace mana sǝ a kǝ earce ama a nǝ ká? We ka, a panǝ kǝ tangnakusǝu mǝnana awu nǝ̀ kum ace mǝnia yì bǝsacau ka ɗang.>>
\p 
\v 23 Pǝlǝa Ahima'az bang ama, <<Ko palang le ka, mǝ nǝ ɓangŋa, mǝ nǝ ká.>>
\p Pǝlǝa Jowap bang ama, <<Ɓangŋa!>> Pǝlǝa Ahima'az ɓangŋa, um nǝ njar ɓawanban, sǝ ɓangŋa akì ɓwa'Kush dǝmba.
\p 
\v 24 Lang Dauda na ban do anre kúnɓala mana nǝ ɓalǝu andǝ mana nǝ nza mala nggea-lê ka, mǝ'sǝn múr nggea-là eau a kuli amur kún nggea-là nǝ rǝ sheran. Lang loasǝ mǝsǝi sǝnban ngga, kara sǝn ɓè ɓwabura aban ɓang nǝmurǝi aban yiu nǝbania.
\v 25 Pǝlǝa mǝ'sǝn múr nggea-là tunǝ murǝm sǝ banggi wi gìr mǝnana sǝn ngga. Murǝm pǝlǝa bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ ɓwe na nǝmurǝi ka, dumǝna púp ndanǝ bǝsacau.>> Sǝ ɓwe kǝ gbàshìban tù kǝ yiu.
\v 26 Pǝlǝa mǝ'sǝn múr nggea-là sǝn ɓè ɓwabura aban yiu nǝ mire, pǝlǝa tunǝ mǝ'yál kunɓala sǝ bang ama, <<Sǝni, ɓè ɓwabura nia ɗǝm kǝ yiu nǝ mire nǝmurǝi ka!>> Pǝlǝa murǝm bang ama, <<Yì gbal ka, dumǝna púp ndaban yinǝ bǝsacau.>>
\v 27 Pǝlǝa mǝ'sǝn múr nggea-là na ama, <<Ən nggǝ sǝni, ɓwa mǝdǝmbe ka, kǝ ɓangŋa kǝla Ahima'az muna-ɓwabura mala Zadok.>> Murǝm pǝlǝa bang ama, <<Yì ka, ɓwa mǝɓoarne na. Ndaban yinǝ bǝsacau mǝɓoarne.>>
\p 
\v 28 Pǝlǝa Ahima'az loasǝ gì tunǝ murǝm sǝ ne wi ama, <<Koman kat ka, nda pepè!>> Pǝlǝa yì ka, ɓùn aɓadǝm murǝm nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali, sǝ bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ ɓwangsǝban pa aban Yahweh Ɓakuli mô, mǝnana pàna amǝ'mgbicau a ɓabuo ka, yià mǝnana à loasǝ buia arǝ ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm ngga.>>
\p 
\v 29 Pǝlǝa murǝm ɗìban ama, <<Nggearǝ lagga, yì Absalom ngga, nda jam le?>> Pǝlǝa Ahima'az pa eare ama, <<Lang Jowap guro mò tasǝam ama ɓǝn yiu ka, ǝn sǝn ban ngga, zurina kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Sǝama, ǝn súrǝ̀ mana girni na ɗang.>>
\p 
\v 30 Pǝlǝa murǝm bang ama, <<Nyar a nkanggariban, kúndǝô.>> Nda yi ka, nyar a nkanggariban, sǝ cam a kǝ banì.
\p 
\v 31 Pǝlǝa ɓwa'Kush yi tusǝo, sǝ bang ama, <<Ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm, ok mǝnia yì bǝsacau mǝɓoarne ka! Yahweh amsǝno yalung, a ɓabù aɓwana mǝnana kat à mgbicau arǝò ka.>>
\p 
\v 32 Pǝlǝa murǝm ɗì ɓwa'Kush ama, <<Mǝlagga Absalom ngga, nda jam le?>> Pǝlǝa ɓwa'Kush pa eare ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ aɓi-mǝbura kat mala ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm, andǝ aɓwana mǝnana kat à mgbicau arǝì ace ɓealɓikea ka, ɓǝà pa kǝla mǝno yì lagga ka!>>
\p 
\v 33 Pǝlǝa murǝm ngga, rǝì twal ɓǝla. Sǝ eauwe, wari a kurǝm-kuli mana amur kunɓala ka, ɓua kàm. A njar aban ká ka, kǝ ɓua kǝ na ama: <<Oi, muna-ɓwabura mem Absalom! Muna-ɓwabura mem, muna-ɓwabura mem Absalom! Ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝa ama, mǝ nda mǝnana ǝn wú a kunio ka, ɓǝ́ ɓoarna, oi muna-ɓwabura mem Absalom, muna-ɓwabura mem!>>
\c 19
\s1 Dauda andǝ Jowap
\p 
\v 1 Pǝlǝa à banggi Jowap ama, <<Sǝni, murǝm ngga, ndaban ɓua sǝ kǝ keban ace Absalom.>>
\v 2 Limurǝm mǝnana à kumi a pwari mǝno ka, yi pǝlǝia amǝ'lwa kat ɓua-lú, acemǝnana a pwari mǝno ka, aɓwe ok ama, <<Murǝm na ban pak-bumkiɗikea ace muni.>>
\p 
\v 3 Sǝ aburane kùtí zàng aɓa nggea-lê [Mahanayim] a pwari mǝno, kǝla aɓwana mǝnana à ɓangŋa a kun-munǝo, kǝsǝkea pakkia wia, sǝ à swár zàng à kùtí aɓa nggea-là ka.
\v 4 Murǝm ngga gìr ɓamǝsǝi, sǝ sa a ɓua, kǝ na ama, <<Oi, muna-ɓwabura mem Absalom! Oi, Absalom, muna-ɓwabura mem, muna-ɓwabura mem!>>
\p 
\v 5 Pǝlǝa Jowap kùtí aɓa ɓala, aban murǝm, sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Yalung ngga, a panì aburana mô kat kǝsǝkea, yià aɓwana mǝnana à nda à amsǝ yilǝmo andǝ ayilǝmi amuna-burana andǝ amuna-mamǝna mô, andǝ ayilǝmi amāmó andǝ amā-twala mô ka.
\v 6 We ka, a kǝ earce aɓwana mana à kǝ ɓinǝmǝsǝo ka, sǝ a kǝ ɓinǝmǝsǝ aɓwana mana à kǝ earceo ka. Acemǝnana yalung ngga, a lǝmdǝni bwāng ama, amǝ'sàrǝ̀ban andǝ aburana mô ka, à nda ka kǝgir a bano ɗàng. Mim ngga, ǝn sǝlǝna ama, ban nǝ ɓoaro yalung, mǝnana ɓǝ̀ Absalom ngga nda nǝyilǝmu, sǝ sǝm kat ka, sǝm wukina ka.
\v 7 Adyan ngga, puro kya ɓakɓabum aburana mô. Mim ngga, ǝn kánagìr nǝ Yahweh, ɓǝ̀ a puro, a wari raka, kǝ ɓwabura pà kàm mǝnana nǝ̀ ue atò, a bu-dù man yalung ngga ɗàng. Sǝ mǝnia yì gìr ka, nǝ̀ duk mǝɓike kǝ̀rkǝ́r, mǝnana kútì agir'murmwana mǝnana kat à kumo, twal a lagga mò, ba yalung ngga.>>
\p 
\v 8 Pǝlǝa murǝm lo, kya do a ban-do male a kún nggea-là. Lang à banggi aɓwana ama, <<Murǝm na aban do a kún nggea-là ka,>> pǝlǝa yià kat ka, à yiu aɓadǝmbi. (Aɓa mǝno anggo ka, amǝ Isǝrayila [mǝnana à nda atà Absalom ngga] à angŋa-dǝmba à ɓangŋǝna, koyan ngga nyarna a ɓala male.)
\s1 Dauda nyar a Urǝshalima
\p 
\v 9 Sǝ aɓalǝ atau mala Isǝrayila ka, aɓwana camarǝ makgir arǝarǝia, à kǝ bang ama, <<Murǝm ngga, nda mǝnana akmúr sǝm a ɓabu aɓisǝm-mǝbura ka; yi ka, nda ɓwa mǝnana amsǝ sǝm a ɓabu amǝ'Filisti ka. Sǝ adyan ngga, ɓangŋǝna nyingŋǝna nzali ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ apî Absalom ngga;
\v 10 sǝ Absalom, mǝnana sǝm ɗārǝí, ɓǝ̀ duk murǝm amur sǝm ngga, wuna a kun-munǝo. Sǝ palang ado sǝ wu na kǝ cau, ace nyesǝ murǝm ɗàng?>>
\p 
\v 11 Pǝlǝa Dauda tasǝ mǝnia yì cau ka, aban Zadok andǝ Abiyata, yià apǝris, ama: <<Wu ɗikâm aɓwana-mǝgule mala Yahuda ama, <Palang ado, sǝ wun nda ka aɓwana mana, she nǝnzǝ́mò, sǝ wun nǝ̀ nyesǝ murǝm a ɓala male ka, yi mǝnana gìr mana kat à bangŋi aɓa Isǝrayila ka, kutina a kir murǝm ngga?
\v 12 Wu nda ka amǝ'eambǝam; wu nda ka nggūrǝam andǝ nkila mem! Sǝ ace mana sǝ wun nda ka aɓwana mǝnana she nǝnzǝ́mò sǝ wun nǝ̀ nyesǝ murǝm a palta ka?>
\v 13 Sǝ wu ne Amasa ama, <We ka, a nda nggūrǝam andǝ nkila mem re? Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli pakkam gìr, yale ɓǝ̀ wal-luem, yi mana ɓǝn twalo a duk mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amur amǝ'lwa mem, a kúnì Jowap raka.> >>
\v 14 Nda Amasa pwanɓabum aburana mala Yahuda kat, kǝla ɓwa mwashat, sǝ à tasǝî murǝm cau ama, <<Nyar aban sǝm, we wunǝ aburana mana kat à nda atò ka.>>
\v 15 Pǝlǝa murǝm nyare, yiu a Jodan. Adyan ngga, aburana mala Yahuda yina a Gilgal, ace mǝnana ɓǝà kya kum murǝm, sǝ ɓǝà yinǝi a nkaring Mùr Jodan ngga.
\p 
\v 16 Sǝ Shimeyi, muna-ɓwabura mala Gera, ɓwa'Benjami, mana pur a Bahurim ngga, fà rǝì akaurǝa andǝ aburana mala Yahuda, à wari a kúllí Murǝm Dauda.
\v 17 Yiu atārǝia andǝ aburana a tàu mala Benjami, ɓwa á-mwashat, andǝ Ziba, muna-ɓala mala Sawul, mǝnana yiu andǝ amuna-burana male lum-nong-tongno, andǝ amǝ'túró-ɓala male, lumi-ɓari ka. Yia ka, à fà rǝia, à wari a kúllí murǝm, a Jodan.
\v 18 Yia ka, à yàlî mùr Jodan, a ban yàl nkaring, ace eamsǝki amǝ'ɓala mala murǝm a nkaring, ace mǝnana à nǝ̀ pwasǝbum murǝm ngga. Pǝlǝa Shimeyi, muna-ɓwabura mala Gera, ɓùn amur ankūnǝi a nzali, aɓadǝm murǝm,
\v 19 sǝ banggi wi ama, <<We murǝm, ɓwamǝgule mem, ida, twàlâm-ban cauɓikea mem, cè a ɗenyinǝ gir mǝɓike mǝnana guro mò pá a pwari mǝnana ɓwamǝgule mem nying Urǝshalima ka ɗàng. Ida, murǝm ɓǝkǝa bwal mǝnia yì gìr ka a ɓabumi ɗàng.
\v 20 Acemǝnana mim guro mò ka, ǝn sǝlǝna nǝma, ǝn pangŋa cauɓikea. Nda gir mǝnana tsǝa sǝ mim, aɓalǝ aɓwana kat, mala ɓala mala Yisǝfu ka, ǝn ak dǝmba, ǝn yiu, mǝ nǝ yia kum murǝm, ɓwamǝgule mem ngga.>>
\p 
\v 21 Pǝlǝa Abishai, muna-ɓwabura mala Zeruya bang ama, <<Ɓoaro Shimeyi ka, ɓǝà wal-luí, acemǝnana yì ka sú ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh ɗārǝi ka re!>>
\v 22 Sǝama Dauda bang ama, <<Man oasǝ wun arǝàm le, wun amuna-burana mala Zeruya, mǝnana wun nǝ̀ dupam kǝla ɓibura a pwari man yalung ngga? Ɓoaro ɓǝà wal-lú kǝɓwa aɓa Isǝrayila a pwari man yalung ngga le? Mim ngga, ǝn sǝlǝ mbak ama, yalung ngga mǝ nda murǝm amur Isǝrayila re?>>
\v 23 Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi Shimeyi ama, <<A pà wu nǝ wù ɗàng.>> Anggo sǝ murǝm kánbi wi.
\p 
\v 24 Sǝ Mefiboshet, mǝ'kà Sawul gbal ka, wario kya kum murǝm. Yi ka, lak akusǝi ɗàng, amsǝ mbotakuni ɗàng sǝ yale lak agir-nggūrǝu male ɗàng, twal a pwari mǝnana murǝm nying là, sǝ uk ka, ba pwari mǝnana murǝm nyar nǝi jam ngga.
\v 25 Lang nying Urǝshalima, sǝ yiu aban murǝm ngga, murǝm ɗì ama, <<Palang sǝ a ɓinǝ ká atàm, Mefiboshet?>>
\v 26 Mefiboshet pa eare ama, <<We ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm, mǝturo-ɓala mem Ziba, nda mǝnana swarkiam ngga. Mim guro mò ka, mǝ nda gbakǝre, nda ǝn banggi wi nǝma, <Tsǝkam gir-do anzǝm mǝdambǝriso, ace mǝnana ɓǝn koè ɓǝ̀ sǝm u sǝnǝ murǝm>ngga.
\v 27 Sǝ yì ado ka, yi mangŋa guro mò, aban ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm. Sǝama, ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm ngga, nda kǝla mǝturonjar mala Ɓakuli; acemani ka, pàk gìr mǝnana kat pwasǝbumo ka.
\v 28 Mim sǝnǝ amǝ'ɓala mala tárrám ngga, ɓǝ́ a walna sǝm, sǝama a kún mani ka, a earam mǝ li girlina a ban-li mô. Ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm, mana ɗǝm ado mǝ nǝ zǝmba, mǝnana nǝ̀ kútì mǝno ka?>>
\p 
\v 29 Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi wi ama, <<Cau mana a ne ka, karǝna anggo. Mim ngga, ǝn tsǝngŋa nzongcau ama, ɓǝà gau nzali ma'wun, anre wun, wun nǝ Ziba, a tsùrú.>>
\p 
\v 30 Sǝ Mefiboshet banggi murǝm ama, <<Ɗeki ɓǝ twal koyagir ka, yi mana yalung ado ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm nyarǝna jam ngga.>>
\s1 Dauda lǝmdǝì Barzilayi pěmǝɓoarne
\p 
\v 31 Barzilayi, ɓwa'Gilǝya gbal ka, pur a Rogelim, sǝ wari atà murǝm ace tsǝkte aban yàlî Nggeasala a Jodan, sǝ nǝ̀ tsǝiandà aban o a là.
\v 32 Barzilayi ka, jamgula na, apǝlǝa male na lumi-tongno-nong-tàrú. Yi ka, nda ɓwa mǝnana ɗenyinǝ murǝm, linǝi, aɓa do male kat a Mahanayim ngga, acemǝnana yì ka, mǝgǝna na kǝ̀rkǝ́r.
\p 
\v 33 Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi Barzilayi ama, <<Fa, ɓǝ̀ sǝm yàl a nkaring sǝnǝ we, ace mǝnana wu kya do a banam a Urǝshalima ka. Sǝ mim ngga, mǝ nǝ ɗenyinǝ we abanì.>>
\p 
\v 34 Pǝlǝa Barzilayi pe murǝm eare ama, <<Apǝlǝa uekam shen, mala do nǝyilǝmu, mǝnana ɓoaro mǝ o a Urǝshalima sǝnǝ murǝm ngga?
\v 35 Adyan ngga, mǝ ndanǝ apǝlǝa lumi-tongno-nong-tàrú a ɓanza. Mǝ nǝ gandǝ gauta gìr mǝnana nǝ̀ ɓoaram ngga, andǝ mǝnana pà nǝ̀ ɓoaram raka le? Mim guro mò ka, mǝ nǝ gandǝ ok ɓoaro mala girlina ko girnùná ɗǝm le? Mǝ nǝ gandǝ ok gì aɓwana aban tu'nggyal ɗǝm le? Palang ado, sǝ mim guro mò ka, mǝ nǝ duk ɓè twalo aban ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm?
\v 36 Ən kārǝa mǝ kum tangnakusǝu mǝgule kǝla mǝnia ka ɗàng. Mim guro mò ka, mǝ nǝ yàlî Jodan atārǝia andǝ murǝm aban ká dǝmba bǝti.
\v 37 Ida, nying guro mò, ɓǝ̀ nyare ɓǝ̀ o, ace mǝnana ɓǝn kya wú a là mem, tù aban ɓembe mala tárrám andǝ nggem. Sǝama, guro mò, yì Kimham ngga, ndya ka. Nyì ɓǝ̀ yàl a nkaring atò, ɓwamǝgule mem, murǝm. Pakki wi gìr mǝnana kat, a sǝni nda ɓoar a mǝsǝo ka.>>
\p 
\v 38 Pǝlǝa murǝm bang ama, <<Kimham ngga, sǝm nǝ̀ yàl a nkaring sǝnǝi, sǝ mǝ nǝ pakki wi gìr mǝnana kat a sǝni nda ɓoar ka. Sǝ gìr mǝnana kat a earkiyice abanam ngga, mǝ nǝ pakko wi.>>
\p 
\v 39 Pǝlǝa aɓwana kat, yàlî Nggeasala Jodan; sǝ lang murǝm yàlǝ́nì nkaring ngga, mǝn abui kùr Barzilayi zǝp, tsǝki wi bù, sǝ tsǝiandà. Nda Barzilayi nyare o a là male ka.
\p 
\v 40 Pǝlǝa murǝm kutio wari a Gilgal, sǝ Kimham o atè. Aɓwana mala Yahuda kat, andǝ gauwa-tsùrú mala amǝ Isǝrayila, tsǝkta murǝm amur njar, aban o a là.
\s1 Tàu mala Yahuda andǝ Isǝrayila makgir amur murǝm
\p 
\v 41 Banì sau ɗang, aburana mala Isǝrayila kat yiu aban murǝm, sǝ à ɗì ama, <<Palang sǝ amǝ'eam sǝm, aburana mala Yahuda, iuo arǝ sǝm sǝ à eamsǝ murǝm andǝ amǝ'ɓala male, à yàlî Jodan, atārǝia andǝ aburana male kat?>>
\v 42 Pǝlǝa aburana mala Yahuda pe aburana mala Isǝrayila eare ama, <<Nda acemǝnana murǝm ngga, ɓǝla-nggurkwar ma'sǝm na ka. Sǝ palang ado sǝ bum wun lúllô amur mǝnia yì gìr ka? Ado ka, sǝm lì ɓekǝ gìr mala murǝm le? Sǝ wu sǝni sǝm twal ɓekǝ gìr abaní ace ɓamurǝ sǝm le?>>
\p 
\v 43 Pǝlǝa aburana mala Isǝrayila, pe aburana mala Yahuda eare ama, <<Sǝm ngga, sǝm ndanǝ atau lum aɓa domurǝm, acemani ka, rǝcandǝa mǝnana sǝm ndanǝi mala bang ama Dauda ka murǝm ma'sǝm na ka kútì ma'wun. Mana tsǝa ado sǝ wu ɓǝsǝki sǝm? Sǝm nda mǝnana sǝm tita nacau mala nyesǝ murǝm ma'sǝm ngga re?>> Sǝama nacau mala aburana mala Yahuda nǝ bumpina ka, kútì mala aburana mala Isǝrayila.
\c 20
\s1 Sheba mgbicau arǝ Dauda
\p 
\v 1 Ɓè ɓwabura \f + \fr 20:1 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Nggur 13:13\xt*\ft .\f*mǝ'ɓealɓana na kam, lullǝi ama Sheba, muna-ɓwabura mala Bikǝri, a tàu mala Benjami. Yì ka, ɓua njawe sǝ bang ama,
\q1 <<Sǝm pànǝ kǝ kāmbe aɓa Dauda ɗàng,
\q2 Sǝ sǝm pànǝ kǝ nzali liɓala aɓa muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi ɗàng.
\q1 Isǝrayila, koyanale ka ɓǝ̀ nyar a gumli male!>>
\m 
\v 2 Nda aburana mala Isǝrayila kat nying Dauda, sǝ à kpata Sheba muna-ɓwabura mala Bikǝri ka. Sǝama aburana mala Yahuda lanzǝ atà murǝm malea, twal a Jodan aban ká Urǝshalima.
\p 
\v 3 Lang Murǝm Dauda nyar a ɓala male a Urǝshalima ka, pwan amā-twala male lum mǝnana nyia ace ɗenyinǝ ɓala ka, tsǝia a ɓè ɓala, sǝ tamsǝ amǝ'yálban ɓǝà kǝ yália. Kǝ pea wia gìr mǝnana kat à paktǝle ka, sǝama pak-ɓwama nǝia ɗàng. À kasǝkunia a ɓala ba pwari lú malea, à do kǝla amā-lú.
\p 
\v 4 Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi \f + \fr 20:4 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 2Sam 17:25; 19:13\xt*\ft .\f*Amasa ama, <<Rambam aburana mala Yahuda abanɓwáná aɓa nongŋo tàrú, sǝ wu yiu wunǝia.>>
\v 5 Nda Amasa puro ace ká tunǝ aburana mala Yahuda abanɓwáná ka, sǝama banì sauwa kútì anonggio mǝnana murǝm kasǝi wi ka.
\p 
\v 6 Sǝ Dauda banggi Abishai ama, <<Adyan ngga, Sheba muna-ɓwabura mala Bikǝri nǝ̀ pàkka sǝm gìr mǝɓane nǝ̀ kútì mǝnana Absalom pàk ka. Twal aburana mem, sǝ wu ɓangŋa atè, ɓǝ̀ ana raka nǝ̀ kumbi ɓamúrì akanggǝrang anggea-là, sǝ nǝ̀ ɓwar arǝ sǝm.>>
\s1 Jowap wal-lú Amasa
\p 
\v 7 Nda aburana mala Jowap andǝ amǝ'Keret andǝ amǝ'Pelet andǝ akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa kat purî ɓá Urǝshalima, aɓata sàrǝ̀ban mala Abishai, sǝ à oa pǝrta Sheba muna-ɓwabura mala Bikǝri.
\p 
\v 8 Lang à yi bik ban tali mǝgule a Gibiyon ngga, Amasa yi kumia. Jowap ka, ndanǝ adaura-murǝm male mala amǝ'lwa arǝì, nǝ nggeabyau aɓa ndè mǝnana marǝ nggurrì a taɓuni ka. Lang Jowap sungŋo nǝ̀ ká a ban Amasa ka, nggeabyaunì swárô kpa a nzali.
\p 
\v 9 Jowap ɗì Amasa ama, <<Mǝ'eambǝam, a nda jam le?>> Pǝlǝa bwal Amasa a mbotokuni nǝ bui-mǝli, ace mǝnana nǝ̀ kùrrì zǝp, mala makkun ngga.
\v 10 Sǝ Amasa ka, sǝn byau mǝnana a bù Jowap ka ɗàng. Nda Jowap zuɓi Amasa nǝ byau a bumi, sǝ amuna-lungŋe solǝ a nzali. Amasa wǔ, nǝ zuɓiban mwashat ɓǝ̀rɓǝ̀r.\f + \fr 20:10 \ft Sǝni gbal aɓa: \xt 1Amur 2:5\xt*\ft .\f* Pǝlǝa Jowap andǝ mǝ'eambi Abishai pǝrta Sheba muna-ɓwabura mala Bikǝri.
\v 11 Mwashat aɓalǝ alaggana mala Jowap cam amur lú Amasa, sǝ loasǝ gì na ama, <<Ɓwa mǝnana kat earmúr Jowap, sǝ ɓwa mǝnana kat nda anzǝm Dauda ka, ɓǝ̀ kpata Jowap!>>
\v 12 Amasa nongŋo aban mgbangtǝki aɓa nkila male a tsùrú mala njargula, sǝ koya mǝ'lwa mǝnana yiu a banì ka, go kusǝi came. Sǝ lang lagga man sǝni ama koyan mǝnana yiu a ban Amasa ka, cam piu ka, nda sungsǝki Amasa ɓǝ̀ gǝshì múr njargula, warinǝi a ɓawan, sǝ kùmsǝi wi kungtung amurí ka.
\v 13 Lang à gǝshina lú Amasa nyingŋǝ̀nà múr njargula ka, aɓwana kat o atà Jowap ace pǝrta Sheba, muna-ɓwabura mala Bikǝri.
\p 
\v 14 Sheba gya atà atau mala Isǝrayila kat yi pur a Abel-Bet-Ma'aka, andǝ ɓá bù-nzali mala amǝ'Beri puppup; à ramba abanɓwáná, sǝ à o atè.
\v 15 Amǝ'lwa mala Jowap kat yiu sǝ à gumbǝli nggea-là Abel-Bet-Ma'aka sǝ Sheba na aɓa nggea-lê. Pǝlǝa à ɓak mgbangban mǝnana eau a kuli aban ká arǝ nggea-lê, sǝ kya cam nǝ nza arǝ kanggǝrang tali mǝnana nggea-lê cam amurí ka. Sǝ aɓwana mǝnana kat atà Jowap ka, à kùtí a tǝmgi kusǝ sheranî, ace mǝnana à nǝ̀ me a nzali ka.
\v 16 Pǝlǝa ɓè ɓwama mǝ'sǝlǝe tunǝban nǝɓa nggea-lê ama, <<Wu kwakikir wun! Wu kwakikir wun! Ida, wu ne Jowap ama ɓǝ̀ yiu kani ace mǝnana mǝ bangcau nǝi ka.>>
\v 17 Lang Jowap sung tù aban ɓwame ka, ɓwame ɗi ama, <<A nda Jowap le?>>
\p Jowap ear ama, <<E, mǝ nda.>>
\p Pǝlǝa ne wi ama, <<Kwakikiro arǝ cau mǝnana guro mò nǝ̀ banggo ka.>>
\p Jowap eari wi ama, <<Mǝ nda ǝn nggǝ oeo ka.>>
\p 
\v 18 Pǝlǝa ɓwame nacau, ama, <<A pwarian ngga aɓwana kǝ̀ bang ama, <Wu alta kwarkiru a Abel,> sǝ anggo sǝ à gilǝki cau.
\v 19 Sǝm nda aɓalǝ aɓwana mana à earce dorǝpwala andǝ domǝsǝcau a Isǝrayila ka. Wun ndarǝ alte ama wun nǝ̀ wal-lú nggea-là mǝnana nggeau na a Isǝrayila ka. Palang sǝ wun nǝ̀ kiɗiki nzali liɓala mǝnana mala Yahweh na ka?>>
\p 
\v 20 Jowap pe wi eare ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sappi banam, ɓǝ̀ sappi banam mǝnana ama mǝ pisǝì ko mǝ bǝbbǝriki ka.
\v 21 Cê pa anggo ɗàng. Ɓè ɓwabura na ǝn alkiyite ka, lullǝi ama Sheba muna-ɓwabura mala Bikǝri, ɓwa nzali múr-ankono mala Ifǝrem. Yì ka loasǝ bui aɓa mgbicau arǝ murǝm, nggearǝ murǝm Dauda. Wu pa mǝnia yì ɓwabura ka, sǝ mǝ nǝ nying nggea-lê.>>
\p Ɓwame ne Jowap ama, <<Sǝni, sǝm nǝ̀ túrò ɓamuri amúr sheran.>>
\p 
\v 22 Pǝlǝa ɓwame wari nǝ kwaro male aban aɓwana mǝnana kat aɓa nggea-lê ka. À kasǝ ɓamur Sheba muna-ɓwabura mala Bikǝri, sǝ à túrì Jowap. Nda Jowap twang njawe, sǝ aburana male mesǝe, à nying nggea-lê, koyan ngga nyar a là male ka. Pǝlǝa Jowap nyar a Urǝshalima aban murǝm.
\s1 Amǝgulo mala Dauda
\r (2 Samu 8:15-18; 1 Acau Kpa 18:14-17)
\li1 
\v 23 \f + \fr 20:23 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 2Sam 8:16-18; 1Amur 4:3-6\xt*\ft .\f*Jowap nda gbani amur amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila kat;
\li1 Benaya muna-ɓwabura mala Jehoyada nda mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amur amǝ'Keret andǝ amǝ'Pelet,\f + \fr 20:23 \fq amǝ'Keret andǝ amǝ'Pelet \ft ka à nda ka amǝ'yáltà murǝm.\f*
\li1 
\v 24 Adoniram nda ɓwamǝgule amur aɓwana mana à tsǝia aɓa túró púp ka,
\li1 sǝ Jehoshafat muna-ɓwabura mala Ahilud nda mǝ'twalcau aɓa malǝmce;
\li1 
\v 25 Sheva nda mǝgilǝgir,
\li1 sǝ Zadok andǝ Abiyata ka, à nda ka apǝris,
\li1 
\v 26 sǝ Ira ɓwa'Jayir gbal ka, pǝris mala Dauda na.
\c 21
\s1 Dauda mbwekî amǝ'Gibiyon a kúnì gìr // mǝnana à pàkkia wia ka
\p 
\v 1 A nza mala yálmúrû mala Dauda ka, nzal-gula kpa mǝnana twal apǝlǝa tàrú a nzǝmarǝia ka, nda Dauda alta ɓamǝsǝ Yahweh ka. Sǝ Yahweh bang ama, <<Mǝnia ka nda atàcau mala Sawul andǝ ɓala-nkila male, acemǝnana wal-lú amǝ'Gibiyon.>>
\p 
\v 2 Nda murǝm Dauda tunǝ amǝ'Gibiyon sǝ nacau nǝia ka. (Amǝ'Gibiyon ngga à pur a nggurkwar mala Isǝrayila ɗàng; à nda ka amǝ'Amor mǝnana à ueo, mana amǝ Isǝrayila kánbia wia ama à nǝ̀ ɗekia nǝyilǝmu ka;\f + \fr 21:2 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt Jes 9:3-17\xt*\ft .\f* sǝama Sawul alte nǝ̀ twaltea aɓa bumpina male ace aɓwana mala Isǝrayila andǝ Yahuda).
\v 3 Sǝ Dauda ɗì amǝ'Gibiyon ama, <<Mana ɓǝn pa ace wun? Sǝ mana ɓǝn pa a kúnì mǝɓane mǝnana à pàkka wun, mǝnana nǝ̀ tsǝa wun nǝ̀ tsǝki aɓwana mala Yahweh bù ka?>>
\v 4 Pǝlǝa amǝ'Gibiyon earî wi ama, <<Cau mǝnana anre sǝm sǝnǝa Sawul andǝ ɓala male ka, bolo-zǝnariya ko bolo-njengǝlan pà nǝ̀ gilǝki ɗàng; sǝ pà aɓa rǝcandǝa ma'sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm wal-lú kǝɓwa a Isǝrayila ɗàng.>> Sǝ Dauda ɗia ama, <<Sǝ mana ado wu kǝ earce ama mǝ pa ace wun?>>
\v 5 À earî murǝm ama, <<Ɓwa mǝnana wal-lú sǝm, sǝ hamce ama nǝ̀ twalta sǝm, ace mǝnana kǝɓwa atà sǝm ɓǝkǝa ue nǝyilǝmu a ɓekǝ ban aɓa nzong-nzali mala Isǝrayila raka,
\v 6 ɓǝà pa sǝm aɓwana tongno-nong-ɓari atà amuna-burana male, sǝ sǝm nǝ̀ gyaria aɓadǝm Yahweh a Gibiya, là mala Sawul, yì ɓwa mǝnana Yahweh tàrì ka.>>
\p Sǝ murǝm bang ama, <<Mǝ nǝ pa wunia.>>
\p 
\v 7 Sǝama ace kána mǝnana anre Dauda andǝ Jonatan a ɓadǝm Yahweh ka,\f + \fr 21:7 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 18:3; 20:12-17; 23:18; 2Sam 9:1-7\xt*\ft .\f* murǝm nying Mefiboshet muna-ɓwabura mala Jonatan mǝ'kà Sawul ɓǝ̀ auwa.
\v 8 Pǝlǝa murǝm twal amuna-burana ɓari, Armoni andǝ Mefiboshet, amuna mala Rizpa ɓoarnsarile Aiya mǝnana ɓǝlî Sawul ka, andǝ amuna-burana tongno, mǝnana Merap ɓoarnsarile Sawul ɓǝlî Adǝriyel muna-ɓwabura mala Barzilayi ɓwa Mehola ka.
\v 9 Dauda tasǝ amuna-burana mǝnia ka a ɓabu amǝ'Gibiyon, sǝ à gyaria amur ɓè muna-nkono aɓadǝm Yahweh; yià mǝno tongno-nong-ɓari ka à wù atārǝia. À wal-luia aɓalǝ anonggio mǝdǝmbe mala pwan-gìrɓaban, a bàkú tita pwan mǝssa-bálì.
\p 
\v 10 Pǝlǝa Rizpa ɓoarnsarile Aiya twal lagir-doatu,\f + \fr 21:10 \fq lagir-doatu \ft ko <<sangina-lagìr>>\f* sǝ sárǝi ace ɓamúrì amur tali, a bàkú tita pwan-gìrɓaban ba kpa mala mbulo nǝ kuli amur aluî. Sǝ earî anyal a bumkuli ɓǝà sulǝ amuria nǝ pwari, ko anyam-bondo nǝ du ɗàng.
\v 11 Aɓwana yi banggi Dauda gìr mǝnana Rizpa ɓoarnsarile Aiya, mā-twala mala Sawul pàk ka.
\v 12 Pǝlǝa Dauda wario kya pwan amú Sawul andǝ amú muna-ɓwabura male Jonatan a ban aburana mala Jabesh-Gilǝyat. Amǝ Jabesh-Gilǝyat ka à akdǝmba à kya iu amuia a nzawara mala Bet-shan, ban mǝnana amǝ'Filisti gyaria kam, a pwari mǝnana amǝ'Filisti wal-lú Sawul amur Nkono Gilbowa ka.
\v 13 Dauda twal amú Sawul andǝ amú muni Jonatan a ban mǝno sǝ yinǝia. Ɗǝm ngga à ramba amú aburana mǝno mǝnana à gyaria ka.
\v 14 À lumsǝ amú Sawul andǝ amú muni Jonatan a ɓembe-ɓa-tali mala tárrí Kish a Zela aɓa bu-nzali Benjami. Koman kat ka à pè kǝla mǝnana murǝm bang ngga. Anzǝm mǝno ka, sǝ Ɓakuli ok hiwi ace nzalî.
\s1 Munǝki-amunǝo arǝ akáɓá-ɓwa mala amǝ'Filisti
\r (1 Acau Kpa 20:4-8)
\p 
\v 15 Ɓè fara ka, munǝo lo ɗǝm a nre ka amǝ'Filisti andǝ amǝ'Isǝrayila. Dauda andǝ aburana male atè wari a mǝno yì munǝo ka, sǝ lang à nda aɓa munǝo arǝ amǝ'Filisti ka, Dauda aulǝa.
\v 16 Pǝlǝa Isǝbibenop, ɓwa'Filisti, mwashat atà amǝ'kau mala akáɓá-ɓwa, mǝnana dǝmbǝrya mala kaɗa male ka, tyang tàrú nǝ gauwa-tsùrú na (3.5), sǝ kùr rǝi nǝ bǝsa nggeabyau ka, bang ama nǝ̀ wal-lú Dauda.
\v 17 Sǝama, Abishai muna-ɓwabura mala Zeruya, yiu yi bwalì Dauda kàm, sǝ wal-lú ɓwa'Filistinî. Pǝlǝa aburana mala Dauda kánbi wi ama, <<A pà wunǝ yiu a lwa ɗǝm atà sǝm ɗàng, ace mǝnana wu kǝa limgi tǎlaban mala Isǝrayila raka.>>
\p 
\v 18 Anzǝm mǝno ka ɓè munǝo lo ɗǝm andǝ amǝ'Filisti a Gop. A bàkú mǝno ka, Sibekai ɓwa Husha, wal-lú Saf, mwashat atà amǝ'kau mala akáɓá-ɓwa.
\p 
\v 19 A ɓè munǝo ɗǝm andǝ amǝ'Filisti a Gop ka, Elhanan muna-ɓwabura mala Jaare-oregim, ɓwa'Betalami, wal-lú mǝ'eam Golaya ɓwa'Gitti, mǝnana tondong kaɗa male nyane kǝla muna-nggun-so ka.\f + \fr 21:19 \ft Sǝni aɓa: \xt 1Sam 17:7\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 20 Ɓè munǝo lo ɗǝm a Gat. A banì ka ɓè ɓwabura nakam kaɓa nggurung mǝnana a koya bui ka, ndanǝ amuna-bu tongno-nong-mwashat, sǝ amuna-kusǝu tongno-nong-mwashat a koya kusǝi; kpapi kat ka à nda lumi-ɓari-nong-ine; yì gbal ka mǝ'kau mala akáɓá-ɓwa na.
\v 21 Sǝ lang ɓǝsǝki Isǝrayila ka, Jonatan muna-ɓwabura mala Shimeyi, mǝ'eam Dauda wal-lui.
\p 
\v 22 Akáɓá-ɓwa mǝnia ine ka, amǝ'kau mala akáɓá-ɓwa mala Gat na, sǝ à wù nǝ bù Dauda andǝ aburana male.
\c 22
\s1 Dauda tùkî Yahweh nggyal
\p 
\v 1 Sǝ Dauda bang acau mala nggyal mǝnia ka aban Yahweh, a bàkú mǝnana amsǝi a bù aɓi-mǝbura kat, sǝ a bù Sawul ka
\v 2 ama,
\q1 <<Yahweh nda tali mem,
\q1 ban-sǝmbǝrǝa mem
\q2 andǝ mǝ'amsǝam;
\q1 
\v 3 We Ɓakuli, tali mem,
\q2 mǝnana aɓalǝo sǝ ǝn nggǝ kum ban-auwa ka;
\q1 ntongŋo mem andǝ rǝcandǝa mala amsǝban mem,
\q1 kanggǝrang-ban andǝ ban-auwa mem;
\q2 mǝ'amsǝam a ɓabù ɓìkìbura.
\q1 
\v 4 Ən ɓua aban Yahweh, yì mǝnana kārǝ́na ɓǝà ɓwangsǝi ka;
\q2 Anggo sǝ mǝ nǝ kum amsǝban a ɓabù aɓiam-mǝbura.
\q1 
\v 5 Lú gumbǝliam kǝla eaki-nkono mala mùr;
\q2 mùrɓangŋa mala kiɗikiban ɓakiam;
\q1 
\v 6 Anggur mala Shewol taɓǝlikiam;
\q2 agbǝli mala lú puratam.
\q1 
\v 7 Aɓa nggikiban mem ngga, ǝn ɓua aban Yahweh,
\q2 ǝn ɓua aban Ɓakuli mem.
\q1 Ok giem aɓa ndà male;
\q2 sǝ ɓua mem ace gbasha kúti a kiri.
\q1 
\v 8 Pǝlǝa ɓanza dǝurǝo sǝ gǝggǝli,
\q2 akusǝɓa mala kuli ɓǝl-ryak'ryak
\q2 sǝ à dǝurǝkio;
\q2 à gǝggǝli acemǝnana bumi-lullo.
\q1 
\v 9 Yele pur a ɓá lullǝi;
\q2 bǝsa mǝ'earke pur a ɓá kúni,
\q2 nkalang mǝnana nggangsǝ ka ear-bǝsa nǝ baní.
\q1 
\v 10 Dìlì kuli sǝ sulǝo,
\q1 pǝndǝa mǝcikciki na aɓata akusǝi.
\q1 
\v 11 Eau a nzǝm cerup sǝ yàlé;
\q2 e, à sǝni a nkpamtari gung.\f + \fr 22:11 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa \xt Ang 18:10\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 
\v 12 Tsǝk pǝndǝa mǝnana gumbǝlì ka, pǝlǝ tara male,
\q2 pǝrɓang mana lùmsǝ nǝ mur ka kàrì.\f + \fr 22:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa \xt Ang 18:11\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 
\v 13 Tǎlaban mana aɓadǝmbi ka,
\q2 tsǝk nkalang bǝsa lo earke.
\q1 
\v 14 Yahweh sa a kuli kǝla mgbarangce.
\q2 Ɓakuli mana Karban Kat nǝ Gulo ka loasǝ gì.\f + \fr 22:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ayu 37:4\xt*\ft .\f*
\q1 
\v 15 Túr amundi sǝ mesǝ aɓi-mǝbura,
\q2 liki'nzama male zurìmúria.
\q1 
\v 16 Abân-mǝlime mala nggeamùr ndǝlya,
\q2 akusǝɓa mala ɓanza nong kwas,
\q1 lang Yahweh gimban,
\q2 sǝ pyau n'yali a ɓá lullǝi ka.
\q1 
\v 17 Sárǝ́ bui nǝ kuli sǝ twalam;
\q2 eamsǝam a ban-mǝlime aɓa nggeamùr.
\q1 
\v 18 Amsǝam a ɓabù ɓiam-mǝbura mǝ'rǝcandǝe,
\q2 a ɓabù aɓwana mana à ɓinǝmǝsǝàm ngga, acemǝnana rǝcandǝa malea ɓākì mem.
\q1 
\v 19 À sulǝ amuram a pwari murɓikea mem,
\q2 sǝama Yahweh pam gbasha.
\q1 
\v 20 Sǝ ɗǝm ngga pusǝam, yinǝ mim aɓa dalang.
\q2 Amsǝam, acemǝnana bumipwasǝ arǝàm.
\q1 
\v 21 Yahweh pàngnǝ mim kǝla mǝnana karǝ arǝ ɓealɓoarna mem ngga;
\q2 pam tangnakusǝ ɗwanyicau-arǝǔ mem.
\q1 
\v 22 Ən kpanata anjargula mala Yahweh,
\q2 sǝ ǝn kyanggi Ɓakuli mem aban ká pàk ɓealɓikea ɗang.
\q1 
\v 23 Anggurcau male kat ka, à nda aɓadǝmbam,
\q2 sǝ ǝn kyanggi anê male ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 24 Mǝ nda jik aɓadǝmbi.
\q2 Ən bwal ɓamúràm arǝ cauɓikea.
\q1 
\v 25 Acemani ka Yahweh panam tangnakusǝu kǝla mana karǝ arǝ ɓealɓoarna mem ngga,
\q2 kǝla mana karǝ arǝ doɓoarnsari mem aɓadǝmbi ka.
\q1 
\v 26 Aban amǝ lǝmdǝ mǝsǝswatǝr ka, awu nǝ lǝmdǝ mǝsǝswatǝr,
\q2 aban amǝ'ɗwanyicau-arǝu ka, awu nǝ lǝmdǝ ɓamúrò, a nda mǝ'ɗwanyicau-arǝu.
\q1 
\v 27 Aban amǝ'doɓoarnsari ka, awu nǝ lǝmdǝ ɓamúrò mǝ'doɓoarnsari,
\q2 aban amǝ'kìɗìkì ka, awu nǝ lǝmdǝ ɓamúrò mǝɓìkìdo.
\q1 
\v 28 Awu nǝ amsǝ aɓwana mǝnana à paria ka,
\q2 sǝama amǝsǝo na arǝ amǝtwàlɓamúrû, ace nyesǝia a nzali.
\q1 
\v 29 A nda pitǝla mem, Yahweh.
\q2 Yahweh kǝ̀ tâ aɓa pǝndǝa mem.
\q1 
\v 30 Nǝ we ka, mǝ nǝ gandǝ loasǝtà amǝ'tǝllìban,
\q2 nǝ pagbasha mala Ɓakuli mem ngga, mǝ nǝ yàlî múr sheran.
\q1 
\v 31 Mala Ɓakuli ka, njar male na jik.
\q2 Cau mala Yahweh ka à mwamǝni.
\q1 Yi ka, ntongŋo na
\q2 aban aɓwana mana à kùmsǝ a baní ka.
\q1 
\v 32 Yana nda Ɓakuli, ɓǝ̀ Yahweh na raka?
\q2 Sǝ yana nda tali, ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli na raka?
\q1 
\v 33 Ɓakuli nda ban-auwa mǝcandǝe mem,
\q2 sǝ kǝ tsǝk njar mem ɓǝ̀ duk jik.
\q1 
\v 34 Tsǝk akusǝam ɓǝà soa nzali kǝla mala mbamba,
\q2 sǝ tamsǝam amur abân mǝ'dāhre.
\q1 
\v 35 Kǝ kanì abuam munǝo,
\q2 ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ anggwarbuam gandǝ kar nta mala bolo-bángŋá.
\q1 
\v 36 Sǝ ɗǝm ngga à panam ntongŋo mala amsǝban mô;
\q2 sǝ pagbasha mô dumsǝnam a gulo.
\q1 
\v 37 A tangsǝna njar ace akusǝam,
\q2 ace mǝnana akusǝam ɓǝà kǝa shambǝrǝ raka.
\q1 
\v 38 Ən pǝrnata aɓiam-mǝbura, sǝ ǝn kiɗikinia.
\q2 Ən pǝlǝ nzǝmam ɗàng she lang ǝn malnia ka.
\q1 
\v 39 Ən twalnatea, ǝn zuɓikia sǝ à gandǝ lo ɗang.
\q2 E, à kpaki a nzali a kusǝam.
\q1 
\v 40 A mārǝnam nǝ rǝcandǝa ace munǝo;
\q2 Aɓwana mǝnana à lo arǝàm ngga, a ɓunginia aɓatam.
\q1 
\v 41 A tsǝ́ngŋǝ̀nà aɓiam-mǝbura à pǝlǝam nzǝmia,
\q2 ace mǝnana ɓǝn kiɗiki aɓwana mǝnana à ɓinǝmǝsǝam ngga.
\q1 
\v 42 À pelǝban, sǝ kǝɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ amsǝia ɗàng;
\q2 à ɓua aban Yahweh, sǝ okia wia ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 43 Pǝlǝa ǝn goea kǝla muku nzali.
\q2 Ən nyakia sǝ ǝn parkia kǝla dǝɓang a njarɓala, sǝ ǝn mesǝkia.
\q1 
\v 44 A amsǝnam aɓa kúnɓuàna sǝnǝ aɓwana mem.
\q2 A tsǝ́ngŋǝ̀nám ǝn dumǝna múrû amur anzali.
\q1 Aɓwana mana ǝn súrǝ̀ia raka, à pàk túróɓadǝmbu aɓadǝmbam.
\q2 
\v 45 Amǝkúnɗàngna nǝ̀ paɓamuria abanam,
\q2 Lang à ok cau nǝ o ani amuram ngga, à nǝ̀ oakam.
\q1 
\v 46 Ɓabum amǝkúnɗàngna nǝ̀ ɓungio,
\q2 à nǝ̀ purkî ɓalǝ abân-sǝmbǝrǝa malea,
\q2 sǝ à nǝ̀ yiu nǝ rǝɓǝla.
\q1 
\v 47 Yahweh na nǝ yilǝmu!
\q2 Ɓwangsǝban ɓǝ̀ pa aban Tali mem!
\q1 Gulo ka mala Ɓakuli na,
\q2 Tali mala amsǝban mem.
\q1 
\v 48 Yì nda Ɓakuli mǝnana mbwekiyiam akúnì,
\q2 mǝnana kǝ yinǝ aɓwapǝndǝa aɓatam,
\q2 
\v 49 mǝnana pusǝam ǝn purì bù aɓiam-mǝbura ka.
\q1 E, a kǝ loasǝam mǝ kútì aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ lo arǝàm ngga.
\q2 A kǝ amsǝam a bù ɓwa mǝɓìkìbura.
\q1 
\v 50 Acemani ka, mǝ nǝ po yàwá, we Yahweh, aɓalǝ anzali,
\q2 sǝ mǝ nǝ tùki anggyal ɓwangsǝki lullǝo.
\q1 
\v 51 Pè murǝm male amsǝban mǝgule,
\q2 sǝ kǝ lǝmdǝì ɓwa male mana ɗārǝì ka, earcearǝu mǝnana kǝ gǝshi raka,
\q2 aban Dauda andǝ amǝɓala male tàtǝ́k.>>
\c 23
\s1 Masǝlǝata acau mala Dauda
\p 
\v 1 Amǝnia ka, à nda ka masǝlǝata acau mala Dauda:
\q1 Acau mǝnana à pùr a kún Dauda muna-ɓwabura mala Jeshi;
\q2 acau mala ɓwa mǝnana à loasǝi a buno gulo,
\q1 yì ɓwa mǝnana Ɓakuli mala Yakupu ɗārǝì ka,
\q2 yì mǝ'ngyal ɓoarna mala Isǝrayila:
\q1 
\v 2 Bangŋo mala Yahweh bangcau nǝ kunam,
\q2 cau male na a lasǝam.
\q1 
\v 3 Ɓakuli mala Isǝrayila nanacau,
\q2 Tali mala Isǝrayila nanàm ama,
\q1 <<Ɓwa mǝnana kǝ yálmúr aɓwana nǝ ɓealɓoarna,
\q2 mǝnana kǝ yálmúrû nǝ ɓanggi Ɓakuli ka,
\q1 
\v 4 nǝ̀ pa kǝla tǎlaban mala dǝmbari, lang pwari nǝ nggǝ eau ka,
\q2 dǝmbari mǝnana pànǝ apǝrɓang raka,
\q1 lang lolloapì bondo nǝ nggǝ to a nzali,
\q2 aɓa tā-pwari anzǝm nya mala mbulo ka.
\q1 
\v 5 Aɓa mǝsǝcau ka, anggo sǝ ɓala mem pa aban Ɓakuli re?
\q1 Yì ka kutina aɓa kùrcau nǝ mim,
\q2 pàcau mǝnana málá male pà kàm raka,
\q2 kùrcau mǝnana gilǝkice aɓa koyagir, sǝ kwakite kàngkàng ngga.
\q1 Mǝno nda amsǝban mem kat,
\q2 andǝ suno mem kat.
\q1 Pà nǝ̀ tsǝì ɓǝ̀ gul re?
\q1 
\v 6 Sǝama amǝ'ɓealɓikea ka, à nda kǝla azwe mǝnana à nǝ̀ sukkia ka,
\q2 acemǝnana kǝɓwa pa nǝ̀ jea nǝ bui ɗàng.
\q1 
\v 7 Ɓwa mǝnana nǝ̀ jea ka,
\q2 dumǝna púp nǝ̀ kùr rǝi nǝ gara-bolo ko gara nzo.
\q1 Sǝ à nǝ̀ pisǝia a bǝsa kàng a kǝ banì.>>
\s1 Akanggǝrang aburana mala Dauda
\p 
\v 8 Amǝnia ka, à nda ka alullǝ akanggǝrang aɓwana mǝnana Dauda ndanǝia ka: Joshep-Basshebet ɓwa Tachemon, nda mǝdǝmba mala amǝgulo-lwa, sǝ à tunǝi ɗǝm ama Adino, ɓwa Ezni; wal-lú aɓwana gbǝman-tongno-nong-tàrú (800) aɓa lwa mwashat.
\p 
\v 9 Ɓwa mǝnana kpate ka, nda Eleaza muna-ɓwabura mala Dodo, muna-ɓwabura mala Ahohi; nda mwashat atà akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa tàrú mana atà Dauda, lang à cam kàngkàng a kún amǝ'Filisti mǝnana à yi ramba abanɓwáná ace lwa, sǝ aburana mala Isǝrayila nyar nǝtea ka.
\v 10 Yì ka, lo sǝ wal amǝ'Filisti ba aulǝa pàkki wi, gandǝa buì shiuri arǝ nggeabyau; sǝ a mǝno yì pwari ka, Yahweh yinǝ limurǝm mǝgule; sǝ lang amǝ'lwa nyare à yiu anzǝmi ka, kǝ gìr mǝnana à pàk ka, nda pwan gǝna-lwa mala aɓiu-mǝbura mǝnana à wal-luia ka.
\p 
\v 11 Sǝ Shamma muna-ɓwabura mala Agi ɓwa Harar kpa. Lang amǝ'Filisti ram rǝia abanɓwáná a Lehi a ban ɓè ɓaban mǝnana lùmsǝ nǝ gwalong ngga, acili amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila ɓanggi amǝ'Filisti.
\v 12 Sǝama yì Shamma ka cam a tsùrú mala ɓabanì, munǝ ace, sǝ wal amǝ'Filisti, sǝ Yahweh yinǝì Isǝrayila limurǝm mǝgule.
\p 
\v 13 Pǝlǝa akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa mǝnia tàrú aɓalǝ amǝgulo lumi-tàrú mala amǝ'lwa ka, à sulǝo sǝ à yiu aban Dauda a gumi-ɓa'tali mǝnana a Adulam ngga nǝ kún pwan-gìrɓaban, a bàkú mǝnana amǝ'lwa mala amǝ'Filisti duk-katti a ɓangŋaban Refayim ngga.
\v 14 A mǝno yì bàkú ka, Dauda na a kanggǝrang-ban, sǝ amǝ'Filisti ka, à angŋa Betalami sǝ à tamsǝna ɓè nggǝsan mala amǝ'lwa malea abanì.
\v 15 Sǝ Dauda ɓua mǝsamur kǝ̀rkǝ́r, na ama, <<Mǝsamur mala mùr tūli-mùr mǝnana a kún là mala Betalami ka, walnam kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Mǝ nǝ earce, ɓǝ̀ ɓeɓwa nǝ̀ ɗàrǝa nǝ̀ pàm ngga!>>
\v 16 Akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa man tàrú ka, à ar nǝɓalǝ amǝlwa mǝnana aɓa kàttì mala amǝ'Filisti ka, à kya ɗàrǝ́ mùr a tūli-mùr mǝnana a kún là mala Betalami ka, sǝ à twali à yinǝì Dauda. Sǝama ɓinǝ nuie; solǝi a nzali aɓadǝm Yahweh.
\v 17 Bang ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ sappi banam, Yahweh, mǝnana ɓǝn nu mùr man ngga! Mǝnia ka nkila mala aburana na mǝnana à twal yilǝmia a kún buia ka re?>> Acemani ka, Dauda nu mùrnî ɗàng. Akanggǝrang aburana man tàrú ka, à na à pàk amǝnia yì agir ka.
\p 
\v 18 Abishai, mǝ'eam Jowap, muna-ɓwabura mala Zeruya nda ɓwamǝgule amur amǝ'lwa mǝno lumi-tàrú ka. Pàktúró nǝ kaɗa male a munǝo arǝ aburana gbǝman-tàrú (300), sǝ wal-luia, sǝ kum lullǝu atà akanggǝrang amǝlwa mǝno tàrú ka.
\v 19 Yì na mǝnana lullǝì zǝ́kí kútì mala aɓwana man lumi-tàrú ka, acemani ka, à twali pǝlǝ mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban amuria; sǝama, à ɓalli aɓalǝ amǝ'lwa man tàrú ka ɗàng.
\p 
\v 20 Benaya muna-ɓwabura mala Jehoyada ka, kanggǝrang ɓwa na mǝnana pur a Kabzil ka; pàkki agir gyambǝliban mǝgulke. Yì na mǝnana wal amuna-burana ɓari mala Ariyel ɓwa Mowap ka. Ɗǝm ngga, a pwari mana talimbulo kpani ka, sulǝ atà im aɓa tūli, sǝ wal-luí kàm.
\v 21 Wal-lú ɓè ɓwa'Masar, kaɓa ɓwa. Ɓwa'Masar mǝno ka, ndanǝ nkongŋo a bui, sǝama Benaya sulǝ atè nǝ gara-kwalta, ak nkongŋo a bu ɓwa'Masarnî, sǝ wal-luí nǝi.
\v 22 Amǝno ka, à nda ka agir mǝnana Benaya muna-ɓwabura mala Jehoyada pea ka, sǝ kumbi ɓamúrì lullǝu atà akanggǝrang amǝ'lwa mǝno tàrú ka.
\v 23 Lullǝì zǝ́kí kútì mala aɓwana man lumi-tàrú ka, sǝama bwalta amǝno tàrú ka ɗàng. Sǝ Dauda twali tsǝì, duk ɓwamǝgule amur amǝ'yáltè.
\p 
\v 24 Aɓea aɓwana aɓalǝ aɓwana mǝno lumi-tàrú ka, à nda ka:
\li1 Asahel mǝ'eam Jowap;
\li1 Elhanan muna-ɓwabura mala Dodo ɓwa Betalami;
\li1 
\v 25 Shamma ɓwa Harot,
\li1 Elika ɓwa Harot;
\li1 
\v 26 Helez ɓwa Palti;
\li1 Ira muna-ɓwabura mala Ikkesh ɓwa Tekowa;
\li1 
\v 27 Abiyeza ɓwa Anatot;
\li1 Mebunayi ɓwa Hushati;
\li1 
\v 28 Zalmon ɓwa Ahohi;
\li1 Maharayi ɓwa Netofa;
\li1 
\v 29 Helep muna-ɓwabura mala Baana ɓwa Netofa;
\li1 Ittayi muna-ɓwabura mala Ribayi ɓwa Gibiya mala bu-nzali Benjami;
\li1 
\v 30 Benaya ɓwa Piraton;
\li1 Hiddayi ɓwa mala amealmur Gaash;
\li1 
\v 31 Abi-albon ɓwa Arbati;
\li1 Azǝmavet ɓwa Barhum;
\li1 
\v 32 Eliyaba ɓwa Shaalboni;
\li1 amuna-burana mala Jashen;
\li1 sǝ Jonatan;
\li1 
\v 33 Shamma ɓwa Harar;
\li1 Ayiyam muna-ɓwabura mala Sharar ɓwa Arar;
\li1 
\v 34 Elifelet muna-ɓwabura mala Ahasbayi, muna-ɓwabura mala ɓwa Ma'aka;
\li1 Eliyam muna-ɓwabura mala Ahitofel ɓwa Gilo;
\li1 
\v 35 Hezǝro ɓwa Kamel;
\li1 Pa'arayi ɓwa Arbi;
\li1 
\v 36 Igal muna-ɓwabura mala Natan ɓwa Zoba;
\li1 Bani ɓwa Gad;
\li1 
\v 37 Zelek ɓwa Amon;
\li1 Naharayi ɓwa Beerot, mǝ-bwal-agirmunǝo mala Jowap muna-ɓwabura mala Zuriya;
\li1 
\v 38 Ira ɓwa Itǝri;
\li1 Garep ɓwa Itǝri;
\li1 
\v 39 sǝ Yuriya ɓwa Hitti. Yià kat ka, à nda lumi-tàrú bwamdǝ tongno-nong-ɓari (37).
\c 24
\s1 Dauda ɓal amǝ'lwa
\p 
\v 1 Ɗǝm ngga bumlulla mala Yahweh earki amur Isǝrayila, soakita Dauda arǝia ɓǝ̀ banggia wia ama, <<Wu kyane wu ɓal amǝ Isǝrayila andǝ amǝ Yahuda.>>
\v 2 Pǝlǝa murǝm banggi Jowap mǝ'sàrǝ̀ban mala amǝ'lwa mǝnana atè ka ama, <<Wu kya aɓalǝ atau mala Isǝrayila tite a Dan aban ká Biyasheba, sǝ wu pwan alullǝ amǝ'lwa, ace mǝnana ɓǝn súrǝ̀ lakki malea.>>
\v 3 Sǝ Jowap ne wi ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh Ɓakuli mô hatǝki aɓwana kusǝ gbǝman, sǝ ɓǝ̀ mǝsǝ ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝni. Sǝama mana tsǝa sǝ ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm earce nǝ̀ pàk mǝnia yì gìr ka?>>
\p 
\v 4 Kat andǝ mani ka, cau mala murǝm par mala Jowap andǝ amǝsà'arǝ amǝ'lwa, pǝlǝa à nying ɓadǝm murǝm, à o a pwan alullǝ amǝ'lwa mala Isǝrayila.
\p 
\v 5 À yàl nkaring Jodan, à kya tsǝk kàttì a Aruwa, a njar-kunmur mala nggea-là mǝnana a tsùrú mala ɓangŋaban, a bu-nzali Gad ka. À lo kano ka, à wari a Jaza.
\v 6 Pǝlǝa à yiu a Gilǝyat, andǝ bu-nzali mala Tatim-Hodshi, sǝ à yiu a Dan-jaan, sǝ à pǝlǝa aban ká a Sidon;
\v 7 sǝ à yiu a kanggǝrang-ban mala Taya andǝ anggea-là mala amǝ'Hivi andǝ mala amǝ'Kan'ana kat; sǝ à pur aban ká nǝ [Negev], njar-kunmur mala Yahuda a Biyasheba.
\v 8 Sǝ lang à gingŋǝ́na aɓa nzalî kat ka, à yi bik Urǝshalima a masǝlǝata zongŋo tongno-nong-ine nǝ anongŋo lumi-ɓari.
\v 9 Jowap pe murǝm lakkì mala aɓwana mǝnana à ɓallia ka: aɓa Isǝrayila ka, akanggǝrang aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ bwal nggeabyau ka, à nda á-gbǝman-tongno-nong-tàrú (800,000), sǝ amǝ Yahuda ka, à nda á-gbǝman-tongno (500,000).
\s1 Ɓashi mala Yahweh arǝ cauɓikea mala Dauda
\p 
\v 10 Ɓabum Dauda tè anzǝm mana ɓallǝna aɓwana ka. Sǝ Dauda ne Yahweh ama, <<Ən pàngŋǝ́nà cauɓikea mǝgule nǝ gìr mǝnana ǝn pàk ka. Sǝama ado ka, ida, Yahweh twalî guro mò ban mǝɓane mǝnana pàk ka, acemǝnana ǝn pàngŋǝ́nà gìr ɓwaɓana.>>
\v 11 Sǝ lang Dauda lo nǝ dǝmbari ka, cau mala Yahweh yiu aban mǝɓangnǝa Gad, mǝ'sǝna mala Dauda ama,
\v 12 <<Kya banggi Dauda ama, <Yahweh kǝ na ama, mǝ nda rǝ po agir tàrú. Twal mwashat atea, mǝnana Mǝ nǝ yinǝi amuro ka.> >>
\v 13 Nda Gad yiu aban Dauda sǝ banggi wi cê ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ nzal-gula mala pǝlǝa tàrú yipo aɓa nzali mô le, ko awu nǝ ɓang a ɓadǝmba aɓio-mǝbura sǝ à nǝ̀ nggǝ pǝrto mala azongŋo tàrú le, ko ɓǝ̀ kwánó-twàl-là sulǝ aɓa nzali mô mala nongŋo tàrú? Ado ka, ɓalkiɓabumo sǝ wu nam, ya pa'eare na ɓabumo twalo, ace mǝnana mǝ kya banggi ɓwa mǝnana túrǎm ngga.>>
\v 14 Pǝlǝa Dauda banggi Gad ama, <<Mǝ nda aɓa nggikiban kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Nǝ̀ ɓoaribani ɓǝ̀ sǝm kpa a ɓabù Yahweh, acemǝnana mǝsǝswatǝr male gulo; pà mǝ nǝ eare ɓǝ̀ sǝm kpa a ɓabù ɓwapǝndǝa ɗang.>>
\p 
\v 15 Nda Yahweh tasǝ kwánó-twàl-là amur Isǝrayila, twal a dǝmbari mǝno aban ká masǝlǝata anonggio mǝnana à kasǝ ka. Sǝ aburana á-lumi-tongno-nong-ɓari (70,000) wǔ, twal a Dan aban ká a Biyasheba.
\v 16 Lang mǝturonjar mala Yahweh sárǝ́ bui sǝ lǝmdǝi nǝban Urǝshalima ace kiɗike ka, Yahweh nggaɗi ɗenyicau male arǝ mǝno yi gir'murmwana ka, sǝ ne mǝturonjar mǝnana kǝ kiɗiki aɓwana ka ama, <<Karǝna! Ado ka nyesǝ buo.>> Sǝ mǝturonjar mala Yahweh ka, nda a katǝra mala Arauna ɓwa'Jebus.
\p 
\v 17 Dauda sǝn mǝturonjar mǝnana kǝ kiɗiki aɓwana ka. Pǝlǝa ne Yahweh ama, <<Sǝni, mǝ nda mǝnana ǝn pak cauɓikea ka; mǝ nda mǝnana ǝn pak mǝɓike ka. Sǝ anzur mǝnia ka, mana à pa? Ida, ɗeki buo ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝ arǝàm sǝnǝ ɓala mala tárrám.>>
\s1 Dauda ɓak gyangŋan
\p 
\v 18 Gad yiu aban Dauda a mǝno yì pwari ka, sǝ banggi wi ama, <<Eauwe, kya ɓakkì Yahweh gyangŋan a katǝra mala Arauna ɓwa'Jebus.>>
\v 19 Nda Dauda lo aɓa kpata cau mala Gad kǝla mǝnana Yahweh na ka.
\v 20 Lang Arauna dili mǝsǝi sǝ sǝn murǝm andǝ amǝtúró male dǝshini aban yiu ka, pǝlǝa wario kya ɓun a ɓadǝm murǝm nǝ ɓamǝsǝi a nzali.
\v 21 Sǝ Arauna bang ama, <<Mana yinǝ ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm abanam, mim guro male?>>
\p Dauda banggi wi ama, <<Ace kúr katǝra a buo, ace mǝnana mǝ ɓakkì Yahweh gyangŋan, ace tamsǝ mǝnia yi kwánó-ɓikea ka, ɓǝ̀ nying aɓwe.>>
\p 
\v 22 Arauna ne Dauda ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ ɓwamǝgule mem murǝm twali sǝ ɓǝ̀ paɓoro mala gìr mǝnana ɓoari wi ka. Sǝni, ajamnda mem nia ka, twalia ace paɓoro mala pisǝe kǝring. Sǝ agara nyagir andǝ anggun-rya malea nia ka ace gimsa.
\v 23 Agir mǝnia kat ka, we murǝm, mim Arauna ǝn panì murǝm.>> Sǝ Arauna banggi murǝm ɗǝm ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Yahweh Ɓakuli mô ak ɓoro mô.>>
\p 
\v 24 Sǝama murǝm ne Arauna ama, <<Awo; mǝ nǝ kúrí nǝ kúró. Pà mǝ nǝ paɓoro mala pisǝe kǝring aban Yahweh Ɓakuli mem sǝ ǝn mbwe kǝgìr ace raka ɗàng.>> Nda Dauda kúr katǝranî andǝ ajamndè a kún mǝsǝboalo shekel lumi-tongno ka.
\v 25 Dauda ɓakkî Yahweh gyangŋan abanì, sǝ pa agir'nkila mala pisǝe kǝring andǝ apaɓoro mala dotarǝu. Pǝlǝa Yahweh ok hiwi male amur nzalinì, sǝ twalî Isǝrayila kwánó-ɓikê.
